Name: SOLEI- Free Slims Pre-Roll 10X0.4G Sativa
description: Freeing and familiar, enjoy Free Slims in a conveniently abundant pack. With CBD dominant flower, they’re flexible enough for any opportunity. Name: 3SAINTS Road Dawg | 28g
description: If you want a gently soothing bud to unwind with after a hard day, look elsewhere, as Road Dawg is NOT your go-to choice. This strain delivers a potent THC punch, accompanied by robust effects, making it advisable to steer clear if you’re a newbie. The flower exhibits a minty green hue, adorned with thick pistils and an even thicker layer of glistening, trichomes. Road Dawg offers a WTF? Flavour profile in a good way — melding tropical fruit with hints of mint, all underscored by a pronounced diesel note, leaving users pondering the enigmatic experience they’ve just encountered. Hand harvested, hang dried, and dry trimmed to protect those hard-won trichomes

Name: GENERAL ADMISSION Pineapple Guava THC & CBD Gummy (1:1)

The Pineapple pre-roll comes packed with Lemon Cookies flower, the Blueberry pre-roll comes loaded with Truffle Breath flower and the Grape Mint pre-roll comes packed with Pink Candy flower.

Name: BERNARD'S CANNABIS CREATIONS Almond Butter Cups
description: A key differentiator for our products is our master chocolatier, Bernard Callebaut. He is a fifth generation chocolatier originally from Belgium. His great-grandfather began making chocolates in Belgium in 1911. Bernard himself has been making chocolates in Canada since 1983. Bernard is known for making quality products with premium ingredients. We are an artisan brand that will be known to consumers as chocolatiers making cannabis edibles and not a cannabis company experimenting with chocolate. Although we use premium ingredients, we want our products to retail at an affordable price. We understand market dynamics in the chocolate industry and cannabis space and we do not want the price point to be prohibitive to our potential customers.

Your Shatterizer will come fully assembled with user instructions.
 
 Your Shatterizer Starter Kit duals as a travel box with:
 1 Shatterizer borosilicate glass globe, atomizer base, Quartz Dual Coil (QDC) coil and coil cap, 1 bonus QDC coil and coil cap, 1 Shatterizer Lithium-Ion battery with 3 Stage Variable Voltage, 1 Magnetic Silicone Lined Wax Storage Container, 1 Micro USB Cord with Pass Thru technology and 1 Dab tool. This special strain is beloved across Canada for its strong aromas, colourful flowers, and high THC potential. Beneath a thick coating of trichomes, the dense and round buds feature forest green leaves, often with a purple hue, mixed with dark amber pistils. Grown in a high-tech greenhouse in the Fraser Valley, each bud is carefully trimmed and hand-groomed, dried and cured to precise standards. Pink Kush showcases gassy aromas of white pepper, orange, butterscotch, coffee, earth, and grapefruit, the result of a rich combination of terpenes that includes caryophyllene, myrcene, humulene, bisabolol, and limonene.

With thick, dense buds that are caked in trichomes, this cultivar's bag appeal is sure to impress even the pickiest cannabis connoisseurs. All buds are grown in living soil, hang dried for 14 days, cold cured and non-irradiated.

Name: PORT NORTH Cherry Boat - Full Spectrum Live Rosin Syrup
description: 100% solventless, no additives, no chemicals, solvents, cuts, fillers or flavour additives. Port North is extremely selective with the genetics and producers it works with. Using high quality, whole plant, fresh frozen, (WPFF) sun grown, living soil flower, never trim, never smalls. Our live rosin syrup is a strain specific, high terpene solventless hash oil (HTSHO). Made from full spectrum 45 - 189u ice water hash delivering an unparalleled flavour that is true to the taste that you would expect from a dab of live rosin. Port North live rosin syrup AVD vape carts use premium hardware to offer mobile dosing that delivers effective, clean and controlled experiences. Lineage: (Cherry Pie x Chem 91) x Top Dog Chem x 11 Week Pink Kush S1. Grow Method: Sun Grown LSO. Bred, selected and grown by 7 Farms Down in Chatham-Kent, Ontario.

Name: (250mg) LEMON THC LOZENGES
description: No description available

Name: Pure Sunfarms - Pink Kush Indica - 28g
description: Pure Sunfarms’ cut of Pink Kush from BC’s Vancouver Island is a coastal relative of the legendary OG Kush. This special strain is beloved across Canada for its strong aromas, colourful flowers, and high THC potential. Beneath a thick coating of trichomes, the dense and round buds feature forest green leaves, often with a purple hue, mixed with dark amber pistils. Grown in a high-tech greenhouse in the Fraser Valley, each bud is carefully trimmed and hand-groomed, dried and cured to precise standards. Pink Kush showcases gassy aromas of white pepper, orange, butterscotch, coffee, earth, and grapefruit, the result of a rich combination of terpenes that includes caryophyllene, myrcene, humulene, bisabolol, and limonene.

Name: JANE & JUICE MTL Blond Hash
description: This product is made using only a single cannabis cultivar called Black Cherry Punch. Our process utilizes cold water with no additional solvents, and a novel method to sift through the plant matter and selects only the trichomes of the plant which yields an extremely pure product. We use precise temperatures and control pressing to ensure minimal loss of terpenes and the production of a soft malleable product resembling ‘traditional pressed hashish’. Our ‘MTL Hash’ is high in THC, has a rich earthy colour, and gives a robust unique aromatic flavour that is sweet and fruity with floral undertones.

Name: JONNY CHRONIC - Reefer-Ready Northern Lights
description: Northern Lights from Jonny Chronic is a potent sun grown indica dominant strain that produces dense green buds with a thick frosting of trichomes. Northern Lights is a landrace lineage crossing an Afghani x Thai cultivar and is dominant in caryophyllene, limonene, myrcene and bisabolol. Cultivated in southwestern Ontario under the sun, all of our plants are hang dried and cured before our team goes through and carefully selects top colas to then be hand trimmed and hand packed in-house.

Name: DIVVY Black Widow CBD 510 Thread Cartridge
description: High in CBD with a little THC and lots of terps in the mix, this 1g 510 vape cartridge uses winterized resin from our popular Black Widow CBD strain with a custom blend of terps to accentuate its existing aroma profile, and offers an entourage of cannabinoids along with that spicy full-bodied flavour you already know and love from the flower.

Name: Outta This World 3D Magnetic Tray Cover
description: No description available

Name: CANACA Afghaniskunk | 28g
description: Afghaniskunk is an indica lover’s paradise with ludicrous amounts of fruity, sweet and sour flavours and high THC potency. Explore classic Skunk #1 x Afghani genetics and their oversized light green buds ablaze with orange pistils and golden trichomes. Afghaniskunk is hang dried, hand trimmed and carefully cured for an ultra-potent experience with irresistible sweet, sour and skunk aromas with a consistently smooth smoke and salt and pepper ash. The bold and dominant caryophyllene, myrcene and farnesene terpenes provide eye-popping aromas and smile-inducing flavours perfect for a potently Canadian journey.

Name: TWEED Lites Quickies CBD OG Kush Pre-Rolled Cannabis Joints
description: Tweed Lites Quickies pre-rolls are made with CBD OG Kush, an indica dominant strain with high CBD and a minimal amount of THC. CBD OG Kush is a cross between a CBD cultivar and the classic OG Kush. Some associate spicy, woody, lemon or fuel flavours with this strain. Tweed Lites Quickies come in a portable and recyclable case, keeping them sealed, protected and ready when you are. Evenly milled and machine rolled for a consistent burn.

Name: QWEST P.S. Cheetah
description: Qwest was born from a deep appreciation for the plant and its process. We are here for the journey every grower undertakes with each new harvest and we respect that even with the most familiar cultivars there's always opportunity to go beyond the ordinary. These bright green buds in a frosty thick coating give off heavy aromas of citrus and gas when broken open, only to indulge taste buds with a creamy and fruity flavour profile. Created by crossing Lemonade x Gelato 42 x London Pound Cake, this is one of the most pungent we've ever released.

Name: DOUBLE J'S Cherry Boat Pre-Rolls | 2-Pack
description: Cherry Boat is a sativa-dominant strain selected from our Cherry Boat worked line that blends the strong THC potency of an 11 week Pink Kush that was found in bag seed many years ago crossed with the delicious flavour of Top Dawg Cherry Chem. Our Cherry Boat was grown in sunny South Western Ontario in living soil, whole plant hung and offering high THC and terpenes. Cared by a talented team of legacy craft growers. Featuring strong THC potency potential with 3.5%+ terpenes the combination yields a sweet fruit with earthy chocolate undertones and a bit of funk. Bred by, selected by, and grown by 7 Farms Down.

Name: PROVINCE BRANDS Yandi Fresh Cranberry Apple Cider
description: Designed with your favourite apple ciders in mind, Yandi Fresh Cranberry Apple Cider is the perfect beverage for both the casual beverage consumer as well as the avid cider connoisseur. Made with real apple juice and enhanced with natural cranberry flavour, this 10 mg THC beverage will remind you of your favourite apple ciders. Boasting a moderate sweetness balanced by a natural cranberry tartness, this light bodied cider creates a refreshing experience from start to finish. Yandi Fresh Cranberry Apple Cider tastes exactly as you’d expect with no experimental flavour combinations or unknown ingredients.

Name: SHERBINSKIS Ceramic Tip Moch & Acai Infused Pre-Roll Duo-Pack
description: Why Choose? This duo-pack of Sherbinskis cult classics, MOCHI & ACAI gives you the best of both worlds. Two unique pre-rolls, each infused with a boost of signature Sherbinskis flavour and distillate, finished with ceramic tips for enhanced air flow and an even burn all the way through. SHERBINSKIS originates from the Sunset District of San Francisco, California where it established itself as a leader in bringing novel genetics, like Sunset Sherbs, to market. The brand is one of the most revered cannabis brands with a strong cult following.

Name: SIMPLY BARE BC Organic Blue Dream Pre-Rolls | 5-Pack
description: Our version of this sativa dominant Blue Dream uses whole flower. This Blue Dream is exceptionally aromatic giving a strong blueberry aroma with a warm and peppery terpene profile. Grown in living soil, hang dried for 14 days, cold cured and hand packed in hemp cones.

Name: REDECAN Khalifuel Redees Hemp'd Pre-Rolls
description: Khalifuel is an indica-dominant cross of Grape Gasoline x Khalifa Mints. Indulge in the dense emerald buds with green hues and golden amber like hairs that are beautifully dusted with a fine layer of trichomes. The dominant terpene profile of limonene, humulene, myrcene and caryophyllene gives this strain an earthy pungency complemented by a fragrant fruit and subtle sourness. This delightfully chill strain reaches heights of high THC through conscientious care and attention given to each plant through every stage of the growing process. Harvested at its peak, expertly cured and hand trimmed to ensure the highest level of quality.

Name: BOLD GLAZED - Kiwi Berry Twist AIO Disposable
description: BOLD GLAZED Kiwi Berry Twist is a burst of juicy kiwi and succulent berries. Fresh tropical flavours with sweet strawberry. This all-in-one disposable vape contains high levels of THC with limonene, myrcene, caryophyllene.

Name: Crystal Skull Glass Dabber
description: No description available

Name: 7ACRES - Sensi Star 3.5G Indica
description: 7Acres’ indica-dominant Sensi Star is grown indoors and sun-enriched to improve its dense flower structure, and then slow-dried, artisan-cured and hand-polished. Sensi Star has strong lemon and pepper aromas that come from the limonene and trans-caryophyllene in its terpene profile, and has very strong THC potency.

Name: SHRED'EMS Pink Lemonade Yuzu 2:1 THCv:THC
description: What's a Yuzu? It's basically a small lemon, maybe a bit more tart. Trust us, it's nice. The added bonus is some THCV in this soft chew at a 2:1 ratio for 20 mg of THCV and 10 mg of THC per pack. SHRED's THCV is derived from the whole flower Get S**t Done strain.

Name: LITTI Gulupa Gulp 510 Thread Cartridge
description: LITTI's Gulupa Gulp 510 vape cart is packed with passion fruit flavoured THC topped with liquid diamonds. And the best part? It won't cost you an arm and a leg. Trust us, your taste buds and your wallet will thank you.

Name: MTL CANNABIS Jungl' Cake | 3.5g
description: These Jungl’ Cake buds are lime green with thin, deep orange hairs and a coating of frosty white crystal trichomes. The flavour is sweet with notes of pastry dough, creamy marshmallow and cashews. The aroma is earthy and nutty with a sweet fruity overtone that’s both sugary and spicy.

Name: SMOKES- Tropical Punch 1:1 Pre-Roll 5X0.7G Sativa
description: All the ancestors are loaded with sweet terps and resin which are inherited by this sweet treat.  She can rival any THC plant in all categories. Purple Punch (Grand Daddy Purps x Larry OG) has met her match with a unique CBD line built with Harlequin (CBD Hashplant) and ACDC (Cannatonic). The product meets and exceeds all craft requirements. It is a true green and pure full spectrum sunlight product from seed to harvest while it has grown within clean greenhouse facility to ensure the highest quality. It has been fed artisan well water only. Our pre-rolls are rolled using slow burning high quality durable unbleached unrefined paper. The “filter” has a whole in the middle allowing for full enjoyment. The pre-rolls are rolled rather than stuffed. This is important because cones are stuffed which stacks the cannabis rather than weaves it. This makes it very easy for cones to fall apart. Slow burning is key to getting the most out of quality cannabis.

Name: PURE SUNFARMS High THC 510 Thread Cartridge
description: This high THC vape is filled with high potency natural cannabis extract. The custom ceramic mouthpiece and coil create a clean and consistent burn for a smooth, flavourful and highly potent product.

Name: Pure Sunfarms- Marmalade Punch Pre-Roll Indica 10X0.3G
description: A potent indica, rolled and ready to spark. Each pre-roll is packed with Marmalade Punch, a high-THC cross of Black Cherry Punch x D. Burger, with aromas of blood orange, candied mango, mulling spices and a light and garlicky gas finish. Pure BC-grown whole flower – no trim, no shake. Conveniently portioned for a quick session. Made with natural paper, each pre-roll is finished with a twisted end to prevent spillage and act as a wick. Potent pre-rolls packaged in a recyclable carton.

Name: Lune Rise Farms - Strawberry Fields Pre-Roll
description: Lune Rise Farms whole flower pre-rolls are sourced from a single strain cannabinoid and hand harvested to preserve each strain's unique cannabinoid and terpene profile. Our Strawberry Fields premium terpene profile delivers a delightfully sweet aroma coup

Name: 3" Crimson Score Spoon Pipe
description: No description available

Name: MINISTRY OF SATIVA Durban Diesel | 7g
description: Durban Diesel is a hybrid between two legendary strains, Durban P and Sour Diesel. Our current batch reaches over 3% terpenes with beta-myrcene being the dominant terpene. Durban Diesel has a gassy, fuel and spice combination of flavours with hints of pine and chestnuts.

Name: CARMEL Kush Life
description: Exclusively bred by us in-house, Kush Life is a cross of Y Life x Skywalker OG. Kush Life was selected for its incredibly unique flavour of cherry cough syrup balanced out by its strong aroma of gas. When you open your bag, you’ll be presented with super frosty, large chunky buds that deliver that legendary OG density. Because it’s the right thing to do, all of our flower is hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cold cured, and hand packaged. We believe fresh and terpy is best, so all our flower is packaged in a nitrogen flushed pouch with a humidity pack. Non-irradiated, obviously.

Name: JONNY CHRONIC- Unicorn Poop 510 Thread Cartridge Indica 1G
description: Unicorn Poop by Jonny Economy is an indica-dominant strain with 88-94% THC and minimal CBD. Made with THC distillate and botanical terpenes, Unicorn Poop is dominant in myrcene, pinene and ocimene providing a sweet cherry aroma. Jonny Economy cartridges are made by Greentank and are compatible with most generic 510- threaded batteries.

Name: COLLECTIVE PROJECT Island Time (Mango Pineapple & Coconut) Sparkling Juice
description: You’ll feel like you’re on a tropical beach with our take on the Caribbean classic. We mixed mango and pineapple juices with coconut and lemongrass. Collective Project brings a local craft mentality to a new category. Our products are crafted with real ingredients and designed with cannabis in mind, but we don’t want that to be the only thing you remember. In our drinks, cannabis is one ingredient and flavour, just like any other — something that needs to be balanced, highlighted and complemented by the recipe. What you get are flavourful juices loaded with fresh ingredients and provide the most elevated experience in the market.

Name: SIMPLY BARE BC Organic Lime Mi'jito Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: Our BC Organic Lime Mi'Jito is a sativa-leaning cross of Limegerian x Orange Blossom Trail cultivars. The strong lime aromas are complimented by floral and earthy undertones. Grown in living soil, hang dried for 14 days, cold cured and non irradiated. The whole bud is milled to perfection and rolled with hemp papers, finished by hand.

Name: TERRA LABS Sticky Papaya Infused Pre-Rolls
description: This sativa-dominant hybrid pops with a topical fruit flavour. Premium flower, grown indoors and infused with single strain sourced diamonds. It contains high levels of terpinolene, farnesene and caryophyllene.

Name: General Admission- 5 Loco Distillate Infused Pre-Roll 5X0.5G
description: Sourced from quality whole-flower cultivars, infused with our signature distillate and dusted in premium kief, this is not just any squish in a stick. 5 Loko is at least one better than four. This fruity, cherry forward pre-roll packed with citrus lime flavour is sure to have taste buds dancing the night away. You’re sure to love ALL the flavour with none of the holes in the drywall.

Name: Barted Metal Rolling Tray - Small
description: No description available

Name: BRZY LLB Cannabis Infused Sparkling Spring Water
description: This flavour is modelled after a popular soda in the Caribbean called LLB which stands for Lemon, Lime & Bitters. Craft, carbon neutral company, eco-friendly packaging, natural ingredients and award winning spring water. Containing only 3g of cane sugar and 20 calories, its citrus flavour pairs very well with the earthy cannabis notes. Contains 20mg CBD and 10mg THC, for a more enjoyable experience.

Name: BOLD Tropical Lime Freeze AIO Disposable
description: BOLD’s Tropical Lime Freeze is a sweet blend of lime and tropical fruit. Inspired by Tropical Lime this cart is fresh, sweet, and packs potency with its high levels of THC, myrcene, pinene and caryophyllene. This all-in-one disposable vape contains high levels of THC with myrcene, limonene and caryophyllene.

Name: HIGH STREET CANNABIS Platinum Punch Remix2 - Bubble Hash Infused Pre-Roll
description: The High Street Cannabis² lineup of infused pre-rolls makes its debut with our current favourite, Platinum Punch Remix². This unique strain with intense flavour and an ultra smooth experience gets an extra boost from bubble hash extracted from itself. With an increase in potency and terpenes, it truly brings out the characteristics of the strain for you to enjoy. Creamy, smooth inhale with a slight berry and fruity flavour on the exhale.

Name: BLK MKT Exclusives
description: Introducing THE EXCLUSIVES by BLK MKT. Limited drops where we bring some of our rarest, most unique genetics to life. Always Handcrafted, from Our Genetics, Our Growers, and grown in Our Facilities. Graded & Hand Packaged into premium matte-black glass jars.

Name: KRONIC Triple P Pre-Rolls
description: We are proud to present Triple Pink – a curated trio of premium pink strains. This unique selection showcases the essence of our passion for cannabis. Prepare to indulge in the legendary Pink Kush, exquisite Pink Cookies, and captivating Pink Pantah. Each pre-roll offers its own unique journey into the world of Kronic Pink Kush, a sensory cannabis experience that stands in a class of its own. Every detail is done by hand, from precise trimming to gentle milling & expert packaging.

Name: FUEGO Tangy Mango Distillate Infused Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: The exquisite combination of sweet tangerine and refreshing mango with high potency, infused flower and dusted with kief makes this pre-roll a fruit lover's dream!

Name: LOWKEY BY MTL Dessert Pre-Rolls | 7-Pack
description: LowKey got slick and sweet with our Dessert. A sweet treat 50/50 hybrid cross of Sour Apples x Animal CKS. A dense light green with undertones of purple exotic flower covered in trichomes featuring caryophyllene, limonene and pinene as its main terpenes. Delivering a sweet and sour apple taste intertwined with light vanilla and decadent pastry flavours, this one’s for special guests only!

Name: PURE SUNFARMS Galactic Haze | 3.5g
description: This hazy sativa is a pheno-hunted cross of legacy legends Haze x Space Queen. Galactic Haze features bright aromas of sliced citrus with a touch of sweet skunk from dominant terpenes terpinolene and beta-pinene. Generously coated with resinous trichomes, the lanky buds showcase a blend of deep greens and burnt orange colours. BC bud, hand harvested, hang dried and hand finished.

Name: ROILTY Hawaiian Thunder & Imperial Peach 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Two Roilty Vapes, two times the flavour for daze. Featuring our popular Hawaiian Thunder Queen cart, and our new juicy Imperial Peach cart. These high potency vapes boast flavourful botanical terpene profiles based on their inspired strains of Tropic Thunder and Peach OG.

These pre-rolls are produced by hand to ensure an amazing experience each and every time. With an alluring aroma and flavour, Freedom Reserve Sunset is the perfect was to watch the sun go down after a long day!

Name: TRURO Caps Junky | 7g
description: Caps Junky by Truro is a potent legacy hybrid. The cultivar is a collaborative project between two breeders, Capulator and Seed Junky Genetics. This 50/50 balanced strain was created by crossing Kush Mints (Bubba Kush x Animal Mints) x Alien Cookies (Alien OG x Cripple Cake Cookies). Flavour profile is sweet, fruity and minty. Caps Junky buds are a beautiful dark green with orange hairs and frosty crystal trichomes. Caps Junky is proudly grown on the East Coast in Truro, NS in our state-of-the-art small batch production facility, where each bud is carefully cultivated, hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cured (21-28 days), and hand packaged in recyclable aluminum cans that are purged with liquid nitrogen to preserve the dried flower's quality, moisture content and terpene profile.

description: There’s never a dull moment with a Redees Taster Series, because two strains are better than one with five King Sherb and five Animal Rntz Redees for a perfect ten-pack of our signature straight-cut pre-rolls. King Sherb is an indica-dominant hybrid with a pungent funk and creamy diesel smoke. Animal Rntz is an indica-dominant hybrid with sweet fruit and sour tartness flavour. Both have high THC and are better together in a fresh Redees Taster Series made from meticulously grown flower that’s perfectly rolled every time.

Name: EMPRISE RAPID Sour Pomegranate Sativa Soft Chews | 2-Pack
description: Emprise’s Sour Pomegranate Sativa Soft Chews are THC-dominant and use Emprise's Advanced Nano THC Technology. Each sativa-dominant soft chew delivers 5 mg THC with a delicious pomegranate taste. Made without animal products.

Name: SIMPLY BARE BC Organic Fruit Loopz
description: Our new BC Organic Fruit Loopz is a FVOPA certified sativa dominant hybrid that's big on flavour. A cross of Blue Dream x White Widow, these two legendary cultivars boast fruity, berry and citrus notes. It's grown in organic living soil, is slowly hang dried and hand trimmed to preserve trichome integrity.

Name: WYLD Real Fruit Sour Peach Mango 3:1 CBG:THC
description: Wyld Sour Peach Mango sativa-enhanced CBG:THC soft chews are a 3:1 ratio product featuring a restorative, CBG-dominant profile and THC. Made sustainably using real fruit, botanical terpenes, and natural flavours, each soft chew contains 15mg CBG and 5mg THC for a total of 30mg CBG and 10mg THC per pack. All Wyld soft chews are packaged in a compostable pouch, and our recipes are formulated by food scientists to provide consistent experiences that taste amazing. Wyld soft chews use sunflower lecithin to improve bioavailability and onset time and are made to be thermostable up to 55°C, with a firm texture that doesn’t stick to your teeth. Each Wyld Sour Peach Mango sativa-enhanced soft chew contains the terpenes limonene, valencene, alpha-pinene, and beta-pinene. Wyld is proud to be a Climate Neutral Certified brand.

Name: Versus - Mad Mango 510 Thread Cartridge Hybrid 1g
description: Versus Mad Mango 510 vapes are made with high-quality cannabis distillate combined with a terpene-rich blend to deliver notes of ripe mango.

Name: Zig Zag Kutcorners Slow Burning Rolling Papers
description:
Since 1879, Zig-Zag papers are Made in France and deliver the quality you know and trust. These Original White rolling papers are thin and durable so you can enjoy a slow burn and unique experience.

Size:70mm x 38mm
These papers are made using natural flax plant fibers and 100% Natural Gum Arabic.
These classic Original White papers have a special thin glue line to provide a perfect seal for every roll. Derived from the sap of the African acacia tree, the 100% natural properties of gum Arabic provide a consistent seal without impacting the taste
Zig zag papers are a classic and even-burning paper designed to enhance your experience!

Name: RIZZLERS Twisters - Blud Orange & Berry Drip Infused Pre-Rolls
description: This pack of infused pre-rolls is rolled to perfection and infused with the citrus and cranberry burst from Blud Orange and the Berry Drip ooze of berries and grape.

Name: RAW Classic 1 1/4 Cones 6 Pack
description:

Ideal for people who are not comfortable with a hand-roll.
They are the ultimate convenience in rolling because you only need to fill them up with whatever you like to smoke, twist off the end and light up.

Name: TRIBAL Cuban Linx Kodo Pro
description: Game on fleek? Accessorized to the nines? Hat match the belt, match the shoes, match the… Vape? Now you can with the new Tribal Cuban Linx Kodo Pro 510 thread vape battery. Black and yellow never looked so good! All the features of the traditional Kodo pro, but now with that Tribal flair. USB-C recharge, puff counter, 1.8-4.2v, 10 second preheat, no magnetic adapter needed. Slim and discreet, perfect for pockets or stashed in a clutch. Tribal Cuban Linx Kodo Pro. It's everything you need.

Name: DEEP SPACE Orange Orbit
description: Welcome to Deep Space. Small, potent and portable, Deep Space Orange Orbit is a full-flavoured beverage with a bold orange soda taste and a unique Deep Space twist. Fueled by 10mg THC, this infused carbonated beverage comes in a 222ml sleek can.

Name: DOMPEN Passionfruit All-in-One
description: Ignite your senses and embark on a tropical journey with our sativa Tropical cannabis vape pen. This vape pen is infused with the perfect balance of sativa strains and a tantalizing passionfruit flavour. The tropical infusion of passionfruit adds a luscious twist with its tangy and sweet notes. Every puff delights your taste buds, delivering a burst of tropical goodness.

Name: D*GG LBS Cherry Drop – 510 Vape Cartridge
description: Take a ride to the sweet cherry stop! This distillate vape is full of a cherry front-end taste, grape middle, lime end flavouring in a 510 thread cart.

Name: NUGZ GRIND Lemon Linx | 7g
description: Nugz Milled Lemon Linx is a zesty citrus followed by savoury spice purposively crafted whole flower milled blend of our Early Lemon Berry and Cuban Linx sativa flower.

Name: 7ACRES SATIVA DOMINANT JACK HAZE BUBBLE HASH-INFUSED PRE-ROLL
description:
Introducing 7ACRES Jack Haze Whole Flower Pre-Rolls infused with Bubble Hash. Jack Haze Bubble Hash Infused Pre-Rolls are made using a true-to-flower infusion of Jack Haze bubble hash to deliver a pre-roll with boosted potency and increased flavour for an elevated smoking experience. This infusion emboldens Jack Haze’s unique flavour profile of sweet citrus, crisp pine and warm spice notes.
 
 The effects of this product can be felt within seconds to minutes, and can last for up to 6 hours or more. Some effects could last as long as 24 hours.

Name: BLK MKT Ya Hemi | 3.5G
description: Bred by Grandiflora out in California, this unique cross of Project 4516 x Melonatta is extremely potent. Burnt tires, fuel and skunk on the nose, with sweet notes of citrus and plum on the exhale. This cultivar delivers a truly unique experience. Not for novices. Our Small Batch Flower is always hang dried, hand trimmed, meticulously cured, graded and then carefully hand packaged inside our premium glass jars.

Name: Countryside Cannabis - Peach Crescendo Resin'N'Terps Infused Pre-Roll - 1x1G Indica
description: Countryside's Peach Crescendo Resin'N'Terps infused pre-roll combines a THC extract with quality bud for those seeking a potent, flavour-forward product.

Name: SHRED Dessert Storm Dartz Pre-Rolls
description: Dessert Storm, which boasts big sweet, dank and spicy aromas, now comes in a convenient pack of SHRED Dartz. Tube-style pre-rolls in one handy little cardboard package. Long story short, a slim roll with fat flavour, rolled in hemp paper.

Name: COMMUNITY C/O PURPLE HILLS Jam Band Diamonds in the Rough
description: Community Diamonds in the Rough is hand-tended, sun-grown flower, infused with terpene-rich diamonds. For the first time in Canada, Community hopes to combine the two most popular cannabis formats in the country into one highly-accessible product. To craft the diamonds, our aromatic flower is preserved through flash-freezing at harvest and then concentrated through BHO extraction before time is given for the recrystallization of cannabinoids into high-potency THCA diamonds. The resulting material still expresses notes of the flower’s unique flavonoids and terpenes, offering more complete and complex flavour than standard diamonds. The diamonds are then mixed with Community flower, cultivated and harvested by a collective of independent growers who aim to deliver quality cannabis to Canadians for a sensible price. This bag is great value for the infused smoker who chooses to roll their own, pack their own. Jam Band is indica-dominant, with the flavour and aroma of sweet, funky cheese.

Name: DIVVY Blueberry Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: Straight from the pre-rolling hills of our Port Perry outdoor farm, Divvy's got you with a classic Blueberry strain in your pre-roll pack. Blueberry is an indica-dominant strain with lineage in Afghani x Thai landrace strains that has historically been an awesome outdoor grower. Juicy and heavy, this fruity cultivar is your new go-to.

Name: MTL CANNABIS Sage n' Sour Pre-Rolls
description: These all flower pre-rolls are crafted from Sage n’ Sour, a sativa-dominant cross between the pungent Sour Diesel x S.A.G.E. This strain takes its well-known Sour Diesel lineage to the next level through its unique terpenes. Sage n’ Sour is full of pungent, gassy diesel notes, with peppery, limey and cedar accents.

Name: ROILTY Queen Bee Kush Shatter
description: Put your hands up! She's beauty, she's grace, she'll punch you in the face with flavour. Roilty Queen Bee Kush Shatter is made from a classic Kush cultivar so you know it's already an icon. This indica shatter has a subtle, earthy and floral smell from the predominant terpene humulene.

The dominant terpenes are myrcene, ocimene and alpha-pinene. Grown indoors in Pointe-Claire, Quebec, we hand harvest, whole plant hang dry, hand trim, slow cure and hand package. Our pre-rolls are prepared using our top quality flower (never trim), finely ground, compacted in 109 mm wood pulp paper, natural brown cone, not bleached and non GMO, using Organic Arabica gum, with a 26 mm tip and burn white to light grey with a slow to medium burn rate. GD#3 is associated to the pheno the Ghost Drops team selected from the King Sherb pheno hunt. King Sherb is a cross between OGKB V2.1 x Blue Sherbert. It’s an indica-leaning hybrid that crosses a female GSC with a Pink Panties male. Its buds are dense, encrusted with bright white trichomes with dark green leaves and an array of beautiful purple undertones. King Sherb has a sweet yet pungent nose. Its flavour is gassy and smooth, with notes of sweet cream and citrus flavours on the exhale, followed by an earthy after taste. King Sherb makes for a relaxing yet creative session. Its aroma and flavour fill you with a sense of serenity.

Name: BROKEN COAST- Holy Grail Kush 7G
description: We’re bringing back a legendary hybrid treasure, Holy Grail Kush. Renowned for its large, resinous flower that overflows with lime, pine and diesel aromas – HGK is a Kush lover's dream. Featuring terpenes at 1-3%, its strength is not to be underestimated. Its buds are beautifully vibrant with colours ranging from deep shades of green to dark purple and silver. Dazzling fox-tailed buds with extra-large calyxes that are thickly covered with trichomes, indicative of its Kush roots, this cross of OG#18 and Kosher Kush features dominant terpenes of caryophyllene, limonene and myrcene. You’ll want to get your hands on this Kush at any cost.

Name: Ness- Ninja Fruit 510 Thread Cartridge 1G Indica

Produced in BC with local whole flower from the Fraser Valley, it has sweet grape and tropical fruit flavour from a terpene profile of caryophyllene, limonene and myrcene. -ness distillate is pulled through an advanced ethanol extraction process and does not contain added solvents, pigments, fillers or waxes. The cartridges feature No Burn Technology™ for exceptional terpene flavour retention and a proprietary ceramic core that smoothly absorbs oil for consistent vaporization and even heating. Don’t let Ninja Fruit sneak past. Explore your -ness.

Simply consume and dispose of responsibly when finished. Each vape is precisely dosed, allowing you to have control over your cannabis consumption. Our disposable vape is designed to be discreet and odourless, ensuring privacy during your vaping sessions. The minimal vapour produced quickly dissipates, leaving no lingering scent behind. We prioritize your safety and well-being. Our disposable vape undergoes thorough third party laboratory testing to ensure product purity, potency and absence of contaminants.

description: Brought to you through years of scouring the North American legacy market, now housed in our onsite tissue culture lab. Next Friday's going to bring exclusive quality cultivars to market through Next Friday Research Institute. NFRI is dedicated to bringing one-of-a-kind cultivars to market, pushing boundaries in the cultivation space and continuing to bring the consumer a full spectrum experience. We have found consumers want the options that a rotating SKU can offer but don't like the fact that most rotating SKUs are being procured from different producers and facility types with varying grow methods. Our master growers love what they do and only the best phenotypes will be selected for the NFRI SKUs. Always grown, cured, packaged and shipped by the Next Friday team. We reserve the absolute best of our genetic stock for NFRI. The first cultivar being offered is Mutant Tire Fire (GMO x Sherb Crasher). Name: Elements Ultra Thin Rice Papers - Single Wide Double Window
description:
Elements are made from natural earth friendly materials like rice and sugar without the use of harsh chemicals or burn agents. They burn with virtually zero ash except for the natural sugar gum turning into caramel as it burns. The earthly result? The best rolling paper known to man.

Each sheet is watermarked with our proprietary criss-cross watermark. This watermark helps prevent runs and allows for the smoothest and most even burn possible. Hold a sheet of Elements up to the light and you will see its beautiful watermark printed on the paper.

Elements rolling papers are 100% windmill powered. Our production for these beautiful papers takes place in a small town called Alcoy, in the mountains north of Alicante Spain. Alcoy is known as the birthplace of rolling papers (circa 1700).

Elements rolling papers are designed for the fire, and alas they burn with zero ash except for the caramel created as the sugar gum burns. This is a result of our proprietay criss-cross imprint. This special imprint helps prevent runs and maintains the smoothest burn.

Sorbetto Sunset has powerful skunky, citrus and cheesy aromas with a gassy smell from the White Caviar influence. During flowering, the plant will take on beautiful colours ranging from purple to black. This genetic was obtained by pairing two strains: the hybrid (Maddyverox x White Caviar) and Sorbetto. Sorbetto (Sunset Sherbet x Zktlz x F10 Magnum Opus) is famous for its large trichome production and strong gassy terpene profile from the Zktlz side of the cross. Selected on the fourth generation, this cut differs from its sisters due to the presence of a subtle combination of exotic fruits and candy.

Our Rotterdam n' Black dutchies are created by combining our Rotterdam indica flower with our Afghan Black indica hash. Our process ensures a balanced mixture of both flower and hash in every pull. The result is a truly unique offering at an affordable price. The perfect indica pre-roll that burns smooth and consistent from start to finish.

That flower is then crafted into hash through dry-sifting, curing and then pressing. The result is a potent concentrate in a familiar and accessible 2g pressed format. This 2 gram hash has a blonde presence due to earlier harvesting and lighter trichomes extracted through a manual solventless process. Fans of lighter hashes with a more malleable texture will love this.

Name: Dab Bods - Grape Ape Live Resin 510 Thread Cartridge Indica 1G
description: DAB Bods Grape Ape Live Resin Vape Cart – this indica leaning hybrid brings to you the bright juicy flavours of our popular Grape Ape. Sweet berry and grape are noted in the distinct flavour this vape cart produces. Pure live resin – no artificial fillers or distillate, this terpene-rich live-resin vape sauce boasts the namesake’s original flavours and aroma profiles, perfect for those who seek a pure and unfettered representation of this sought-after strain. Featuring a complex mix of cannabinoids, terpenes and flavonoids that have been extracted via hydrocarbon processing (BHO), this unique vape cart offers an experience that benefits from the synergistic abilities (entourage effect) of a true full-spectrum product. Simply put, while other carts use additives and distillates to attempt to replicate the taste and experience of popular strains, our superior live-resin carts offer the purity, potency and profile that can only be achieved with live-resin.

Bred and selected for its unique aromas and taste, you can expect intense flavours of sour strawberry candy and gassy petrol. Don’t dilly dally, get yours today.

Carmel is proud to be a BTDF Certified Organization (Botanical Terp and Distillate Free).

You’ll be tickled pink by its sweet and nutty flavour profile, mingled with a subtle touch of funky fuel aroma. GreenSeal’s pre-rolls use unbleached Dutch paper cones designed with a slim profile for a longer, smoother, more consistent burn. Name: ONO  Ono Astrono
description: Introducing Astrono (Rainbow Pie) whole dried flower, a sativa strain. Astrono is a unique strain made by crossing Grand Blueberry Pie and Zktlz. This cannabis packs a rainbow of flavours into each and every bud. Our aeroponic cultivation techniques use air and misted nutrient-rich water instead of soil, resulting in more consistent colas. With our vertical columns, each plant receives individual attention, creating a breathtaking sea of green canopy. We meticulously track more than 2,000 data points and a secret recipe to maximize cannabinoid, terpene and flavonoid expressions. Our plants are flushed before cutting to ensure a clean product. Once harvested, our sea of colas is expertly manicured and hand dried for ten days, optimizing flavour and aroma. The Astrono flower boasts a unique combination of creamy and nutty blueberry flavour accented by hints of spicy flowers. The aroma is reminiscent of freshly baked blueberry pie, with hints of creamy nuttiness and a touch of earthiness.

Name: CANNABIOMEDIC Future Island | 7g
description: Future Island is a fantastic sativa-dominant hybrid. To create this strain, Anesia breeders used their legendary Future # 1 and their amazing strain Imperium X. Future Island – an extremely potent hybrid with a fast onset. The flowering time of Future Island is  9 to 10 weeks. In that time, its buds reach an amazing size and density. The resin and yield production is excellent, up to 650 g / m² indoors and up to 1.4 kg per plant outdoors, making it one of the highest-yielding strains. To develop its full potential, it needs a lot of light, good soil and an excellent climate. Make sure that there is adequate air circulation around the buds, especially towards the end of the flowering period. Name: THE BC BUD CO. Blue Chemdawg Live Hash Rosin Cold Cured Budder
description: Outdoor grown & handcrafted on Vancouver Island, Blue Chemdawg is a cross between DJ Short’s True Blueberry x Chemdawg 91, named for its sweet lemon flavour and colour tones. From field to freezer in under 2-hours, the fresh flower is flash frozen at -30c to capture and preserve all the terpenes, cannabinoids, flavonoids, and other compounds while the plant is still “live”. Gently agitated in ice water and sieved multiple times to capture the optimally ripe resin glands sized from 45-159um, the resulting live ice (bubble) hash is freeze dried and then gradually heat pressed through a 25um filter bag. Creating an artisanal premium live hash rosin that is the purest and most true-to-plant cannabis concentrates available. Standing by The BC Bud Co’s commitment to exceptional quality, Blue Chemdawg Live Hash Rosin Cold Cured Budder is a full-spectrum, single strain & solvent-free extract that is sure to provide consumers with a premium cannabis experience – dab at the top of its class.

Each pre-roll is packed with quality dried flower and homogenized with premium distillate and the perfect amount of botanical terpenes. Dive into a Blue Dream this summer and ride the wave of the delicious flavour of blueberry with a hint of fruity vanilla aromas.

Name: TRIBAL Cuban Linx Trifecta Infused Pre-Rolls
description: Tribal Trifecta. When your journey is of the utmost importance, you equip yourself with the best gear. No fake terpenes and no distillate. Tribal Trifecta Cuban Linx Infused pre-rolls start with Cuban Linx flower that is triple infused with Cuban Linx live resin, terp sauce and THC-A diamonds. Rolled in a hemp paper and finished with a ceramic tip. Live resin, terp sauce and THC-A diamonds make the Tribal Trifecta.

Name: Pure Sunfarms - Pink Kush Indica - 3.5g
description: Pure Sunfarms’ cut of Pink Kush from BC’s Vancouver Island is a coastal relative of the legendary OG Kush. This special strain is beloved across Canada for its strong aromas, colourful flowers, and high THC potential. Beneath a thick coating of trichomes, the dense and round buds feature forest green leaves, often with a purple hue, mixed with dark amber pistils. Grown in a high-tech greenhouse in the Fraser Valley, each bud is carefully trimmed and hand-groomed, dried and cured to precise standards. Pink Kush showcases gassy aromas of white pepper, orange, butterscotch, coffee, earth, and grapefruit, the result of a rich combination of terpenes that includes caryophyllene, myrcene, humulene, bisabolol, and limonene.

Name: FOUR54 Route 66
description: Route 66, also known as Jelly Rancher, is a vibrant cross of Very Cherry x Notorious THC. It tantalizes the taste buds with a burst of sweet berries, zesty citrus, and a hint of sour apple, balanced by an earthy undertone. True to the Jelly Rancher reputation, it offers potent effects. Route 66 is a hit for those who love their cannabis with character.

Name: Pop King Pre Rolled Cones (Tropical Mango)
description: No description available

Name: Fraser Valley Weed CO - Top Crop 28g
description: Top Crop from The Original Fraser Valley Weed Co. delivers a generous ounce of quality dried flower, always 20% THC or higher. Depending on what’s fresh in the greenhouse, aromas will vary from sweet herbs to creamy citrus to fruity gas. Each bulk ounce is greenhouse-grown in abundance in BC’s finest growing region, the Fraser Valley.

Name: TRURO Sleeping With The Stars
description: Sleeping With The Stars by Truro is a potent legacy hybrid of Poison OG X Planet Purple. This special hybrid strain is based on a 20-year-old+ Poison OG line containing vintage OG Kush genetics. The flavour profile is a classic earthy diesel Kush with hints of spice and floral. Sleeping With The Stars is proudly grown on the East Coast in Truro, Nova Scotia in our state-of-the-art small batch production facility where each bud is carefully cultivated, hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cured (21-28 days) and hand packaged in recyclable aluminium cans that are purged with liquid nitrogen to preserve the dried flower quality, moisture content and terpene profile.

Name: 1964 Organic Gelato #41 | 14g
description: Gelato #41 is a legendary cultivar that comes from a cross of Thin Mint GSC x Sunset Sherbet. Known for its sweet, herbal aromas, this product is the perfect option for a seasoned consumer who's looking for a potent, flavourful cultivar. Grown in our living soil, hang dried for 14 days, cold cured and non-irradiated.

Name: COOKIES Georgia Pie | 3.5g
description: Georgia Pie is a potent hybrid strain bred by Seed Junky Genetics and is a cross between Gellati and Kush Mints. This strain is known for having a pungent aroma that smells like a fresh peach cobbler. Georgia Pie buds have striking orange hairs with trichomes that are tinted purple, orange and green.

Name: ANIMAL Orange Tsunami 510 Thread Cartridge
description: The Orange Tsunami 510 Cartridge unleashes a swirling rush of tangy orange flavours and a bright citrus aroma on exhale. Attach this high quality 510 cartridge to any compatible battery and unleash your inner ANIMAL.

Name: Orange Chronic Bong Cleaner Super Hero 16oz
description: No description available

Name: Spinach - GMO Cookies 7g Indica
description: Don’t let the name deceive you. GMO (Garlic, Mushroom, Onion) Cookies has an unmistakable sweet and savory taste and is one of the most sought-after and popular Indica strains out there. You can’t make a soup out of it, but it sure goes nicely in a bowl.

Name: PORT NORTH Full Spectrum Cold Cured Live Rosin Batter
description: Port North's Full Spectrum Cold Cured Live Rosin Batter is made with fresh press live rosin that sits in cool temperatures so the raw THCa can crystallize while the terpenes cure. Our Cold Cured Batter is a strain specific solventless hash oil made with ice water extraction methods and careful mechanical separation techniques. The cannabis is frozen directly after harvest to preserve extremely volatile terpenes found in the living plant. The trichomes are harvested during peak flower to capture the full range of naturally occurring cannabinoids and a high amount of cannabis derived terpenes. Our Full Spectrum Cold Cured Live Rosin offers a balanced between flavour and potency – made solventless with zero additives.

Name: Versus - BC Purple Kush 28G Indica
description: Versus BC Purple Kush is an indica dominant flower that delivers authentic grape flavours with sweet and earthy notes.

Name: D*GG LBS Cryptic Chronic + Lodi Dodi OG Blunts | 2-Pack

Name: TRIBAL Power Sherb Live Resin 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Motorheads! Start your engines! Fresh off the exhale of Power Sherb Vape Cart, the gasoline flavour and "high-octane" horsepower are noticeably intense from this powerful indica strain. Parent genetics are Sherb x CKS & Cream IX3, breeder is Exotic Genetics. Expect full flavour, first exhale to last thanks in part to our extraction process and premium vape hardware.

Name: STATION HOUSE Organic Black Hash Token | 2g
description: Crafted from high quality black hash powder and pressed into tokens embossed with the Station House emblem. Station House hash tokens are highly potent and rich in native terpenes full of flavour with a very smooth burn. Each hash token is scored into quarters and can be easily portioned for multiple uses. 100% solventless extracted with no added botanical terpenes or flavouring agents.

These slow-dissolving sublingual lozenges are made without animal products. For optimal sublingual/buccal absorption, suck lozenge for about 15 seconds, then hold under tongue or between cheek and gum until fully dissolved. Patent pending.

Each bowl piece features a thumb grip for comfortable handling and easy removal

Easy to clean and maintain, ensuring hassle-free smoking sessions

description: The Cryptic Blueberry vape brings a flavour like no other with a botanical terpene profile that oozes with an aroma of fresh blueberries. Featuring a 510 thread connection, medical grade stainless steel airway and a ceramic heating element.

Name: THE LEGACY MARKET AAAA | 3.5g

Drink ice cold, with a lemon wedge, or a lime wedge, or a lemon wedge AND a lime wedge, or neither... you’ll figure it out. Fun fact: You and your friends won’t need to Macgyver a sploof to enjoy! Bubble Kush is a 100% Canadian brand. Taste tested by Canadians and perfected for Canadians. Flavour, not flavor. ‘Cause our flavour includes ‘u’. Feel the Fizz.

description: Pineapple M Diamonds & Sauce is 99.9% THCa Diamonds smothered in a delectably sweet and gassy Terp Sauce that is sure to tickle your senses. We encourage our diamonds to crash slowly, keeping purity and clarity as high as we know how. We separate the Terp Sauce from the Diamonds prior to packaging to ensure each jar gets a precise ratio of each, staying true to the ratio that the plant provided.

Name: BROKEN COAST EmergenZ Pre-Rolls
description: Introducing EmergenZ, an incredibly flavourful sativa strain crossed between Orange Push Pop x Sunset Sherbet. Reaching high THC potencies, this strain is potent and delicious. Indoor grown in small batches on the West Coast, Broken Coast strives to push the limits on what craft flower can be. Experience notes of Citrus, Grapefruit and Pine in a unique format.

Name: CALI SLIMZ Watermelon Zkittlez Pre-Roll
description: Watermelon Zktlz is a sativa strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through crossing the delicious Zktlz x Watermelon strains. Watermelon Zktlz packs a mouthwatering sweet citrus and watermelon flavour into each and every earthy toke. The aroma is of earthy herbs and rich fruity citrus with a heavily sour overtone that turns slightly pungent the more the buds are burned. Watermelon Zktlz buds have heart-shaped dark olive green buds with rich purple undertones, sparse orange hairs and a coating of tiny purple-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Name: GHOST DROPS Trap Pack 14
description: Ghost Drops Trap Pack combines two different premium strains – Banana Acai Mints and Singapore Sling. Split down the middle, this bag allows you to experience a variety of flavours in one convenient assortment pack. Banana Acai Mints is a Indica cross of Banana Punch x Acai Mints. Singapore Sling is a sativa-dominant cross of Creamsicle x Tiki Cookies.

Name: STICKY GREENS Tasty Trio Multipack Infused Pre-Rolls
description: Experience three different unique infused pre-roll offerings in one pack that recreate the nostalgic flavour experience you get with every Sticky Greens vape! Sticky Greens' Disti Sticks deliver a uniquely flavoured pre-roll experience by combining high quality flower with the same distinctly flavoured distillate that customers across Canada have come to know and love. We carefully inject our high potency distillate and naturally derived terpenes into the centre of the pre-roll in order to ensure an explosion of flavour from start to finish.

Name: BOXHOT Terpedos - Velvet Grape Pre-Roll
description: Boxhot Velvet Grape Terpedos indica flavour bombs have a grape flavour with a zesty citrus accent.

Name: PURE SUNFARMS Kush God Pre-Rolls
description: A potent indica, rolled and ready. Each pre-roll is packed with Kush God, a powerful indica cross of Pink Kush x Pineapple God featuring notes of tropical fruit, grape and dairy from dominant terpenes myrcene, limonene and humulene. BC grown whole flower with no trim and no shake. Made with natural paper, each pre-roll is finished with a twisted end and packed in a recyclable carton.

Name: COLOR CANNABIS Pedro's Sweet Sativa Pre-Rolls
description:
Unique to Color, Pedro's Sweet Sativa is a proudly Canadian sativa-dominant hybrid with fluffy, trichome covered buds with very strong THC potential. Pedro’s Sweet Sativa is rich in beta-caryophyllene and pinene giving it a sweet smell with undertones of spice. The same high quality Pedro's Sweet Sativa you’ve come to expect from Color is now available already rolled for you!

These pre-rolls are perfectly packed with gently milled flower, not trim or shake, to ensure each joint contains the freshest and most flavourful cannabis possible. Color Cannabis pre-rolls use flower that has been harvested with care, dried naturally, gently milled and then rolled into the perfect size.

Color Cannabis products are grown in Southern Ontario, using state-of-the-art greenhouses.

Name: Redecan - Redees Glueberry OG Pre-Roll 10x0.4G Hybrid
description: Glueberry OG is an evenly-balanced hybrid strain characterized by bright green buds, orange pistils and frosty white trichomes. With high levels of myrcene, caryophyllene and farnesene in its terpene profile, Glueberry OG exudes a sweet, fruity and earthy aroma. Derived from crossing OG Kush x GG x Blueberry strains, this triple threat lineage has high THC levels. Now available in perfectly packed pre-rolls that are Redee to be enjoyed.

Name: 1964 Organic Super Lemon Haze
description: Super Lemon Haze by 1964 is our version of one of the most well-known sativa cultivars. Originating from a cross of Lemon Skunk and Super Silver Haze, this cultivar gives off citrusy aromas with an underlying sour tang. Grown in living soil, hang dried for 14 days, cold cured and non-irradiated.

Name: SWEET JUSTICE- OG COLA FREE

OG Cola FREE is FREE of sugar, caffeine, and calories – yet delivers the same refreshing and full-flavoured taste as our classic OG Cola, along with a fast-acting dose of 10mg THC.

Name: Jonny Chronic  | Purple Haze 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Purple Haze by Jonny Chronic is a sativa-dominant strain with 88-94% THC and minimal CBD. Made with THC distillate and botanical terpenes, Purple Haze is dominant in caryophyllene, limonene, humulene and myrcene providing a rich grape aroma. Jonny Chronic cartridges are made by Greentank and are compatible with most generic 510- threaded batteries.

Name: PURPLE HILLS - Purple Jane HTFSE 510 Thread Cartridge Indica 1g
description: Purple Hills HTFSE Carts are filled with a proprietary single-strain blend of our terpiest live resin and distillate. This reliable, accessible vape cart brings the full profile of our fresh-frozen cannabis to life. The high-potency, high-terpene extract is made from fresh-frozen flower, full of sungrown flavour. The Purple Hills farms are located in Creemore, Ontario, in the heart of Ontario's Greenbelt. Purple Hills genetics are selected to thrive outdoors in the Creemore microclimate and are hand-tended throughout the season by a small and dedicated team. The terpene-rich, aromatic flower is preserved through flash-freezing at harvest and then concentrated through hydrocarbon extraction. The resulting live resin contains all of the flower’s sun-expressed flavonoids, terpenes and cannabinoids, packing a more complete and complex cannabis flavour than CO2 or ethanol extracts. Purple Jane is sweet and earthy with hints of grape.

Name: ENDGAME The Gas Pack
description: The Endgame crew is always on the hunt for fire strains. They're hunters not growers. While looking for cannabis to extract, they often find fire that the people need to see. This rotating single strain offering will always be gassy fire. Strains may change but they'll always be listed on the bag and consistently fire.

Name: Back Forty - Mandarin Cookies 7g
description: Life's a little sweeter in the back forty and you won't want to wait for dessert to give our Mandarin Cookies a try! This sativa-dominant banger pulls a tangy citrus flavour with a hint of sweet nuttiness on the exhale. A cross of the classic CKS strain and Mandarin Sunset with some major limonene. Packaged in a resealable foil pouch to make sure that it stays fresh for the long haul, take a trip and explore the Back Forty.

Name: CARMEL- Rares Pre-Rolls
description: Top-shelf flower always start with a pheno hunt, where untold hours are spent popping seeds in the pursuit of finding a unicorn. Rares features a rotation of limited drops grown by our partner craft growers and hand selected by our Master Grower.

Name: BC WEED CO. Joker Juice
description: This particular cut from First Blood Genetics brings together a roster of champions. Jealousy, ICC, Gummiez and Grape Gas are all found in its lineage. These dense purple buds have a sweet candy grape note that first greets the palate and follows through with fuel and chemicals to complete. Nitrogen flushed and canned for terpene preservation.

Name: 1964 Tropical Punch Live Rosin Gummies
description: Quick-onset soft chews made without animal products using full spectrum live rosin. A splash of fruity tropical punch flavour perfectly paired with complimentary single strain live rosin to create a superior experience.

Name: Ghost Drops | Rotational 2 Jar | Donny Burger
description: Ghost Drops offers a wide selection of expertly curated legacy cannabis. Fresh drops of premium genetics hunted by the best, award-winning geneticists, grown by several ultra-premium, hand selected, and vetted craft micro-producers. Every jar features small batch, hand trimmed, hang dried, craft cannabis.

Name: FULL SESH LA RNTZ
description: LA RNTZ is an alluring cannabis strain with visually captivating small to medium-sized buds displaying vibrant shades of green complemented by fiery orange pistils and a generous coat of trichomes. Its touch reveals a sticky and resinous texture, indicative of its high trichome content. The strain's aroma is a blend of sweet, fruity notes reminiscent of berries and tropical fruits, coupled with a hint of citrus and earthiness. LA RNTZ’s flavour profile mirrors its scent, delivering a delightful burst of fruity sweetness with a subtle creaminess, followed by a hint of earthiness and spice upon exhale. The smoke is smooth, making it suitable for cannabis enthusiasts of all levels, offering a flavourful experience.

Name: CARE BY DESIGN Mango Raspberry Relax 10:1 Vegan Soft Chews
description: Introducing Mango Raspberry Relax soft chews by Care By Design. Our soft chews are infused with a potent blend of CBD and THC, making them ideal for those looking to experience the benefits of both cannabinoids. These delicious soft chews are made without animal products or gluten and come in a mouth-watering mango raspberry flavour that will transport you to your favourite sunny beach with every bite. Each piece contains 22 mg of broad-spectrum cannabinoids, providing a precisely dosed, consistent and delicious way to consume cannabis. Our soft chews are made with high-quality ingredients and are lab-tested for purity and potency. Plus, with their convenient packaging, you can take them with you wherever you go.

It's got everything you want with all your favourite tropical fruits in one.

description: This pre-roll features Electric Grapefruit, a potent sativa cross of the legendary Acapulco Gold and Grapefruit Tangie. The dark green buds offer complex aromas of citrus, tangy candy and tropical blooms. Ground from small batches, hang-dried and hand-detailed whole flower, this classic cone style pre-roll is finished with a Dutch crown for a smooth and even burn.

Name: PLUSH Taro Milk Tea Full Spectrum Vegan Soft Chews

Name: PAPA'S HERB HYBRID BLUEBERRY ZLSHIE 510 THREAD CARTRIDGE (1G)
description: Papa's Blueberry Zlshie is a hybrid cross of Blue Sherbet, Blue Cookies and Sunset Sherbet in a 510 vape cart. It tastes like blue raspberry with earthy undertones. The aroma is fruity and sweet.

Name: OUEST - Gelatti Kush 7G Sativa
description: Cookies and Cream x Secret Weapon bring you Oreoz, a potent indica leaning hybrid. Caked in sparkly trichomes, this stunning strain is a feast for the eyes and the taste buds. Rich flavours of chocolatey sweetness and punches of diesel make this terpene-rich delight one you'll keep dipping into.

Name: UP- Pine Kosher Kush Pre-Roll Indica 3X0.5G
description: No description available

Name: SAN RAFAEL '71 Sourdough
description: Sourdough by San Rafael ’71 is a high-THC strain, bred from Cake and Diesel genetics. Sourdough carries very interesting sour, cake, and gasoline notes from primary terpenes, Myrcene and Caryophyllene. An indica strain with completely unique and proprietary genetics, Sourdough is the result from two years of screening thousands of genetics.

Name: 1809 UNDERGROUND Rntz Punch Pre-Rolls | 5-Pack
description: A carefully crafted cannabis strain, that is dried using our Cryo Cure technology takes the essence of its parent strains and amplifies it into a symphony of flavour, aroma, and effects. Born from the crossing of two potent strains, the Soap x Red Velvet Rntz, Rntz Punch offers a harmonious blend of potency and palatability. The buds are dense and compact, showcasing an array of colours ranging from deep purples to vibrant greens, accented by orange pistils and a frosty blanket of trichomes. Rntz Punch delivers on every front, starting with its aroma. As soon as you crack open a jar, you're greeted by a burst of dankness. Notes of earth tones, and candy dance together in perfect harmony. Rntz Punch packs potency in terms of effects as well.

Name: ENDGAME The Za
description: The Za is that fire you've been looking for. We looked through many packs and met a lot of growers before we found "The Za". Whole plant, indoor grown, hang-dried and expertly cured.

Name: COMMON GROUND Northern Lights Pre-Rolls | 5-Pack
description: Northern lights is a popular Indica-dominant strain originating in the 1980's. This sought after legacy cultivar is coated with frosty trichomes and dark orange hairs and is known for oozing with resin and earthy/floral notes. Carefully cured, rolled and packaged for a truly enjoyable experience.

Name: Simply Bare - BC Organic Lime Mi'jito Sativa 3.5G
description: Our BC Lime Mi'jito is a sativa-leaning flower that is a cross of the Limegerian x Orange Blossom Trail cultivars. The strong lime aromas are complemented by floral and earthy undertones. Grown in living soil, hang dried for 14 days, cold cured and non irradiated.

Name: Terra Labs - Lemon Heads Organic 3.5g
description: Introducting a bright and citrusy strain, Lemon Heads. Fresh sativa dominant strain pops with lemon notes and flavour. Premium flower, grown indoors and infused with single strain sourced diamonds.

Name: NORTHBOUND CANNABIS StrawMelon Smasher 510 Thread Cartridge
description: High in THC, The Northbound StrawMelon Smasher 510 vape cartridge skillfully blends your favourite fruit flavours with botanical terpenes, resulting in a smooth and delightful strawberry and watermelon product. This unique combination of custom THC distillate and botanical terpenes delivers a sweet inhale, followed by a creamy, crumbly and fruity exhale. Inspired by the crossing of Strawberry Shortcake and Watermelon OG cultivars. Made with a hemp-based mouthpiece and packaged in mylar bags made from more than 40% post-consumer materials.

Name: BUD LAFLEUR Moby Dick | 3.5g
description: Moby Dick is a sativa-dominant strain with a strong THC potency potential made by crossing Haze x White Widow. Moby Dick delivers a pine and citrus-forward flavour profile. Grown indoors in Pointe-Claire, Quebec, we hand harvest, hang dry, hand trim and slow cure.

Name: TRURO Jealousy x Apples & Bananas Pre-Roll
description: Jealousy x Apples & Bananas pre-rolls by Truro Cannabis are a potent legacy indica dominant hybrid. Jealousy is a 50/50 hybrid strain produced by crossing Sherbet Bx1 with Gelato 41. Compound Genetics and Cookies collaborated to create Apples & Bananas, a combination of a Platinum Cookies and Granddaddy Purple hybrid with a Blue Power male. They crossed the resulting hybrid with Gelatti to create Apples & Bananas. The flavour profile is earthy and gassy with hints of spice. Jealousy x Apples & Bananas pre-rolls are produced from the whole flower of our batches and we have refined our mixing and milling processes to mirror the high quality and THC levels of our popular whole flower products. All Truro pre-rolls are hand weighed and hand packaged in 100% recyclable tubes.

Name: JUICY JAYS- Terp-Enhanced Cherry Pie Hemp Wraps 2 Sheets
description: No description available

Name: Liiv - G&C Pre-Roll
description: It’s officially in Canada! Fan-favourite Grapes and Cream has landed. This well-known high potency Cali dessert strain from Cannarado is a recognizable hybrid of Grape Pie x Cookies & Cream, offering sweet moorish fruit and cream aromas. But don’t be surprised by liiv G&C’s kushy punch among the cake and cookie profiles. True to its name, this first-gen grape strain has bright, round, dense grape-like purple buds.

Name: D*GG LBS Juicy OooWeee AIO Vape
description: The Juicy OooWeee vape is a multi-flavoured fruit experience. Expect juicy pineapple, vibrant orange, banana and lemon flavours. This premium unit is made of medical grade stainless steel. This flavourful distillate formulation is offered in a high potency with a focus on a fruity profile.

Name: FIGR Go Play Coastal Sage Pre-Roll
description: Go Play Coastal Sage is a sativa-dominant strain which comes from the fan favourite Zeta Sage crossed with the pungent Sour Diesel. With almond-shaped buds and a mossy green colour, the strain stays true to its name with a sage-forward flavour. The unique terpenes, terpinolene and ocimene produce a sweet, piney and earthy taste, followed by herbal and citrus notes thanks to linalool and limonene. This strain yields potent, terpene-rich buds that are also high in CBG. FIGR pre-rolls are expertly rolled with a paper filter and conical shape for a smooth, consistent smoke. Coastal Sage features a potent THC range. The trimming process utilizes a combination of automatic and hand trimming; the buds are then dried in our state-of-the-art, purpose-built drying rooms.

Name: PALMETTO Pink Burst & Melonberry Ice Dual Chamber AIO
description: Get ready for a choose-your-own flavour adventure with Palmetto's Pink Burst & Melonberry Ice 3-in-1 Disposable Vape. The Palmetto 3-in-1 Disposable Vape lets you effortlessly switch between flavours. Unwrap a sweet strawberry-lemon flavour explosion with Pink Burst, or dive into the cool Melonberry Ice, a delightful mix of minty-melon and red berries. Craving a fresh flavour destination? Create your very own unique blend by mixing the flavours together with a single pull, delivering a one-of-a-kind flavour adventure every time. Indulge in the fruity tartness and sweet and sour aroma from the dominant caryophyllene, limonene, ocimene and bisabolol terpenes. Sporting dense tight buds, this potent strain achieves remarkably high THC potency. This expression of Animal Rntz is improved through conscientious care and attention given to each plant through every stage of growth process. Harvested at its peak, expertly cured and hand trimmed to ensure the highest level of quality.

Name: NAKED MUMMER Cactus Breath Pre-Rolls | 5-pack
description: Cactus Breath features large, crystalline flowers with dark green and purple hues and distinct orange pistils. Unparalleled trichome presence makes this flower an exceptional candidate for solventless extraction techniques. Fresh herbal aroma with undertones of gas and spice. Noteworthy terpene profile is dominated by terpinolene and supported by caryophyllene, farnesene and myrcene. Sativa-dominant hybrid bred by ThugPug Genetics, a cross between Cactus x Mendo Breath 2. This cultivar is unique to Atlantic Cultivation, pheno-hunted by our founder. Grown in our indoor, purpose-built facility under HPS lighting using Athena nutrients in our hydroponic system. After a one-week flush, whole plants are harvested by hand and hung to dry for 2 weeks. Flower is then cured, trimmed, and carefully de-stemmed. Pre-rolls are made from milled flower and finished by hand with a crown fold.

Name: TENZO Prima Rose Infused Pre-Roll

Bred by Deep East in California, Studio 54 got its name from being the 54th pheno of a breeding project that crossed Pink Guava x Sunset Sherbert. Large dense spear shaped buds feature deep purple marbling and orange hairs. With this highly potent strain, expect bold flavours of guava, fuel and a little sherb. Because it’s the right thing to do, all of our flower is hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cold cured, and hand packaged. We believe fresh and terpy is best, so all our flower is packaged in a nitrogen flushed pouch with a humidity pack. Non irradiated, obviously.

description: Atomik Sour Haze is the newest addition to Original Stash's line of high-quality cannabis products. Atomik Sour Haze has a pungent citrus aroma thanks to the unique terpene profile of terpinolene, farnesene and caryophyllene.

Name: TOP LEAF Donkey Butter
description: Donkey Butter is an elusive indica with very strong THC potency. Its robust and pungent flavours are a fusion of spicy skunk and diesel-infused pine derived from its Grease Monkey lineage. Top Leaf prides itself on carefully crafted cannabis cultivars with rich full-bodied flavour and complex terpene profiles grown to exacting standards.

Name: LITTI Sunrise Smash 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Introducing Litti's Sunrise Smash 510 thread cartridge THC vape, with the fusion of sweet strawberry and tropical mango flavours. This vape cartridge is compatible with 510 thread batteries for convenient use.

Name: BIG Black Hash
description: Big Black Hash is a hash lover’s dream. The hash is carefully pressed and cured to produce an Afghani style hash by one of Quebec’s leading hash makers. In a pre-roll or a bowl with your favourite flower or on its own if you love hash.

Name: SITKA MICRO COLLECTION - Strawberry Lemonade Pre-Roll Sativa 3x0.5g
description: Micro Producer KnL Cannabis did what they do best -- bring out the flavour! And they do an incredible job with their Strawberry Lemonade. This cross between Sour Lemon OG and Strawberry Cough provides a wonderful scent of strawberries, sour lemon and other fresh citrus fruits. It has a flavour of fresh sweet strawberries and zest of lemons. KnL's small batch crops allow them to really focus on the terpenes and flavour profiles for which they have become well-known. Each cone is carefully packed by our team to ensure you get the experience you deserve.

Name: NUGZ Galactic Burger Infused Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: Tribal Galactic Burger Infused Pre-Rolls. Open the package and you'd swear that you could put these in your vehicles gas tank and it'd work. Galactic Burger Infused Pre-Rolls are a blend of two of our most potent stains for effects and aromas (Galactic Runtz x Triple Burger), we first mill down whole buds to a precise consistency. Then we mix the strains together, add in BHO produced from each strain and roll them up in a convenient pre-roll.

Name: TWEED Tiger Cake | 14g
description: Tweed Tiger cake is a hybrid strain with high THC and minimal amounts of CBD. Tiger cake comes from a cross of Layer Cake and Menthol. Its buds are known to be an intense green with heavy hints of orange and dense trichome coverage. Some associate vanilla, diesel and minty flavours with the Tweed Tiger Cake strain.

Name: BACK FORTY Wedding Pie | 3.5g
description: Wedding Pie is the marriage of Wedding Cake x Grape Pie. This indica can reach high potencies of THC and boasts a terpene content of up to 2.89%. Plenty of caryophyllene, linalool, limonene and bisabolol make these vibrant green buds rich with a spicy, cracked pepper flavour. Packaged in a resealable foil pouch to make sure that it stays fresh for the long haul, take a trip and explore the Back Forty.

Name: CODEWORD CANNABIS Money In The Bank
description: A robust and distinct flavour profile that includes melons, warm vanilla and almond. Terpenes include limonene, linalool, and caryophyllene. This strain pulls in a distinct nutty aroma, underscored by a soothing lavender finish.

Name: ROSIN HEADS Hash Rosin Coins - Caramel Coffee Crunch
description: Introducing our Hash Rosin Coin Caramel Coffee Crunch. A blend of sweet caramel chocolate infused with rich coffee flavour and a wafer cookie crunch. Infused with 10 mg of strain specific hash rosin.

Name: DBZ Metal Rolling Tray
description: No description available

Name: KRONIC The Authentic Diamond & Terpene Infused Blunt
description: This hand rolled blunt combines whole flower buds with finely crushed THCA diamonds. Our craft flower is expertly wrapped in a terpene-infused hemp wrap, chosen to capture the authentic blunt experience. Every blunt is hand crafted with a glass filter tucked inside. You’ll want to get a photo of this as soon as you get it in your hands.

Name: Community | Archives 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Community Archives 510 cartridges deliver classic flavours in an accessible, reliable and affordable format. Community flower is cultivated and harvested by a collective of independent growers who aim to deliver great cannabis to Canadians for a sensible price – with CO2 extraction, that flower is converted to fill our 510 format carts with smooth distillate that draws a clean hit from start to finish. Chemdawg took the long, strange trip from a Grateful Dead concert parking lot to almost every cannabis market in the world over the last three decades. Community now offers this memorable flavour in a modern way for consumers across Canada!

Name: DISQ Giggling Grape Disposable Vape
description: THC, terpenes and technology. Savour the discreet and dependable DISQ disposable vapes. Starting with our THC distillate rich with cannabinoid terpenes, we then infuse our recipe with deep, rich and flavourful botanical terpenes. Our innovative DISQ technology ensures a consistent vaping experience, eliminating clogging, leaking and dry hits.

Name: Versus- Slugger Kief+Distillate Infused BC Purple Kush Pre-Roll	 1X1G
description: Sluggers are infused with cannabis extract and kief. Made with BC Purple Kush, an indica-dominant flower delivering authentic grape flavour with sweet and earthy notes.

Name: Raw Black Organic Hemp King Size Slim Rolling Paper
description: No description available

Name: J.R. STRAIN Wagyu Pink | 7g
description: Pink Kush – carefully crafted into our finest version, this baby produces hand grenades of dense, sticky flowers shimmering with trichomes, purple and dark green. Great smoke, Wagyu Pink will handle the job.

Name: FLYTE Balla Berry All-In-One Vape
description:
Take off with Flyte's Balla Berry disposable. Picture a fusion of blueberry, grape and zesty blue raspberry, delivering a sweet and tangy blend.

Balla Berry is made using high potency distillate and natural terpenes for a smooth vape. Just like Smashin’ Passion, it’s designed for simplicity and reliability, including a rechargeable feature. No button, no refills.

Name: Melt - Honey Woo Tang - Hybrid 3.5g
description: Honey Woo Tang is an anomaly. It’s unexpected. It’s alluring flavour of sweet honey ends with grape kung-fu punch to the taste buds. Its aroma fills the room with a tangy grape scent. Small batch and hand harvested.

Name: NOYA Craft Cut
description: Cultivating unique genetics from the cookies family, our craft cut bags allow us use unique phenotypes to consistently offer a newer taste to the consumer. The focus for this SKU will be around sativa dominant strains offering non-existent genetics in the industry and always bringing new flavours.

Name: EASTCANN Mango Sour
description: Mango Sour is a high THC sativa dominant hybrid of Citradelic Sunset x Mango Sour. This potent sativa has a distinct citrus and mango flavour profile. Mango Sour buds are dense with beautiful frosty trichomes. Mango Sour is grown in small batches in living soil. Mango Sour is packaged in a can using a purge of liquid nitrogen and a hermetic seal to maintain freshness. All EastCann flower is grown using craft practices.

Name: BOXHOT 1000 Retro Rocket Fuel 510 Thread Cartridge
description: BOXHOT Retro presents Rocket Fuel, a 510-threaded vape boasting a 1,000 mg of THC and some of the purest cannabis distillate available on the market. Fill your tank full of retro summertime flavour with a powerful blue raspberry and cherry blast, and a hit of bright citrus. All BOXHOT vapes are manufactured with exclusive, oversized hardware, making them optimized for big and full hits. Better yet, all BOXHOT vapes are produced with industry-leading CO2 extraction and refining processes, and feature an entourage of expertly infused premium strain-specific terpenes.

Name: Raw Classic Connoisseur KS Slim Rolling Papers and Tips
description:
Raw Classic Connoisseur KS Slim Rolling Papers and Tips comes with 32 leaves and tips each. These classic RAW papers offer unmatched, unrefined cleanliness to your smoke sessions– no more worrying about additives or dyes!  Each pack includes tips for added smoking filtration and patented run-preventing watermark system that allows slow, smooth burns.

- 32 leaves and tips each
Pure, clean tasting smoke that is best described as natural, light and pure
It contains a hybrid blend of unbleached (not chlorine whitened) fibers, the paper is a translucent natural light brown color.
Exclusive cross pattern watermark, which minimizes runs and odd burning of the papers for a more even burning smoking experience.
All Natural, Additive-Free, 100% Vegan
Translucent Ultra Thin Rolling Paper
Raw papers are made of pure Hemp Paper and Hemp Natural Gum!
