description: Petrolcan is a BC-grown, gassed-up sativa hybrid crafted by Tantalus Labs. It’s a cross also known as Chem de la Chem, consisting of the legendary Chemdawg and I-95, known for its high-octane potency. Rising to notoriety in the early 90s, Chemdawg has become a favoured parent for breeding powerful strains. Petrocan lives up to its name as a notably sticky flower that has a subtly sweet yet unique fuel aroma with spicy and herbal undertones.

Name: 9" Hemper Spotted Egg XL Bong
description:
Embrace the holiday spirit with the "9" Hemper Spotted Egg XL Bong", a festive addition to your collection. Standing tall at 9 inches, this bong features assorted color decals on its body, adding a touch of whimsy to your smoking sessions. The highlight of this piece is the large showerhead percolator, ensuring clean and smooth bowl packs every time. Available in a variety of colors, you're sure to find one that suits your style!

Height: 9 inches
Diameter: 4 inches

Thickness: 5mm for durability and stability

Name: PISTOL AND PARIS Hawaiian Fanta
description: A Compound Genetics strain packing a sweet and fruity punch into a sour lemon candy taste. Enjoy these pungent, tangy flavours and smooth pineapple soda aromas. The bud structure is medium to slightly larger size buds of average density. Lighter green in colour with faint purple highlights, illuminated in trichomes. The flavour is sweet tropical fruit, with a sour tang finish, while the aroma has an uniquely similar nose and taste, bursting with a prominent pineapple zest and sweet aromatics of tropical fruit.

description: Get great value without sacrificing flavour or potency with Muskoka Grown's Onion Ringz. This high THC indica leaning hybrid delivers a classic garlic and gas aroma. We fill each pouch by hand to ensure you only get the best buds and seal the bag with nitrogen to ensure a fresh and terpene-rich experience. Onion Ringz is not irradiated.

description: This delicious strain packs potency with a mouth-watering fusion of sweet fruit flavours, citrus and a subtle hint of gas. Cosmic Fuel's buds are dense and covered in a thick layer of resin, with a sparkling trichome coating that looks like a galaxy of stars.

description: Let your imagination run wild with Back Forty’s latest cultivar – Liquid Imagination. A cross between Blue Zktlz x Jet Fuel Gelato, this potent hybrid boasts rich dark green buds adorned with orange pistils and chock-full of trichomes. With a flavour profile that blends sweetness with a pinch of gas, Liquid Imagination is a real treat for your senses.

Flower that has been sungrown and rain watered which promotes better and more varied terpenes (meaning more flavour and entourage effect for you) and given a slow, steady cure for a deeper, richer experience. description: True OG Pre-Rolls from Truro Cannabis are produced from the whole flower of our popular True OG craft cultivar – a high THC unique indica-dominant hybrid cross of True OG x Kush Mints 11 with a spicy, gassy profile with hints of citrus. True OG Pre-Rolls are produced from the whole flower of our best-in-class batches, and we have refined our mixing and milling processes to mirror the high quality and THC levels of our popular whole flower products. description: Max Yields of 3rd Coast Genetics is celebrated for their mastery in crafting top-tier cannabis strains. Name: WANA Quick Orchard Peach Sativa
description: Wana Quick Orchard Peach fast-acting  soft chews are ripe with juicy peach flavour and infused with a sativa THC distillate. These quick onset and offset soft chews are smoke-free. Terpene-infused, made without animal products.

Name: Buddy Blooms – 2 x Big Buddy Sativa Pre-Roll – 2x1g
description: Buddy Blooms presents the lil Buddy sativa, quality and high THC flower, mirroring the roll you'd meticulously craft for yourself. Except this time, we've done the rolling for you. Get the convenience of expertly crafted sativa pre-rolls without the effort. Buddy Blooms, where quality meets convenience.

Name: COMMON GROUND Sour Marg Pre-Rolls | 5-Pack
description: Sour Marg is a unique cross of the renowned Sour Tangie and Dagwood. This sativa dominant cross has frosty and dense buds that are popping with heavy citrusy flavour arising from the high limonene content. Floral and herbal notes finish off the experience. Our pre-rolls come from sun-grown cannabis that is carefully trimmed and evenly ground for a consistent rolling experience.

Name: SOAR Confetti Cloudz Infused Blunt
description: Our Confetti Cloudz infused blunt is a potent combination of cannabis oil and a sweet mix of cream and vanilla flavours. This kief coated infused blunt from Soar’s Collection is potent and aromatic. Ground from a small batch, hang dried whole flower, this classic cone style blunt is finished with a Dutch crown for a smooth and even burn.

Name: Versus - Quarter Mill Black Mountain Skunk Indica 7g
description: Versus Quarter Mill Black Mountain Skunk is an indica-dominant milled flower that delivers great quality and potency at a killer price.

Name: THE HASH ORDER Legacy Reserve Hashish (1-Year Aged)
description: Indulge in the ultimate sensory experience with The Hash Order’s Legacy Reserve Hashish (1-Year Aged) – an artisanal blend that has been carefully crafted using traditional techniques taught by hashish artisans for generations. This premium hashish has been aged for a minimum of one year under dark conditions with strict temperature and humidity controls resulting in an intense and complex flavour profile that is gas-dominant with aged “hashene” flavours on top of a sweet and buttery roasted undertone that lingers on with the effects. Don’t settle for ordinary hashish – elevate your senses and experience the The Legacy Reserve Hashish. Total Cannabinoid Content: >70% | Total Terpene Content: >10% | Hash Micron: 45µ-159µ

Name: Divvy- Cropped Sativa Harvest 14G
description: Already milled and ready to roll… or vape… or pack a bowl. Divvy’s sativa-dominant flower is available in bulk bags containing gently ground from whole flower.

Name: 7ACRES- Papaya Whole Flower Pre-Rolled Infused Joints Indica 1X1G
description: No description available

Name: EARTHWOLF FARMS Afghan Hash
description: Our Afghan Hash is a modern take on the traditional classic.  We use only live ice water hash, heated and homogenized to make the perfect consistency. With a soft and pliable texture, this hash is a delicious full spectrum concentrate made from sun grown cannabis.

Name: Shatterizer - White Widow Shatter 1g hybrid
description: White Widow is a hybrid strain that’s global in nature and famous with deep historic roots. This cross between a Brazilian Sativa and South Indian Indica, is renown for resinous white sticky crystally fluffy buds and tantalizing trichomes. Sourced from our friends with a dense delicious harvest, our White Widow cannabis was extracted into a glimmering shiny shatter. Preserving clusters of trichomes with our proprietary hydrocarbon blend and using the highest scientific processes, become entangled in the terpenes and get caught in webs of flavour.

Name: AR.GO Dilemma Pre-Rolls | 10-Pack
description: We all face dilemmas daily, so let us handle this one. Welcome to Ar.go Dilemma, a multipack of pre-rolls for fruity strain lovers. This pack of pre-rolls contains two rotating fruity strains. These Ar.go Dilemma packs will generally contain two sativa dominant strains, giving you two great options to pick from. The cultivars found in Dilemma will typically be dominant in terpinolene, pinene and caryophyllene terpenes. Dilemma is special to our hearts. When you purchase Dilemma, you’re supporting us and one of our micro-cultivators.

Name: PRIMEAU CRAFT CANNABIS Lava Cake
description: Lava Cake is indica dominant with a very strong THC potential. This strain is cultivated using coco-coir and without the use of pesticides. Plants are flushed for an extensive period with artesian water and then harvested as whole plants, hang dried, hand trimmed and hand packaged. Meticulously hunted and selectively bred. Rock-solid buds are coated in thick layers of rich trichomes.

Name: 14G Simply Bare  BC ORGANIC DUCT TAPE
description: No description available

Name: WAGNERS Pink Bubba Pocket Rocket Infused Pre-Rolls
description: Our popular Pink Bubba pre-rolls are well-known for their quality, flavour and smooth smoke. WAGNERS has given these favourites an extra kick by infusing our milled whole flower for a taste sensation.

Name: JONNY CHRONIC- Reefer-Ready Indiana Bubblegum 7G
description: Reefer-Ready Indiana Bubblegum is a high THC indica strain landrace. Grown in small batches, every plant is hang-dried, trimmed and milled to the perfect consistency. Indiana Bubblegum has a berry and cherry aroma due to its unique terpene profile.

Name: RIFF BOOST Tropical Burst
description: Tropical Burst is a kick in a can with bold tropical punch and sweet berry flavours. Get hit with a Hawaiian haymaker in a cannabis drink that’s infused with 10mg each of nano-emulsified THC and CBG, 30mg of caffeine and guarana and ginseng extract for extra potency. Crafted for maximum taste and zero cannabis aftertaste. Spark something new with RIFF BOOST cannabis-infused energy drinks.

Name: MTL CANNABIS Jungl' Cake Pre-Rolls | 7-Pack
description: These Jungl' Cake buds are lime green with thin deep orange hairs and a coating of frosty white crystal trichomes. The flavour is sweet with notes of pastry dough, creamy marshmallow and cashews. The aroma is earthy and nutty with a sweet fruity overtone that's both sugary and spicy.

Name: DOUBLE JOINTED SFV OG Kush - Luxury Handcrafted Straight Joints
description: Finest single strain whole buds SFV OG Kush input, 2.2% of 177 terpenes, slow burning eco-conscious hemp paper, premium hollow filter, truly hand-craft, grown with music in happy environments… When you smoke these pre-rolls, you are smoking cannabis only. Premium hollow filters provide full-bodied world class smoking experiences. The smooth of smoking, slow burning and white ash are the indicators of purity and quality. San Fernando Valley OG Kush selected from our 498 candidates of large pheno hunt to Cali Connection's OG Kush for the highest resin content. The smell and taste are gas, fuel and lemon terpenes. Created with love by our world class passionate breeder and grower as well as a pickiest smoker, these pre-rolls are setting a new highest standard for premium craft cannabis pre-rolls for all pre-roll lovers.

Name: NUGZ Indica
description: What's better than tearing into a fresh sack of beautiful big buds? This is a sack packed with only the best buds we can offer. Nugz Indica, a rotating offering of indica strains from our rare genetics library. You can expect strains like Gelato Mint, Triple Burger, Drip Station, Galactic Rntz, Slapz, and new drops! Get in, get out, get Nugz!

For flavour, Flamingo is a perfect representation of her parents, expect lots of gas, a little musk and that classic kush flavour we all love. Because it’s the right thing to do, all of our flower is hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cold cured, and hand packaged. We believe fresh and terpy is best, so all our flower is packaged in a nitrogen flushed pouch with a humidity pack. Non-irradiated, obviously.

Name: ORCHID CBD CBD Runtz Pre-Rolls | 5-Pack
description: Orchid's CBD Runtz pre-rolls are produced with nothing but hang-dried, slow-cured whole buds which have been consistently ground, and wrapped in premium RAW organic hemp cones. Enjoy five pre-rolls packaged in eco-friendly tin tubes. CBD Runtz is a sativa-hybrid strain. Its lush green, high-quality buds are generously covered in light orange pistils and resinous, surprisingly sticky trichomes. CBD Runtz contains a deliciously sweet, floral aroma and wonderfully diverse terpene profile that is full of myrcene, caryophyllene, limonene and much more.

Name: HiWay - Fast Lane Sativa - 28g

Name: PHANT Diamond Infused Pre-Roll
description: Our Diamond Infused pre-roll is a balanced infusion. With a potent THC content and natural terpenes, the infusion is extremely pleasant to taste and smell. It is rolled in a manner designed to allow air flow through the pre-roll while smoking it. Our "Burn Right" technology allows the pre-roll to burn evenly and gives the user the ability to draw on the pre-roll without it clogging. This product is a breakthrough for infused pre-rolls.

description: Ponderosa Pine by San Rafael ’71 is a premium, indoor-grown flower that was exclusively bred for San Rafael '71 from rare genetics. A high-THC indica, Ponderosa Pine hits with a medley of dough, pine and diesel notes. Ponderosa Pine’s eye-catching buds display a vibrant palette of royal green and bright violet hues and blanketed in frosty trichomes for an unforgettable first impression. Ponderosa Pine is hang-dried, hand-finished and carefully hand-bottled with an included humidity pack.

Our proprietary extraction process allows us to produce a full plant product while preserving the plant's distinctive earthy notes, subtle flavours and all of its natural properties without the need for added terpenes, flavours or carrier oil. This results in a product that fully embodies the strain specific benefits unavailable in a formulated distillate product housed in high quality rechargeable hardware. Understand the process, know the ingredients and demand the best.

These pre-rolls are perfectly packed with gently milled flower, not trim or shake, to ensure each pre-roll contains the freshest and most flavourful cannabis possible. Our meticulous growing practices, including full temperature and humidity control and hand-trimming, ensure a consistent and enjoyable smoking experience. Try Color's Mint Cookies Kush today and discover the difference in quality and flavour.

Its flavour is gassy and smooth, with notes of sweet cream and citrus flavours on the exhale, followed by an earthy after taste. King Sherb makes for a relaxing yet creative session. The thick buds are overwhelmed with deep orange hairs, dapples of purple, and thickly blanketed in milky trichomes. This potent and terpy indica is cultivated with meticulous care, ensuring each small batch meets the highest standards. Grown in a controlled indoor environment, the plants are nurtured in strain-specific conditions to optimize their potential. The buds are inspected for purity and carefully hand-trimmed.

Owen, Artisanal’s Master Grower, hand-picked this Sour Tangie phenotype and immediately knew he found a keeper. He's cultivated it with careful intent ever since in order to preserve the genetic integrity and stabilize its key features, but most importantly, to serve as a reminder to the market of what a classic, well-balanced sativa strain should look, smell and smoke like. Artisanal is a next generation, grower-centric cannabis company with a proven track record of cultivating exceptional cannabis in the legacy market, small craft-style grows and large licensed facilities. We've partnered with licensed producer Abba Medix, and we cultivate our premium genetics within the Abba Medix facility.

AUTO DRAW VAPE PEN BATTERY
The M3 is an evolution of CCELL's quality and compact vaporizer batteries that combine performance and function in one sleek design. The M3 comes with all symbolic CCELL features, such as a button-free profile, a discreet breathing indicator, a micro-USB charging port, inhale-activated, and an aluminum alloy housing which offers a sophisticated aesthetic. The magnetic connector is compatible with 510-thread cartridges, and creates an easy-to-use system. With a battery capacity of 350mAh, this stick vaporizer battery can generate 25% more vapor volume when compared to other brands. It is recommended to use the M3 with CCELL cartridges to achieve maximum flavour, performance, and potency.

Name: SHATTERIZER- MK ULTRA SHATTER INDICA
description: Shatterizer’s MK Ultra Shatter is an indica with an OG Kush and G-13 strain lineage that is full in taste and texture. This shatter has a very strong THC potency potential and is extracted to perfection using a proprietary hydrocarbon blend. The natural terpene profiles are perfectly preserved through the delicate and precise control of temperature throughout the extraction process. Specially sourced and selected from the finest growers across Canada, we look for flower with the right characteristics, from THC levels to terpenes and flavonoids. All Shatterizer extracts are made with love in Ontario, using the highest-levels of science, tech and quality extraction methods. Please enjoy responsibly.

Name: -NESS Ninja Fruit Infused Pre-Roll
description: A limited release for 420, Ninja Fruit from -ness™ takes a new form in a terpene and THC distillate infused pre-roll. With very strong THC potency potential, this hybrid pre-roll also offers enhanced flavour with added terpenes to boost its sweet grape, tropical, sour and berry tasting notes. How many forms will this Grapefruit Haze x Grape Ape cross take? She loves to keep you on your toes! Explore Your -ness™

Name: Carmel Summer Drop Pre-Rolls | 6-Pack
description: For our Summer Drop, we wanted to bring you two of our favourite smokes right now. First in line is our LA Beatnik, a cross of Kush Mints x Seed Junky OG. For this one, expect bold notes of citrus, gas and coffee. Up next, we’ve got Star Scream bred by Elev8. Star Scream is a cross of Cereal Milk x Gelato and we fell in love with this smoke because of its creamy mouthfeel and balance of gas and fruit.

Our flower is cultivated and harvested by a collective of independent growers who aim to deliver quality cannabis to Canadians for a sensible price. This flower is then BHO-extracted into honey-toned, translucent shatter. The Community Shatter Sample Pack offers two different rotating strains in one pack! Choose independent, choose local, choose quality. Choose Community.

Name: Simply Bare - BC Organic Hollywood MAC 3.5g
description: Return of the MAC! Our BC Organic Hollywood MAC is ready for its time in the spotlight. This cultivar is a cross of LA Kush Cake x MAC, bringing two popular cultivars together to create this beautiful indica dominant hybrid. With a cake first profile and finishing with gassy and sour notes, it has plenty of potency and flavour. Grown in our living soil, hang dried and hand trimmed, these beautiful dense and frosty buds are packed in our glass jars for optimal freshness.

description: First Class Funk is a brand new flower offering from Holy Mountain. This legendary cultivar is a cross between GMO and Jet Fuel Gelato, which combined, bring out strong creamy, funky and earthy aromas. That earthy aroma comes from the rare selina-diene terpene, which joins forces with hefty amounts of limonene and beta-caryophyllene.

description: Platinum Vape Limonade disposable is an all-in-one rechargeable THC Distillate vape designed for everyone. With its exotic flavour profile, it is sure to please any palate. Tangerine Sunrise is a flavourful way to enjoy the benefits of CBG.

Name: UFEELU Rest Drops
description: Rest Drops by ufeelu features a non-psychoactive blend of 900mg CBD and 300mg CBN in a sunflower oil base. Infused with ufeelu’s signature REST blend of 18 botanical terpenes, featuring light notes of eucalyptus and clove. Our premium drops are designed to be taken sublingually (under the tongue), but may also be added seamlessly to coffee or tea. Each 1ml dispensed with the supplied syringe contains 30mg CBD and 10mg CBN of broad-spectrum oil extracted from Canadian grown hemp. ufeelu is an experienced and passionate cannabis collective based in Vancouver, BC, founded in 2018. We believe in using natural and simple ingredients to curate thoughtful non-psychoactive cannabis products designed with versatile usability in mind.

Name: TABLE TOP Yogurt | 14g
description: A flower called Yogurt? Yeah, you heard right! This purple-hued hybrid from TABLE TOP™ has very strong THC potency potential and a flavour profile that can only be described as herbal, cheesy, earthy and dank. What else would you expect when UK Cheese and Forbidden Fruit cross paths? Sounds like some dank, Ontario-grown Yogurt to us. It’s Got Legs™

Name: Mood Ring- MR Sommelier Selection Indica 3.5G
description: In an endless quest to discover the finest flower, our cannabis sommelier meticulously evaluates and selects Canada's best cannabis to bring you MR Sommelier Selection Indica. With 20+ years of cannabis experience, our sommelier has mastered the art of pheno-hunting and evaluating premium cannabis. Their dedication to excellence ensures that this flower will appeal to even the most discerning cannabis consumers. With satisfaction in mind, we focus on four key criteria: Potency & Terpenes (minimum of 27% THC and a highly desirable olfactory indica profile); Visual Appeal (only the largest flower buds with perfect humidity – hand trimmed, portioned & packaged); Smokability (a clean burn leaving a white ash); Packaging (nitrogen sealed cans which ensure preservation of the cannabinoids, terpenes, humidity & aromas). Through extensive selection, testing and quality control processes Mood Ring ensures consumers experience what premium quality cannabis looks, smells and tastes like.

Name: BUD LAFLEUR Banana Daddy Pre-Rolls | 5-Pack
description: Banana Daddy is an indica strain with a high THC potency made by crossing Granddaddy Purp x Banana Hammock R1. Dense, chunky bud structure, deep green, purple buds coated with frosty trichomes, Banana Daddy delivers fruity aromas with a light diesel finish. The dominant terpenes are myrcene, ocimene and alpha-pinene. Grown indoors in Pointe-Claire, Quebec, we hand harvest, whole plant hang dry, hand trim, slow cure 14 days and hand package. Our pre-rolls are prepared using our whole flower (never trim), finely milled, filled in 98 mm wood pulp paper, natural brown cone, not bleached, non GMO, using organic Arabica gum, a 26 mm W tip and burn white to light grey with a slow to medium burn rate. We use whole flower to prepare our pre-rolls (never trim). In addition to our stringent quality control points from cloning to packaging, we hand inspect every pre-roll before it is packaged.

This dual-flavored soft chew blasted with sour crystals is over-the-top with only natural flavours and colours. With 5 big “S” gummies per pack, you and your friends can enjoy more SOURZ by Spinach™ in one sitting. 10 mg THC total per pack.

Name: REDECAN Wappa | 28g
description: Standing firm at a moderate height and with a stocky build, Redecan Wappa is an indica dominant strain, characterized by its large, densely packed flowers with a broad base, and tapered, pointed tip. Its flowers grow a beautiful green and yellow, sporting vibrant hues of purple in the fall as a response to its cooler growing environment. Wappa exudes an overwhelmingly skunky, yet fruity aroma, thanks to high levels of myrcene and caryophyllene. Consistently testing at high THC levels between 23-29%, Redecan's Wappa strain is the go-to choice for cannabis lovers across the nation. All of our bud is carefully harvested, expertly cured to preserve natural flavour and moisture, trimmed by hand, and inspected.

Hand packaged and nitrogen flushed with a humidity pack and detailed information on the package including top five dominant terpenes, strain name, harvest date and cultivation processes. CELEBRITY is dedicated to providing the connoisseur with an exclusive selection of small batch cannabis. No hype and no gimmicks.

High-quality expectations but through a more affordable and eco-friendly positioning. Out is the new in? Catch me outside!

Each delicate press preserves the essence of Crumbled Lime, capturing its potent effects and captivating aroma. Indulge in the sublime flavours and effects of Crumbled Lime with 3Saints' Pressed Hash. Elevate your cannabis journey with a touch of sophistication and experience the epitome of quality and craftsmanship.

Name: Redecan Warlock 3.5G
description: Warlock is a storied award winning indica dominant strain (85:15) that was derived through purposeful breeding and backcrossing classic strains of Skunk #1 and Afghani to extract favourable genetic traits. Warlock buds are characteristically dense and pepper shaped with emerald green hues with sparse thick furry orange hairs dusted with a fine sweet sticky layer of nearly translucent trichomes. This magical strain achieves a high THC level with a terpene profile that includes caryophyllene, myrcene and bisabolol which showcase its earthy skunky origins while elevated by its fragrant fruity sweet and sour nuances. Warlock by Redecan is further improved upon through the care and attention given to each plant through every stage of growth, harvest and curing that is complemented by being expertly hand trimmed to ensure high quality in every batch.

Name: PURE SUNFARMS Pink Kush Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack

Always packed with BC grown whole flower, no trim and no shake. Rolled with natural paper and finished with a twisted end. A potent pre-roll, packed in a reusable and recyclable tube.

With 2.5 mg of organic live rosin, each soft chew is naturally sweetened with organic fruit purée and is made without animal products or gluten. Simply Bare soft chews are a perfect complement to our BC Organic Fruit Loopz terpene-rich flower.

Don’t let the tropical vibes fool you, these buds are covered with a frost that matches Holy Mountains snowiest peaks.

Name: GENERAL ADMISSION Tiger Blood Indica (1:0) Rechargeable All-In-One Vape
description: Made for the masses, General Admission disposable vapes are made with you in mind. This all-in-one disposable vape comes with a USB-C rechargeable battery and our signature distillate infused with botanical terpenes. Tiger Blood has one speed, delicious. This banger is bringing berry, blood orange and coconut. Tiger Blood is a crowd favourite.

Name: BEURRE BLANC. Carte Blanche Solventless Live Rosin All-in-One Vape
description: The Carte Blanche All-in-One Live Rosin Vape features full spectrum solventless extract from a single cultivar. Our hashmakers cure the live rosin in sealed containers under heat and pressure just long enough to transform the cannabis resins into a homogenized, jam-like consistency prior to being filled into specialized vape hardware. One of the most true-to-strain experiences in a vape!

Name: COOKIES GP20 Ceramic Tip Pre-Roll
description: GP20 is a coveted hybrid strain collab between Cookies and Powerzzz Genetics combining the strains Y-Griega and Snowman. This strain is known for having a very potent gassy smell. GP20 buds have minty green nugs with bright orange hairs and a coating of frosty white crystal trichomes.

Name: Dykstra Greenhouses - Niagara's Own 7G Sativa
description: Niagara’s Own is a sativa-dominant hybrid strain with a potent level of THC between. The buds are dense, mossy-green and have dark orange hairs with frosty white trichomes. In addition, the buds produce a strong aroma with notes of earth, pine sweetness and a trace of “diesel”.

Name: DEBUNK ICE Moon Drops Liquid Diamonds 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Expertly crafted with high purity liquid diamonds, the Moon Drops DEBUNK Ice premium vape cart is an indica that delivers a full serving of lychee and pear and a frosty cooling sensation on the exhale. Our proprietary technology and innovative process for the ultra-clear THC liquid isolate comes from a fresh cured milled flower extracted with hydrocarbon to crystallize potent, clear and pure THC liquid with 3% terpenes and a freshly cool taste for an icy experience. Ultra pure, clear, potent, icy.

Name: 3SAINTS Di-Fruitti
description: 3Saints' Di Fruitti – a cannabis masterpiece crafted by Karma Genetics & grows exceptionally well in our greenhouse. Di-Fruitti is a cross of Strawberry Guava x Headbanger giving potent sativa effects to the consumer. With high THC levels, Di-Fruitti promises a potent experience for both seasoned enthusiasts and newcomers alike. Each bud is a testament to meticulous cultivation and expert breeding, ensuring optimal quality and consistency. Indulge in the tantalizing aromas & different fruity flavours, giving off blends of strawberries, bananas, and papayas as well. Di-Fruitti offers a symphony of flavours that tantalize your taste buds.

Name: D*GG LBS The G-Pooch Pre-Roll
description: The G-Pooch is that real deal indo, smelling like a fruit explosion with hints of candy and gas. This 1G blunt features a ceramic tip that’s bringin’ a whole new level of class to your puffin’ game.

Name: BUD LAFLEUR Deep Mandarine Pre-Rolls | 2-Packs
description: Deep Mandarine, a balanced CBD/THC cultivar, is an indica dominant hybrid with high CBD made by crossing Carmen and Sugar Black Rose. This well-balanced strain features dense resinous buds with deep mandarin and orange blossom aromas. Grown indoors in Pointe-Claire, Quebec. We hand harvest, whole plant hang dry, hand trim, slow cure and hand package. Our pre-rolls are prepared using our whole flower (never trim), finely milled, filled in 98 mm wood pulp paper natural brown cone, not bleached, non GMO, using organic arabica gum, 26 mm W tip and burn white to light gray with a slow to medium burn rate.

Name: Good Supply - Grower's Choice Indica - 28g
description: High-quality indica-dominant bud at a great price; Good Supply is taking it to the next level with Grower’s Choice.

Name: Dab Bods - Ghost Train Haze Resin Infused Pre-Roll
description: Dab Bods Resin Infused Pre-Roll featuring the spooky strain Ghost Train Haze is a cross of Ghost OG x Neville’s Wreck. With a sour citrus and floral aroma, Ghost Train Haze delivers a potent dose of THC. These pre-rolls might be small but they pack potency!

description: No description available

Name: COUNTRYSIDE CANNABIS HARVEST RESERVE HYBRID GRAPE DIAMONDS PRE-ROLL
description: Countryside’s Harvest Reserve Grape Diamonds premium pre-roll is a great way to taste-test our indoor premium flower.

Name: PERSY Full Spectrum Cold Cured Live Rosin Batter
description: Our Cold Cured Live Rosin Batter is a strain specific solventless hash oil made with 70-159u ice water hash and careful mechanical separation techniques. Using premium indoor whole plant material grown to its full potential, it is frozen directly after harvest to preserve extremely volatile terpenes found in the living plant. This method allows us to capture a true representation of the strain’s genetics and how they were grown, with very little degradation to colour and flavour. The cold cure process naturally homogenizes the live rosin without heat into a shelf stable consistency that preserves a high amount of naturally derived terpenes.

Name: CROOKED DORY Newfoundland Cloudberry 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Crooked Dory is a beloved brand rooted in the heart of Atlantic Canada, celebrated for its commitment to quality and innovation. This 1-gram 510 vape cartridge is a testament to our dedication to crafting premium cannabis products. Immerse yourself in the authentic flavours of Atlantic Canada with Newfoundland cloudberry terpenes, extracted directly from the pristine landscapes of the region. The result is a terpene profile that's as unique as it is delicious. These exotic berries are only found remote regions across the world. The infusion of Newfoundland cloudberry terpenes offers a captivating blend of sweet, fruity, and earthy notes, ensuring every inhale is a journey into the heart of Atlantic Canada. Our 510 vape cartridge is carefully crafted for a robust, yet incredibly smooth vaping experience. The terpene infusion elevates the flavour while enhancing the overall satisfaction of each draw.

Name: BON VOYAGE! Flight Pass Pre-Roll
description: Our Lyonleaf team of passionate cannabis experts, operation masterminds and plant scientists has been cultivating craft cannabis at our newly purpose-built 30,000 square foot indoor facility in Montreal, Quebec since February 2020. To date, we have had over 150 successful harvests. We consistently harvest once per week following a sophisticated production schedule. This allows us to dial in on many variables at our facility such as grow media, nutrients, environmental, lighting and cultivation practices, to produce standardized craft cannabis from each batch. We have been providing our standardized craft cannabis in bulk flower format with other licensed producers that package it for their brands and distribute to different provinces. In supporting these brands, we have learned what consumers want in terms of price, potency, strain, product type and packaging type in addition to the standardized bag appeal that consumers deserve.

Name: VIRTUE CANNABIS Galactic Glue Firecracker Infused Blunt
description: Are you ready for the fireworks? This premium hand-crafted firecracker brings you the best of our first-class Galactic Glue flower, packed in an artisanal maté blended blunt cone, enveloped in rich and flavourful terp sauce, dusted with ultra-fine Galactic Glue kief. Let the slow burn of a fine no-tobacco blunt cone spotlight the entourage effect in a smoking experience like none other! This crafted combination highlights the rich earthy, spicy, sour flavours of Galactic Glue in a sweet and citrus terp sauce. Ideal for the seasoned cannasseur looking for a remarkable ensemble of top shelf cannabis extracts with unparalleled flavour. The firecracker is packaged in a fully recyclable hemp-based plastic tube. When you remove it from the tube, it smells like heaven!

Name: BUZZ'D Buzz'd OG
description: A crossbreed of Garlic Sherb x Cactus Breath, Buzz'd OG is a phenomenal strain that was created by Space Sherpa in Barrie, ON. This locally designed strain has a unique spicy aroma and dense flower-like buds that has great bag appeal. It's considered a unicorn strain since it's high in both terpenes and cannabinoids, most notably high in CBG. This 12-week grow flower expresses vigorous vegetative growth with strong vertical branching.

Name: PURE SUNFARMS Baked Animal Pre-Rolls
description: A potent hybrid rolled and ready to spark. Each pre-roll is packed with Baked Animal, a high THC cross of Animal Face and Baker's Delight with the sweet aromas of berries, cake, cream and light gas. BC-grown whole flower – no trim, no shake. Made with natural paper, each pre-roll is finished with a twisted end to prevent spillage and act as a wick. The potent pre-rolls are nestled in a reusable and recyclable tube.

Name: TENZO Cocoa Delight Infused Blunt
description: Delight your senses with a rich cocoa-y experience. Our Cocoa Cake blunt is filled with handcrafted premium indoor flower and infused with a curated blend of natural terpenes and dusted in kief inside a unique natural blunt wrap. Packaged by hand into a recyclable glass tube with a humidity pack to ensure optimal quality and moisture.

Name: THINKER ON (Jack Herer) + OFF (Dos Z Dos) Variety Pack (2pk)
description: Turn your thoughts ON+OFF. THINKER's ON+OFF multi-pack features two complementary strains to turn your thoughts ON (Jack Herer) and OFF (Dos Z Dos). Every pack includes 2x0.25g prerolls; 1 x Jack Herer (sativa) and 1 x Dos Z Dos (indica), that are machined rolled and hand-finished using craft flower to deliver a quality experience in every preroll.

Name: CANACA Headbanger | 28g
description: Throw up the horns for Headbanger. With high THC, this sativa absolutely shreds and features amped-up earth, fruit and gas aromas. This Biker Kush x Sour cross is hang-dried, hand trimmed and carefully cured for an ultra-potent and irresistible flavour with a consistent burn. The buds are tight and dense with purple flecks and excessive trichome coverage. Advanced production techniques and cultivation expertise allow us to produce an intense expression of Headbanger with an enhanced sour and citrus flavour profile, high potencies. Featuring dominant terpenes of caryophyllene, limonene and fenchone dominant terps – you’ll want to experience an encore.

description: Juicy Rouge is inspired by a cross of two A-list strains: Blueberry and White Widow, aka Blue Widow. This indica-leaning hybrid profile has a sweet and strong aroma with a hint of cherry flavour. Our botanical terpenes are blended with double distilled CO2 distillate to provide both potency and classic flavours. Our oils lead the charge on potency and purity using only botanically derived terpenes. Absolutely no fillers like PG, VG, MCT or vitamin E acetate. Our discreet design is made of premium materials such as stainless steel, glass and soft-touch finish

Name: KRONIC Super Silver Haze
description: Super Silver Haze is a classic sticky sativa-dominant strain, and one of many precious gems we acquired in the Legacy market. Bred in the 90's by Greenhouse Seeds, Super Silver Haze combines Skunk, Northern Lights, and Haze genetics. It was the first prize winner at the High Times Cannabis Cup in 1997, 1998, and 1999. Lime green buds come dusted in a heavy layer of sticky trichomes. The flavour palette is a delightful fusion of spice, skunk, and citrus with an aroma to match. Grown in Toronto, this strain was pheno-hunted in-house by our team. Where all strains are hang dried, hand trimmed and never irradiated! We take pride in flushing each crop for 10-14 days, ensuring a smooth taste and a clean burn every time.

Its taste and aroma are nostalgic, with its subtly sweet and fruity notes being reminiscent of fruity cereals.

description: A new Green Monké flavour with a nostalgic flavour. With a 2:1 ratio of CBD to THC, this drink contains 20 mg of CBD and 10 mg of THC. Now made in a recyclable printed can. Pour this purple jungle juice into a cup full of ice and serve with a slice of lime. Made without animal products or gluten.

Name: VORTEX | Alaskan TF Live Resin

Flowers are harvested at night and flash frozen before being extracted at sub zero temperatures. This creates a strong, sticky resin packed with all the rich terpenes intact. A true entourage effect generating a powerful effect. Each Live Resin is made from single source flower. Packaged in a high quality glass concentrate jar, and sealed in a child resistant bag to seal in freshness. Contains dominant terpenes such as pinene and myrcene.

Name: COTERIE Pink Rose #4
description: Pink Rose #4 is a potent pheno-type of the genetic cross of Lemonchello x Lemon Pound Cake. This potent indica-leaning hybrid has bright floral and fruity aromas with a sweet dry pull and earthy exhale. The buds are extremely frosty with shades of green, orange, and light pink. Fresh out of a pheno-hunt, Pink Rose #4 expressed with the best bag appeal, the highest potency and terpene profile. Craft designated and packaged in compostable jars.

Name: TRURO  Donair Kush | 7g
description: Straight from the East Coast. Donair Kush by Truro is a unique and potent indica dominant legacy cultivar of Platinum Kush (Platinum OG Kush X Kush Mints). The flavour profile is earthy, sweet and tangy. Donair Kush is proudly grown on the East Coast in Truro, Nova Scotia in our state-of-the-art small batch production facility, where each bud is carefully cultivated, hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cured (21-28 days) and hand packaged in recyclable aluminium cans that are purged with liquid nitrogen to preserve the dried flower quality, moisture content and terpene profile.

Experience the loud aroma, a blend of sweet vanilla and earthiness. The large, dense buds feature a mix of light and dark green, adorned with vibrant orange pistils. It's been meticulously hang-dried, hand-trimmed, and slow-cured to perfection. With love from Scarborough.

description: Sarah’s stash is a rotating selection cultivated by some of Canada’s finest growers and curated by Sarah Sunday, Karma Cup founder, and her community of judges and cannabis experts.

Name: SOAR Citrus Cyclone Infused Blunt
description: Citrus Cyclone is a potent combination of premium cannabis oil and flavours of sweet and creamy orange with hints of lemon and strawberry. This kief coated infused blunt from Soar’s citrus collection is potent and aromatic. Ground from small batch hang dried whole flower, this classic cone style blunt is finished with a Dutch crown for a smooth and even burn.

Name: CANNACRUSH 4-Piece 2.5" Grinder | Black
description: CannaCrush's four-piece 2.5" grinder features 50 specially designed aluminum diamond-cut teeth and 30 grinding holes (made from aircraft-grade anodized aluminum on CNC machines) that are scratch resistant, which prevents flaking or pealing. Its knurled grip makes grinding easier, and the lid stays in place with a neodymium magnet that also keeps the odour locked inside and maintains freshness. The chamber contains an advanced micron mesh screen to filter the kief. Every CannaCrush premium grinder is equipped with a kief scraper, and a lifetime warranty. This grinder is available in black or grey.

Name: TRURO Titanimal Bubble Infused Pre-Roll
description: Truro’s Titanimal Bubble infused pre-roll is a blend of whole craft Titanimal flower (Animal Cookies x Platinum Kush Mints) infused with Truro bubble hash. The flavour profile is earthy, sweet and pine. Titanimal Bubble pre-rolls are produced from the whole flower of our batches proudly grown on the East Coast in Truro, Nova Scotia in our small batch production facility where each bud is carefully cultivated, hang dried, hand trimmed and slow cured (21-28 days). Truro bubble hash is produced in-house from a blend of Truro’s craft cultivars using a solventless ice water extraction process resulting in a clean and pure hash product. The low temperatures used in our extraction and pressing process ensure minimal loss of terpenes and results in a consistent and premium infused pre-roll. Titanimal Bubble pre-rolls are hand weighed and hand packaged in 100% recyclable tubes.

Name: Spiral Sticks 63mm 4-Piece Grinder
description: No description available

Name: POTLUCK Pineapple Express Pre-Roll
description: Pineapple Express is a sativa dominant classic known for its citrus, earthy and pine aromas. Dominant in myrcene, caryophyllene and pinene. Just one of our four classic Fruit Collection flavours.

Name: PALM GARDENS CANNABIS COMPANY Watermelon Sugar Blunts | 3-Pack
description: This indica leaning lineage of Watermelon and OG offers a distinct full bodied and fruity aroma with sharp hints of melon and a zest of sweetness.

Name: THE LOUD PLUG With love from Scarborough
description: Experience the love from Scarborough with the elite cross of Kush Mintz x Do-Si-Dos. Immerse yourself in its rich aroma, a subtle combination of gassy undertones, earthiness and a hint of sweet mint chocolate. The buds? They're a sight to behold. Large and dense with a touch of foxtail structure, playing between shades of light and dark green, complemented by bright orange pistils and finished with a trichome sparkle. This indica dominant flower is hang dried, slow cured and carefully hand trimmed.

Name: Zele LO - Cherry Limeade Hybrid Craft Soda
description: No description available

Name: REDECAN Gems 10:0
description: Redecan’s Gems are a perfect way to discreetly consume pre-dosed oil. Processed using state-of-the-art CO2 extraction technology, Gems are made with responsibly sourced MCT oil and encased in gelatine capsules that are produced in-house. Redecan's 10:0 Gems contain 10mg of THC per capsule.

Name: CANACA Alien Guy | 28g
description: Alien Guy is a supernatural sativa made from a cross of Jean Guy x Alien Dawg with high THC potency and the bold sour citrus aromas and hints of lemon and sweet pine. Dense emerald green buds dappled with fiery amber pistols and absolutely blanketed in trichomes, this is one unique strain you’ll have trouble putting down.

Name: CARMEL Studio 54 Pre-Rolls
description: At Carmel, making a great pre-roll means starting off with top-shelf whole flower, and producing in small batches for the perfect smoking experience. Each of our pre-rolls is filled into a slim cone and hand packaged in a glass tube with a cork top. Studio 54 was pheno hunted in-house and grown by Carmel. Bred by Deep East in California, Studio 54 is a cross of Sunset Sherbert x Pink Guava. Large dense spear shaped buds feature deep purple marbling and orange hairs. With this potent strain, expect flavours and aroma of guava, fuel and a little sherb.

Name: *COGNOSCENTE - The Craft Tasting Flight: Micro Edition Hybrid 6g
description: Welcome to Flight #2 – The Micro Edition. Crafted for connoisseurs, experience a curated selection of small batch handcrafted flower from some of Canada’s up-and-coming micros. Meticulously designed to offer a sampling of 3 premium cultivars which were hand-picked and packaged in a sleek, reusable box. A limited edition offering.

Name: TERP TOWN COLLECTIVE Lazer Wolf Pre-Roll
description: Lazer Wolf begins with a blistering high THC and mesmerizing purple hued buds - glistening with sticky trichomes. Lazer Wolf has inherited a unique flavour profile, Animal Sorbet brings a sherbet kick that dances devilishly with the tangy, citrusy, punch from Trop Souffle. Even experiences smokers should be wary of the power of the Lazer Wolf.

Name: COMMUNITY Sweet Rocks Diamonds
description: Community Sweet Rocks Diamonds are powerful refinements of cannabis that are formed from fresh-frozen, sun-grown flower. Our terpene-rich, aromatic flower is preserved through flash-freezing at harvest and then concentrated through BHO extraction before time is given for the crystallization of cannabinoids into high-potency THCA diamonds. The resulting material still expresses notes of the flower’s unique sun-expressed flavonoids and terpenes, offering more complete and complex flavour than standard diamonds. High quality input leads to high quality results. Community Sweet Rocks Diamonds are the gems potency-minded consumers have been searching for.

Name: SEEKER Molten Lava Cake | 3.5g
description: Seeker Molten Lava Cake is a potent and delightful cultivar. This strain is engulfed in chocolate flavours and fired up herbal and floral aromatic notes. With terpenes such as humulene, ocimene and caryophyllene, dive right into a serious treat of a strain.

Name: CHOKLIT PARK Vader OG
description: Vader OG was developed by crossing SFV OG (San Fernando Valley Kush) with Larry OG. The bud is a light green accented by fuzzy pistils and amber trichomes. The flavour and aroma are similar in that they have a strong floral overtone contrasted with spice and pepper. The dominant terpene is limonene followed by caryophyllene and pinene.

Name: PROPER Blueberry Pomegranate Cannabis Infused Sparkling Water
description: Proper Blueberry Pomegranate is a sparkling cannabis beverage made with natural flavours and deoxygenated Ontario spring water. With 10 mg of THC, one calorie and no sugar, Proper Blueberry Pomegranate is an incredible beverage that delivers flavour. All our beverages are proudly crafted in Canada with an attention to flavour and quality, because that’s Proper. This isn’t corporate cannabis; it’s made with care.

Name: MOOD RING MR Sommelier Selection Sativa Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: Mood Ring MR Sommelier Selection sativa pre-rolls. In an endless quest to discover the finest flower, our cannabis sommelier meticulously evaluates and selects some of Canada's best cannabis to proudly bring you MR Sommelier Selection sativa pre-rolls. With 20+ years of cannabis experience under his belt, our cannabis sommelier has mastered the art of pheno-hunting and evaluating cannabis. With the satisfaction of cannabis connoisseurs in mind, MR Sommelier Selection sativa pre-rolls focus on four key criteria. 1. Potency and terpenes: high THC and a highly desirable olfactory sativa profile. 2. Craft flower: no trim and no shake, just full bud craft flower. 3. Premium papers: premium cannabis requires premium cones. 4. Smokability: a clean burn leaving a white ash.

Name: CALI SLIMZ Hawaiian Tropics Pre-Rolls | 10-Pack
description: Hawaiian Tropics – is an evenly balanced hybrid strain (50% indica/50% sativa) created through a delicious cross of the potent Maui Wowi x Tutti Frutti strains. Hawaiian Tropics has a sweet and citrusy tropical fruity flavour with a touch of sharp mint to it, too. The aroma is just as delicious, with a fruity berry overtone accented by sweet and sour citrus and sharp flowery mint. Hawaiian Tropics buds have fluffy dense oversized bright neon green buds with golden amber undertones, orange hairs and a coating of golden amber crystal trichomes.

Name: PIFF Maui Wowie Pre-Rolls | 2-Pack
description: Just the mention of Maui Wowie to some brings back memories, to others we only know it as the parent to some of the most potent sativas on the market today. Hints of spice and fruit poke through a herbaceous back note, giving this high energy sativa a profile you can’t help but recognize.

Name: DEEP SPACE PROPULSION Pulsar Peach THC + CBG + Caffeine
description: Deep Space Propulsion Pulsar Peach is a refreshingly delicious bold peach soda with vibrant notes of melon. Pulsar Peach is fuelled by 10 mg of THC, 10 mg of CBG and naturally occurring caffeine. Made with natural flavours and colours.

Name: LOT420 Off Menu Pre-Rolls | 2-pack
description: Lot420 and United Greeneries have teamed up again to bring you Off Menu. This rotating strain product allows consumers to discover exclusive new strains in legacy market fashion. Each strain is associated with a specific lot number. Retailers and budtenders will be able to identify each specific lot number and inform the consumer on how to find the product description online. You will be able to obtain your strain specific product description through Lot420’s website and social media channels. Upcoming strains include Apples and Bananas, Area41, Baklava and many other tantalizing legacy strains.

Name: 3Saints - Sundae Strudel 3.5g
description: Give into temptation with this terpene rich hybrid. A cross of Cherry Strudel x Sundae Driver. The cherry & fuel profile comes from the Cherry Strudel, which adds a kick to the already sweet and creamy Sundae Driver. Righteously grown in the sun, rain watered, and expertly cured for a deeper, more satisfying experience. Dominant terpenes include: caryophyllene, myrcene, limonene, germacrene and humulene. All 3Saints flower has high THC. Hail Mary Jane.

Name: CARMEL High Fructose Corn Syrup Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: At Carmel, making a great pre-roll means starting off with top-shelf whole flower, and producing in small batches for the perfect smoking experience. Each of our pre-rolls is hand filled into a slim cone and packaged in a glass tube with a cork top. High Fructose Corn Syrup is an indica-dominant strain, which we pheno hunted in-house. Bred by Full Moon Genetics, High Fructose Corn Syrup is a cross of GMO x OZ Kush with golf ball, purple marbled buds. This strain boasts an initially offensive and funky aroma with a savoury finish.

Name: UFEELU Calm Drops
description:
Calm Drops by ufeelu features a blend of 900mg of CBD and 300mg of CBG in a sunflower oil base. Infused with ufeelu’s signature CALM blend of 18 botanical terpenes, featuring light notes of lavender and peppermint. Our premium drops are designed to be taken sublingually (under the tongue), but may also be added seamlessly to coffee or tea. Each 1ml dispensed with the supplied syringe contains 30mg of CBD and 10mg of CBG of broad-spectrum oil extracted from Canadian grown hemp. ufeelu is an experienced and passionate cannabis collective based in Vancouver, BC, founded in 2018. We believe in using natural and simple ingredients to curate thoughtful cannabis products designed with versatile usability in mind.
LICENSED PRODUCER

Name: GRIND- Fruity Haze - Premium Craft Buds Grind 7G
description: Grind is ground craft cannabis on the market at an affordable price. Single strain input only. The whole buds are hand-trimmed, hang-dried, slow cured and finely ground properly right before packaging. In California, the Haze brothers created Haze using sativa strains Mexican (Acapulco Gold), Colombian (Gold), Chocolate Thai and Jamaican Lamb’s Bread. These land race sativas were bred in year after year to build the ultimate sativa. It was brought to Amsterdam and formed the basis for all modern strains using Northern Lights as the indica input. Bong smokers and those who don't want to grind their own now have quality premium craft buds pre-ground for convenience. Convenience doesn’t mean that quality should be sacrificed.

Name: HIWAY INDICA DOMINANT SCOTT'S OG PRJ PRE-ROLL
description: True to its OG heritage, Scott’s OG is an indica-dominant hybrid with a lineage of Triangle Kush and Rare Dankness #1. Thick blankets of crystal trichomes cover its buds in a coat, alluding to its potency. Scott's OG gives off an earthy, sour aroma that is sweetened by hints of citrusy lemon-lime. Hiways PRJ’s are evenly rolled for a smooth burn; these joints are ready when you are.

description: No description available

Name: FIGR Notable Nancy - Pre-Rolls
description: Notable Nancy, an indica-dominant strain created in California’s Orange County, is a cross between Larry OG x Legend OG. Starting with a sharp gassy inhale, this kush strain transitions to a sweet citrusy exhale, with both lime and orange notes. The taste is complemented by a floral aroma from its strong caryophyllene, limonene, and myrcene terpene profile. A legendarily potent strain, these dense, yet large emerald buds, sparkle with a frosty layer of trichomes. FIGR pre-rolls are expertly rolled with a paper filter and conical shape for a smooth, consistent smoke.

Name: FLOWR Pink Kush Bubble Hash & Sauce Infused Pre-Roll
description: The original cut from FLOWR is grown to high AVANT standards. Pheno-hunted, tissue cultured, dialled in and infused with solventless bubble hash and terpene sauce, all derived from our small batch, indoor grown Pink Kush, then packed inside a custom organic hemp cone and housed in our custom cobalt blue glass tube.

Name: REDECAN Cold Creek Kush Redees King Pack
description:
Redees by Redecan are an unparalleled pre-roll experience that just got even more convenient. The Redecan King Pack offers 1 oz of your favourite Redecan strains, pre-rolled in our signature packaging and sealed in packs of 10 to guarantee freshness. Thoughtfully designed for personal use at 0.40g, Redees by Redecan are rolled with all bud, no shake. A sativa dominant hybrid between the ever-popular MK Ultra and Chemdawg 91, Cold Creek Kush, or CCK, is a globally recognized strain, known for its light green hues, amber hairs, and trichrome-frosted flowers. Cold Creek Kush is recognized for its dank smell, resembling a damp rainforest with notes of earth, wood, sour, and pine, giving a strong but fresh aroma and a dank, spicy, herbal flavour. 
 
 Each Redecan King Pack contains 70 Cold Creek Kush Redees.

Name: Purple Hills- Lake Huron Haze HTFSE 510 Thread Cartridge Sativa 1G
description: Purple Hills Lake Huron Haze High Terpene Full Spectrum Extract (HTFSE) cart places flavour first. This concentrate combines fractions of sativa-dominant terpenes and potent cannabinoids, derived from fresh-frozen live cannabis flower, extracted through a hydrocarbon process. For consumers in search of powerful and complex flavours, who don’t want to compromise on potency, and want it all for a great price, the Purple Hills Lake Huron Haze HTFSE cartridge is the answer.

Name: TRURO Tres Dawg x I-95 Pre-Roll
description: Tres Dawg x I-95 pre-rolls by Truro is a potent legacy hybrid of Afghani 1 X Chemdawg BX1. This unique indica dominant hybrid provides a classic Kush aroma with a complex flavour profile featuring earthy notes, fuel undertones, peppery spice and a hint of lemon. Tres Dawg x I-95 pre-rolls are produced from the whole flower of our own batches, and we have refined our mixing and milling processes to mirror the high quality and THC levels of our popular craft whole flower products. All Truro pre-rolls are hand weighed and hand packaged in recyclable tubes for a true craft pre-roll.

Name: PHANT Orange Cream Live Resin Gummies
description: Orange Cream Live Resin Soft Chews by Phant are a 2-pack sweet soft chews infused with full spectrum live resin. Each soft chew delivers an orange flavour that’s paired with our live resin – made from fresh cannabis flower and extracted using proprietary hydro-carbon extraction technique. Every pack includes 2 soft chews, each with 5 mg THC for a total THC of 10 mg.

Indoor grown in small batches on the West Coast, Broken Coast strives to push the limits on what craft flower can be. Experience notes of Citrus, Grapefruit and Pine from large, trichome-rich buds.

Name: TEAPOT Good Evening Iced Tea Blueberry Chamomile Tea
description: Using only the finest ingredients, TeaPot Blueberry Chamomile is made with real chamomile tea and natural blueberry flavour, and infused with 5 mg of single origin THC derived from indica dominant Black Sugar Rose cannabis. It has subtle sweetness.

Name: BLK MKT The Flurry Pre-Roll
description: A BLKMKT Exclusive. A unique cross of two classic strains, ICC and MAC (Miracle Alien Cookies). Close your eyes and imagine sweet lime cordial syrup, with dense buds that are iced out in trichomes, with hints of bold purple underneath.

Name: PURA VIDA Pineapple Express Live Resin Cartridge
description: This popular Pineapple Express strain expresses sweet, zesty and citrus flavours and aromas​. Made using single strain whole bud inputs​, this live resin cartridge is the easiest decision you'll make all day.

Name: 3SAINTS Crumbled Lime Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: Get ready to pucker up. 3Saints has once again delivered the goods with this powerful sativa as we continue giving you potency, without sacrificing taste. This bud doesn't hold back. With a deliciously sweet and citrusy lemon-lime flavour that gradually turns into sour lime, Crumbled Lime is a strain to be reckoned with. The aroma is a blend of earthy lime and sweet citrus. If you're a fan of bold, in-your-face flavours, you're going to love Crumbled Lime. This cultivar is the result of crossing Citron CKS x Biker Kush, and the result is a strain that packs serious potency.

description: Versus Bubba Mint 510 vapes are made with high quality cannabis distillate combined with a terpene-rich blend to deliver a smooth, cool and sweet spearmint sensation.

Name: SHATTERIZER Rockstar Shatter Diamonds & Kief Triple Infused Pre-Roll
description: Rockstar Shatterizer Family … we’re Infusing 3 loved Shatterizer Extracts into a concentrated, powerful and perfected Rockstar triple infused pre-roll. It’s a triple hit, tripling the #PerfectClouds with Shatter, Diamonds and Kief. Our flavourfully cured and potent Rockstar cannabis flower is evenly concentrated with golden shatter and THCa diamonds for a very high THC range. This innovative triple infusion of shatterized flower, enriched with diamonds, is perfectly pre-rolled and hand spun in kief, tripling the height, taste and density of #PerfectClouds Rockstar Shatterizer Family! Made for our Rockstar Shatterizer Family, our triple infused pre-roll is a triple hit of Rockstar Flower, Shatter, Diamonds and Kief!

Name: HIWAY Berry Boulevard 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Hiway Berry Boulevard is a scenic route of very berry forward flavour in a 510 cart. Hiway vapes are thoughtfully created to bring you a big vape at a great price that doesn't compromise on quality. Simply attach a 510 vape battery and take a stroll down the Berry Boulevard.

Name: Top Leaf - LA Kush Cake Indica 7g
description: Top Leaf LA Kush Cake is proof that sometimes you can have your cake and smoke it too. Simultaneously smooth and surprisingly strong, treat yourself to LA Kush Cake’s sweet vanilla scent and indulge in its earthy mint flavour. This indica-hybrid is very potent.

Name: RAD Blue Razz Fuel Cell 510 Thread Cartridge
description: RAD Blue Razz Fuel Cell (ceramic) vape cartridges deliver flavours of blue raspberry with pops of sour. This triple distilled extract is encased in cutting-edge fully ceramic 510 thread hardware.

Name: SHEEESH! Trop Cherry 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Hand-trimmed, hang-dried, cold cured. These single-strain vapes feature a unique, tropical, gassy, sativa – what’s more to love? This strain has a citrus/fruit aroma.

Name: NUGZ Guava Jam
description: Feel the rhythm, feel the rhyme, come on y'all it's Guava time! Nugz Guava Jam. Coming from Bloom Seed co, Guava Jam is a genetic backcross of Guavaz x Guavaz to stabilize the genetic and really bring out the flavours of the tropics. Expect buds laced with red/orange pistils and glistening with trichomes like the ocean at night.

Name: FLEUR DE L'ILE Jack Herer Pre-Roll
description: A crossover between Northern Lights #5 and Shiva Skunk genetics that's well suited for outdoor cultivation. Great sativa dominance with high THC and may contain CBD and CBN. Its aromas are earthy, woody and spicy. The colour of the flower is brown and moderately dense. Terpenes most commonly present include beta-caryophyllene, alpha-pinene, humulene and myrcene.

Name: STATION HOUSE |OG Kush Infused Pre-Roll
description: Riding solo doesn’t need to be boring. The Station House infused pre-roll uses proprietary technology to meticulously blend high THC isolate with OG Kush whole flower. With genetics stemming from Chemdawg, Hindu Kush and Lemon Thai, OG Kush offers mixed aromas of earth and diesel with hints of pine and lemon.

Name: THRIFTY GRAB BAG Big Steal Live Resin Concentrate
description: Thrifty Big Steal Live Resin Concentrate is one of the best concentrate deals in Canada. You won't find a better diamond in the rough offering than this amazing and portable grab bag.

Name: SPINACH Fully Charged Pink Lemonade Infused Pre-Roll
description: Our Spinach® Fully Charged Pink Lemonade infused pre-roll is infused with cold filtered cannabis extract and a dusting of kief coating. Inspired by a strain with a Lemon Skunk and Purple Kush lineage and dialled up with a terpene infusion, the sweet, raspberry and lemonade flavour notes are like a summer breeze on your face.

Name: Glow In The Dark Marley 52mm 4-Pc Grinder
description:
The Arsenal Glow In The Dark Marley 52mm 4-Piece Grinder is a versatile and stylish tool for grinding your favorite herbs. With its glow-in-the-dark feature, this grinder adds a fun and unique element to your smoking accessories. The 52mm size ensures ample space for grinding herbs, while the 4-piece design includes a pollen catcher for collecting fine particles. Sold as a pack of 3, you'll have plenty of grinders to use or share with friends.

Specifications:

Glow-in-the-dark feature for added style
52mm size for ample grinding space
4-piece design with pollen catcher
Durable construction for long-lasting use
Pack of 3 for convenience and value
Grind your herbs with style and convenience using the Arsenal Glow In The Dark Marley 52mm 4-Piece Grinder. Its unique design and functionality make it a must-have accessory for any smoking enthusiast. Enjoy smooth and consistent grinds for your smoking sessions.

Name: GRIZZLERS Sour Zktlz Indica Pre-Roll
description: Rooted in traditional market values and knowledge, Grizzlers brings you back to the forest with Sour Zktlz, an indica-dominant mix of Grape Ape, Grapefruit and a grower’s secret cultivar.  Sour Zktlz chunky colas explode in a spectrum of light green hues, and emit a sweet, tropical blend of fruit flavours with subtle notes of earth and wood, balanced by bright citrus and diesel overtones. At Grizzlers, we’re all about accessible craft-grown products. Always hang dried, hand-trimmed and hand-packed, Grizzlers offers an impeccable smoking experience legacy consumers can be proud of. Our commitment to craft, focus on the flower, accessible pricing, signature BC vibes, and of course our legacy market clout, set Grizzlers apart from the rest.

Name: FIGR Sunshine Bubble Kush | 7g
description: Sunshine Bubble Kush is a balanced hybrid created by crossing the Sunshine State’s Triangle Kush with the dank, bubble hash-esque ‘88 G13 Hashplant. The strain has a sugary, earthy flavour with a gentle, spicy aroma of cloves and pine, followed by a citrusy perfume. The bud is compact and quite dense, with deep purple, almost black sugar leaves. It’s known for producing extremely potent flowers with THC levels. FIGR dried flower products are hand selected to ensure dense, high-quality buds are in every package.

Name: Redecan - Cold Creek Kush Sativa - 1g
description: Cold Creek Kush from Redecan is a cross between MK Ultra and fellow Colorado native Chemdawg 91, with dense, heart-shaped, light green buds full of trichomes and amber hairs. Grown in the Niagara region of Ontario, the strain has very strong THC potency and a recognizable dank smell, much like a forest after a rainfall. Its taste profile, informed by its beta-pinene, nerolidol, trans-caryophyllene, linalool and limonene terpene mix, is strongly herbal, earthy and woody, with fresh sour pine.

Name: Carmel Rares
description: Rares is a pursuit of the uncommon. Rares is our tireless dedication to bring you the most exclusive gear we could get our hands on. From terpenes to bag appeal, we look to check all the boxes, knowing you’ll be as excited as we are for these limited drops. Sometimes grown in-house, sometimes grown by our network of incredibly talented craft growers, always fire.

Name: GOOD SUPPLY Monkey Butter | 3.5g
description: This $#!% is bananas! Monkey Butter is on the loose and someone should call animal control, because this indica is a beast with high THC. No, really though — it’s nutty with earth and woodsy aromas thanks to the dominant terpenes of beta-caryophyllene, cedrene and humulene. So quit your monkeying around and indulge in these compact light green buds with amber pistils that shimmer with milky trichomes. Because this cross of GG #4 x Peanut Butter Breath means business. Monkey business.

Name: Weathered Islands Craft Cannabis- Lemon Cream Pre-Roll	Sativa 3X0.5G
description: Texada Island’s best kept secret is now available in pre-rolls! Lemon Cream was created on Texada Island and is a Weathered Islands exclusive. With lineage from a spectacular Lemon Haze cultivar crossed with a frosty island bred cream phenotype, the Lemon Cream is a crystalline sativa-dominant strain with a unique terpene profile and high THC content. Want to try something truly unique? The Lemon Cream is the answer. Packaged in a fully compostable tube.

With fresh, tropical flavours and a hint of pineapple, this stack of pre-rolls is infused with distillate and a tasty botanical terpene blend. To top it off, we’ve coated these pre-rolls in kief.

description: Dymond Concentrates THCA Diamond-Infused cones are handcrafted to perfection using only premium flower and beautiful high potency THCA Diamonds. Using our state-of-the-art hydrocarbon extractor in conjunction with our hands-on approach throughout the life cycle of the cannabis results in a high-quality concentrate, rich in cannabinoids and terpenes. Our soil to oil process ensures we remain committed to providing consistent and natural flavours. Proudly producing beautiful and pure concentrates.

This magical strain achieves a high THC level with a terpene profile that includes caryophyllene, myrcene and bisabolol which showcase its earthy skunky origins while elevated by its fragrant fruity sweet and sour nuances. Warlock is further improved upon through the care and attention given to each plant through every stage of growth, harvest and curing that is complemented by being expertly hand trimmed to ensure high quality in every batch.

The aroma is much like a sour lemon candy in a citrus grove right after the rain, with touches of earthy woodiness accenting sharply sour lemon. This bud has super sticky and fat pepper-shaped bright neon green buds with dark leaves, light orange hairs and a coating of tiny, frosty white crystal trichomes.

description: Hot Ch33tos is a cross of Cheeta Piss x Runz, and was one of the winners from our most recent pheno hunt. Because it’s the right thing to do, all of our flower is hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cold cured, and hand packaged. We believe fresh and terpy is best, so all our flower is packaged in a nitrogen flushed pouch with a humidity pack. Non-irradiated, obviously.

The flavour is said to be much like a sweet sherbet with fruity blueberry and orange flavours. The aroma is just as sickly sweet with a lavender citrus berry bouquet that has a woody scent as the buds are broken apart and smoked.

description: A deep dive into the lineage of Blue Iguana brings us back to a strong skunk base found predominately in Double Dutch.   Skunky, earthy aromas could be challenging to the nose but a pleasant taste. Cross this with Old Time Moonshine (aka Blueberry Muffin Tops) for those enthusiast who enjoy flavour and a preference for classic indica. This bud has oversized tapered dark olive green buds with purple undertones, long thin light orange hairs and a coating of frosty purple-tinted white crystal trichomes. Grown outdoors with all organic practices, this well-balanced strain has been hand cultivated with utmost care and quality of traditional cannabis. Cannabis connoisseurs will appreciate the heritage, detail and expertise given to this cultivar.

Numero Ono is the epitome of cannabis artistry, tailored for both the casual enthusiast and the seasoned connoisseur.

Each pack offers pre-rolls containing Cosmic Cream – an impressively high-THC indica bred from original, elite genetics sourced from Occo – our world-renowned breeding facility in Comox, BC. Always rolled from finely milled whole flower, never shake, and packaged in a reusable, compact doob tube with a humidity pack included.

Name: 1SPLIFF- Island Pink Pre-Rolls |7-pack

Pre-rolls are produced directly from the buds of the dried flower - ensuring no stems, no sticks, and no shake - just pure compact dried flower.

Our plants are flushed before cutting to ensure the cleanest possible product and our colas are expertly manicured and hand-dried for 10 days, optimizing flavour and aroma. Planet of the Grapes, an indica dominant strain, has high levels of myrcene, caryophyllene and limonene terpenes and features a distinct, fruity and grape-like aroma. Our buds undergo a cold dark cure using specialized craft techniques for 14 days. This unique 80 x 0.35g pre-roll multipack gives you the best of the OHJA family with a combination of our Indica and Sativa strains: 40 x Lemon Mintz pre-rolls (Sativa) 40 x El Jefe Pink pre-rolls (Indica).

Name: GOOD SUPPLY Jean Guy Temple Ball Hash | 2g
description: What’s old is new again – experience the new world of old hash with this Moroccan-style Jean Guy Temple Ball Hash. Hand-rolled into a ball with a shiny, dark brown exterior, break it open to experience oozing, spicy-citrus aromatics of Jean Guy with a sticky, brownie-like colour and texture. You might even say we’re bringing Temple Ball Hash back to the future.

Name: LORD JONES Gorilla Z Pure Live Resin All-in-One Vape.
description: The Lord Jones Purple Gorilla Z Live Resin 510 thread cartridge. Gorilla Z shines in its live resin form, delivering a flavour burst of fruity, berry, cherry and grape flavours. Lord Jones Pure Live Resin immerses you in the natural terpenes and cannabinoids of the plant, using a 510 thread cartridge optimized for live resin with bold and flavourful hits.

Name: Zig Zag Hemp 1 1/4 Papers
description: No description available

Name: CARE 1:1 Frankincense & Eucalyptus Mood Oil Blend
description: INNOCA is a unique collection of topical personal care products formulated from herbal ingredients and botanical extracts. Inspired by the richness of essential oils, the INNOCA Mood Oils offer a fragrance-based THC and CBD delivery system in a portable packaging format. The Nº1 CARE Aromatic Mood Oil is an essential oil formula enhanced with a 1:1 blend of extracted and distilled THC and CBD cannabinoids. As the name suggests, the aroma therapeutic blend in CARE is a warm and spicy fragrance with sweet undertones that couple a balance of THC and CBD. Features an essential oil blend of frankincense, lemon, eucalyptus, rosemary, thyme and cinnamon. The cannabinoids round out the fragrance with a subtle and pleasant grassy note. The carrier base is skin-friendly jojoba oil. Apply two to three drops to fingertips and/or directly behind the ears, neckline or hairline. Re-apply as desired.

Name: 1964 Cured Resin - Indica
description: The 1964 cured resin is the newest addition to the 1964 concentrate line up. It will feature a rotating selection of cultivars that have been specifically chosen for their delicious flavour. The consistency will vary by cultivar, but each has been dialled in to provide a smooth dab.

Name: TRURO MAC & Cheese Pre-Roll
description: No description available

Name: CELEBRITY Façade Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: Façade defies the conventional norms. So, dear connoisseur of the extraordinary, venture forth.

Name: EASTCANN Banana Mints
description: Banana Mints smells a bit like kiwi, which gives banana-adjacent in taste. That extra fruitiness is evidence of a luscious stash of terpenes and flavonoids. The aroma is really rather intoxicating — pleasantly tart and honey sweet. Remarkably, that banana flavour follows through into the smoke, amidst the citrusy terpenes and something reminiscent of chocolate. The bud is densely packed and each petal is crystal-covered, giving them a notably pale appearance, though they are rather lightly hued by themselves.

Name: BLK MKT Ya Hemi | 14g
description: Bred by Grandiflora out in California, this unique cross of Project 4516 x Melonatta is extremely potent. Burnt tires, fuel and skunk on the nose, with sweet notes of citrus and plum on the exhale. This cultivar delivers a truly unique experience. Not for novices. Our Small Batch Flower is always hang dried, hand trimmed, meticulously cured, graded and then carefully hand packaged inside our premium glass jars.

Name: SUPER TOAST Pop n' Pour Melonade
description: Freshly ground, potent indica, full of sweet melon and tangy lemonade aromas. Fluffy, sticky goodness packed in a pop top tube with a humidity pack to keep things extra fresh and super easy. Always ready. Just shake, pop n’ pour.

Name: ELIOS RESERVE Sour Pebble Infused Pre-Roll
description: A new addition to our Elios Reserve family of infused pre-rolls. Whole flower is infused with our high-potency, reserved distillate. This amplified pre-roll balances a sweet and sour aroma, delivering a sweet fruity flavour with a hint of fresh lemon.

Name: TOP LEAF Alaskan TF | 3.5g
description: Alaskan TF emerges with pungent citrus and earthy flavours, embodying the whispers of its origins amidst the towering peaks of Matanuska. This very strong THC potency sativa is born from the union of an Afghani indica landrace and a mystery offspring of unknown Northern California and Russian ruderalis strains. Top Leaf prides itself on carefully crafted cannabis cultivars with rich, full-bodied flavour and complex terpene profiles.

Name: BACK FORTY S'Mores
description: First, you take the graham … actually, scrap that. Back Forty just made s'mores THAT much easier. Back Forty S'mores chocolate is 10 mg of pure THC distillate in a single piece of delicious chocolate that combines the flavours of marshmallow, graham crackers and, of course, chocolate. This mouthwatering combination will take you to your very own campfire in the back forty. Always packaged in a resealable foil pouch to make sure your chocolate stays fresh. Back Forty requires no introduction because it already feels familiar with a product suite that fits seamlessly into your day-to-day. Without the need to overthink it, Back Forty provides a better experience for less. Take a trip and explore the Back Forty.

Name: SHATTERIZER Concentrate Vaporizer
description: The Shatterizer concentrate vaporizer, designed in Canada, is engineered for cannabis concentrates and extracts. It delivers perfect clouds, every time! The black or silver aluminum globe shaped atomizer is durable, matte on the outside, smooth on the inside and a hit with connoisseurs appreciating flavour! The battery operates for approximately 40 hours with 2 hour charge, has 3 variable voltage settings and a 15 second continuous heat option. Shatterizer’s all-inclusive Starter Kit comes with Instructions, Aluminum Atomizer Globe, 2 Quartz Dual Coils (QDC), 2 Coil Caps, 510 Thread Battery, Magnetic Storage Container, Charging Cord and Dab tool. Replacement QDC and CTECH Ceramic coils available separately. For videos, cleaning instructions and 6 month warranty visit Shatterizer.ca

Name: KINLOCH WELLNESS Serene™- CBD Green Apple Gummy Drop
description: This high potency value pack of Serene™ CBD Green Apple Drops contains uniquely shaped naturally flavoured terpene enhanced non-pectin soft chews each with a generous volume of 50 mg of CBD without the expected bitterness. These European confectionery-style soft chews have a great mouth feel and are made by hand in a low-temperature process that preserves the broad-spectrum effect of the terpene and cannabinoid combination. This highly flavour focused soft chew is presented in an eye pleasing custom drop shape. We source low-THC plants that are hand-tended by Canadian farmers, grown outside in the warm sunshine of Ontario’s southern farmlands. Using efficient extraction methods, we have removed the THC leaving only broad-spectrum minor cannabinoids enhanced with terpene formulations.

Name: BOXHOT Stubbies - Mango Vortex Infused Blunts | 3-Pack
description: Introducting BOXHOT Stubbies, blunts infused with some of the sexiest distillate on the market and enhanced with juicy flavours you've come to expect from BOXHOT. Wrapped in natural, highly durable chamomile blunts, these powerful pre-rolls offer a consistent burn. These blunts have ripe mango and floral notes with a sharp diesel finish.

description: Introducing Mother Pucker Peach, the mother of all sour peach vapes. Mother Pucker Peach features a sweet and sour peachy flavour. Housed in the Feather 510 cart, this offering boasts all stainless steel hardware and slick black soft touch exterior.

Lit Silicone Donut Hand Pipe on Keychain

Prepare your sweet tooth! The new LIT™ Silicone Donut Hand Pipe & Keychain is here to help you accessorize your smoking experience. This delicious dessert is available in multiple colours and includes a keychain that allows you to take your pipe with you wherever you go.

Product Features:
- BPA-free

- Glass bowl included

What's Included: 
1 x 2.25" Donut Hand Pipe & Keychain 
1 x Glass Bowl
