Name: CARMEL Summer Drop
description: For our Summer Drop, we wanted to bring you two of our favourite smokes right now in one pouch. The first half of our Summer Drop is Star Scream, which is bred by Elev8 and is a cross of Cereal Milk x Gelato. Upon opening your bag, expect a potent bouquet of gas and fruit backed by a smooth milky mouthfeel. For the 2nd half of your pouch, we’ll be bagging up some LA Beatnik. Bred by Seed Junky, LA Beatnik is a cross of Kush Mints x Seed Junky OG. For this one, expect large chunky buds with bright notes of citrus, coffee and gas.

Name: CATCH ME OUTSIDE Rooster Call |3.5g
description: Catch Me Outside is a 100% outdoor growth brand, from Quebec, offering first quality of products without taking themselves too seriously. Rooster Call is there to offer strong THC sativa strains, in rotation. With the current strain and terps wrote on the packaging, All Catch Me Outside flower are thoughtfully hung to dry, hand trimmed and hand packaged. High-quality expectations but through a more affordable and eco-conscious positioning. Out is the new in? Catch me outside!

description: Clipper lighters are the world's number 1 refillable lighter brand. The iconic shape of this reusable lighter is a true refillable lighter. Not only can you replace the gas in it, but you can even replace the flint as well. With over 4000 designs per year, you are sure to always find the perfect look for any occasion. Each Clipper lighter features a uniquely designed pressing tool. Just pop out the flint arm and you got a handy tamper that's always with your lighter.

Name: WAGNERS Cherry Jam Joints Pre-Rolls
description: At WAGNERS we believe in hard work and Well Made Weed. Our Cherry Jam joints are just that, Well Made. The contrast between light and deep greens broken up by big hits of purple create a striking camouflage effect. Cherry Jam gives off aromas of sweet fruit and skunky Christmas cake. The smoke itself is smooth, flavourful and reminds us of sour cherry and rich dried fruits. Joints rolled with this hybrid strain deliver the best parts of the indica and sativa side of a smoke.

Name: Versus - Sweet Island Skunk | 28g
description: Versus Sweet Island Skunk is a sativa-dominant flower, delivering sweet skunky flavours with notes of grapefruit.

Name: DRY ISLAND Papaya x Blue Power Pre-Rolls
description: Papaya x Blue Power is an indica-dominant strain with high THC. Nirvana Seeds bred this to be their take on a Mango strain and crossed Citral #13 x Ice #2 to make their own fruit. Blue Power is one of Sin City Seeds’ indica-dominant signature strains, bred from Sour Double, Master Kush, The White, and Blue Moonshine genetics. Blue Power offers a sweet fusion of lemon and berry flavours with an earthy finish. This strain combination ( Papaya x Blue Power ) brings all the fruit to the table, tropical fruits are the initial flavours you will experience with a lingering berry profile left on the pallet during exhale. Upon opening this package you will get an overwhelming aroma of ripe Papaya! Our products are hang dried and hand trimmed. We pride ourselves in the use of whole flower for our pre-rolls and not just smalls, time is taken to remove all stems prior to milling to ensure a clean burning smooth smoking pre-roll second-to-none – smooth cannabis is what Dry Island is known for.

Name: TRIBAL Jigglers (Gelato x Red Pop)
description: Gettin' Jigglers wit' it! From Exotic Genetix, Jigglers is a sativa cannabis strain that crosses Gelato x Red Pop. Envision flavours and aromas of Strawberries & Cream. Jigglers combines that creamy, berry-fuel flavour of Gelato with an extra layer of creamy-sweetness from Red Pop. A true sensory experience, Jigglers smells sweet but tastes sour, some might say funky or tart.

Name: Cookies - TQ Sunrise Fat Boy 510 Cartridge Maximum THC! -
description: This TQ Sunrise Fat Boy 510 vape packs the maximum amount of THC (1000mg) in a cartridge. TQ Sunrise has a tropical, woodsy flavour with a bite of lime.

Name: TWEED Sparkling Lemonade
description: Find your bliss with Tweed Lemonade. Tangy, refreshing and sweet, Tweed Classic Lemonade with 7.5 mg of THC is bursting with flavour and refreshment. It is made with real juice, natural flavours and light bubbles.

Grown in small batches, hang dried and hand trimmed, we put a lot of effort into our strain selection, as well as the growing, drying and curing process of this flower. We grow our own. We manufacture our own. All strain specific. All for you.

Kush Life was selected for its incredibly unique flavour of cherry cough syrup balanced out by its strong aroma of gas. Our infused pre-rolls are made with whole flower and our in-house, solventless ice water hash. Name: DIVVY Sour Kush
description: Our Sour Kush is super smelly. Potent and high in terpenes, it’s an assertive flower with a terrifically tart and ultra-pungent aroma. Dense buds are peppered with orange pistils and coated in sparkling trichomes that hit the nose with a combination of sour lemon and invigorating pine. Its powerful flavour profile is just as tangy, balanced with hints of earth, wood and diesel.

Name: Highly Dutch Organic - Rotterdam Indica 7g
description: Highly Dutch's Rotterdam Indica is a high potency, strain-specific, rotating variety of some of the finest carefully grown cannabis flower. These terpene-rich, high-THC indica flowers deliver a strong aroma and rich flavour profile for the cannabis enthus

Name: BACK FORTY Liquid Imagination |28g
description: Let your imagination run wild with Back Forty’s latest cultivar – Liquid Imagination. A cross between Blue Zktlz x Jet Fuel Gelato, this potent hybrid boasts rich dark green buds adorned with orange pistils and chock-full of trichomes. With a flavour profile that blends sweetness with a pinch of gas, Liquid Imagination is a real treat for your senses.

Name: NUGZ G Sherb 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Hands to the ceiling and let the beat drop! Just don't fumble your Nugz Blueberry Haze Vape Cart! Brighten your palate with the Nugz line of high potency botanical-infused distillate vape carts, now offered in Blueberry Haze, with high potency & in-your-face fruit taste!

Name: NOYA Pound C 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Our Pound Cake vape cart is a distillate vape cart made with live terpene extract. This light gold concentrate has a sweet cake like flavour with a candied aroma. This product is formulated using our LPC75 strain, which is indica dominant. Utilizing high quality flower that can be found in some of the most prolific brands in the country, we've taken that same quality and shifted it to a 510 format.

Name: PURE LAINE Little Pleasures
description: This Little Pleasures is exactly that. Pure Laine cannabis arriving at your door like a pleasant surprise. You may not predict what it could be, but you can count on it being simple and nice.

Name: BOXHOT Peach OG 510 Thread Cartridge
description: BOXHOT PRESENTS: Peach OG, a 1.2 g 510 threaded vape, featuring 1000MG of THC and some of the purest cannabis distillate available on the market. This sweet beast boasts a sweet flavour, with a fruity aroma, complimented by a complex profile of earthy undertones that keep you guessing. All BOXHOT vapes are manufactured with exclusive, oversized hardware, making them optimized for big, full hits. Better yet, all BOXHOT vapes are produced with industry-leading CO2 extraction and refining processes, and feature an entourage of expertly infused premium strain-specific terpenes. All BOXHOT vape carts now work with auto-draw batteries!

Name: ADULTS ONLY Promicuous Peach NFSW Liquid Diamond 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Adults Only Promiscuous Peach NSFW liquid diamond cartridge. You can keep your options open but the Promiscuous Peach NSFW liquid diamond vape brought to you by Adults Only will be the cart to hold your attention. This hybrid 510 thread vape is packed with potent liquefied THC diamonds that have a burst of juicy peachy flavour. All Adults Only NSFW liquid diamond vapes are made using our advanced and industry leading BHO extraction equipment and processes. You won’t find any added solvents, pigments, fillers or waxes in this extract.

Name: STICKY GREENS Disti Sticks - Carnival Clouds Infused Pre Rolls | 3-Pack
description: These tasty pre-rolls are carefully infused with a distillate core and amped up with a delicious blend of naturally derived terpenes that match our best selling vape flavours. Meet Carnival Clouds, inspired by Cotton Candy Kush, these infused pre-rolls have all of the sweet, fruity and pillowy goodness that you love, without those dreadful sticky fingers.

Name: CONTRABAND GLUE99 Pre-Roll
description: Bred from Baby Gluey and C99 with plenty of spice and sour notes with hints of skunk.

Name: Pyptek Pocket Glass And Metal Pipe- Blue
description: No description available

Name: SHRED'EMS Cloudberry Snoozers CBN:THC Softchews
description: Don’t sleep on Cloudberry Snoozers! This new SHRED’ems features a unique cloudberry and hibiscus flavour profile, as well as some CBN for those seeking some minor cannabinoids in their THC soft chews. Cloudberry Snoozers are indica dominant and contain 10 mg of THC and 10mg of CBN per pack.

Name: WEATHERED ISLANDS CRAFT CANNABIS Haze-Drenched Sativa Seeds
description: Texada Island’s best kept secret is now available in a pack of feminized fast outdoor seeds, each carefully nestled in a compostable bag. Haze-Drenched Sativa was born and bred on Texada Island and remains a Weathered Islands exclusive. This extraordinary strain boasts lineage from a spectacular Lime Haze cultivar, crossed with a frosty island-bred Durban/diesel phenotype. Haze-Drenched Sativa is a crystalline sativa dominant gem, showcasing a one-of-a-kind terpene profile and boasting high THC content. Keep an eye out for our Texada Coastal pre-rolls that feature the Haze-Drenched Sativa and the Plum Kushwave.

Name: 3SAINTS Crumbled Lime
description: Get ready to pucker up, because Crumbled Lime is about to rock your world. 3Saints has once again delivered the goods with this powerful sativa as we continue giving you Potency without sacrificing taste. This bud doesn't hold back. With a deliciously sweet and citrusy lemon-lime flavour that gradually turns into a sour lime as you take more hits, Crumbled Lime is a force to be reckoned with. The aroma is an invigorating blend of earthy lime and sweet citrus. If you're a fan of bold, in-your-face flavours, you're going to love Crumbled Lime. This cultivar is the result of crossing Citron CKS with Biker Kush, and the result is a strain that packs serious potency.

Name: HIGHLAND GROW Apple Mintz Pre-Rolls
description: Shrouded in myth and legend, nobody truly knows the genetics of Apple Mintz. The only common ancestor people can agree on is sherbet. Other than that, whether it’s Pure Kush, Sour D, Zktlz or Apple Fritter, no one really knows. All we know is it tastes phenomenal with a sweet vanilla note backed by spice and fruit.

Name: VERSUS - Death Star | 28g
description: Versus Death Star is an indica-dominant flower, delivering heavy diesel with a slight citrus kick.

Name: BACK FORTY Banana OG | 28g
description: Settle in for a tropical, slow-burn with the delightful sativa that is Banana OG. Packed in a resealable pouch, and with a high THC potency. Take a trip, and explore the Back Forty with this cross between Banana Kush x OG Kush.

Name: Creature X SCS Hemp Trays - Small

Name: DAB BODS Baja Banana Disti Infused Joints
description: Dab Bods Baja Banana Disti Pre-Rolls brings the beaches, the deserts and the forests all together in a fruity sweet sensational banana packed pre-roll. This sativa-leaning hybrid, Banana Rntz, is a cross between Banana OG x Rntz and is an great way of bringing the effects of a sativa to cross over with the effects of an indica. Made from dried flower, distillate and all botanical terpenes.

Name: JONNY CHRONIC Acapulco Gold Live Resin All-In-One
description: Acapulco Gold live resin by Jonny Chronic is a sativa dominant strain with high THC and minimal CBD. It's made from dried Acapulco Gold flower and run through a closed loop column with butane. The end product is a highly potent extract with high terpene contents. Acapulco Gold should be stored in a cool dry place in the upright position when not in use. Rechargeable with a USB-C cable, not included.

Name: TRIBAL Galactic Rntz 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Tribal's Galactic Rntz live resin vape cart has one ingredient: our fresh frozen Galactic Rntz flower. The strong fuel flavour and fruity undertones are noticeably intense from this powerful indica dominant strain. Galactic Rntz is Falcon 9 (Sunset sherbet x Tina) and Runtz (Zktlz x Gelato), bred by Exotic Genetix. Galactic Rntz is best appreciated for its fruity flavour with tropical citrus and sour berry notes. Expect a matching aroma with hints of spicy pineapple.

Name: DIVVY- Roll Up Sativa Pre-Roll Sativa 1X0.5G
description: Roll Up and grab our current Divvy sativa dominant flower that’s ready to rumble whenever you are.

Name: VERSUS Sour Razzleberry Rapid Soft Chews
description: Versus Rapid Soft Chews are made with SōRSE® cannabis emulsion technology which delivers a rapid and consistent onset with almost no cannabis taste or smell. Five soft chews and 10 mg THC per pack.

Name: Holy Mountain - GMO Tropical Reign | 28G
description: Holy Mountain is embarking on a journey to more balmy climates with the introduction of GMO Tropical Reign. This sativa dominant bud is a descendent of GMO Crescendo and Super Tropical #100. The combined result yields cheesy, peppery and nutty aromas with just a light fruity backdrop. It might be described as a lighter and fruitier GMO Cookies. Don’t let the tropical vibes fool you, these buds are covered with a frost that matches Holy Mountains snowiest peaks.

Name: Dime Industries Wedding Cake Hybrid Rechargeable All in One Disposable Pen
description: Dime Industries is quickly becoming a leading cannabis brand because of its superior hardware, potent concentrates and delicious cannabis flavour profile. All Dime products have been vigorously lab tested and vetted by cannabis connoisseurs, ensuring everyone has the ultimate experience. You don’t need a special occasion to eat cake, especially not with this iconic Wedding Cake hybrid. A tried-and-true cross between Cherry Pie and GSC, you’ll fall so hard for this strain you might not even need a plus one. Deliciously subtle notes of cherry and strawberry paired with the boldness of vanilla and cream.

Name: IMPROMPTU HYBRID THC2 SPACE ELEVATOR 20 DELTA-8 THC:10 THC COLA
description: Experience THC squared! This extra-full-dose, crisp cola is naturally sweetened with cane sugar and combines 10mg of THC and 20mg of Delta-8 THC to create an extraordinary beverage like never before. Enjoy casual cannabis on a whole new level. Come on over, everyone’s welcome. This product contains delta-8 THC, a novel synthetic cannabinoid, that can produce a similar intoxicating effect as THC. If you experience adverse effects from this product, call Poison Control immediately at 1-800-268-9017.

Name: SEÑORITA Señorita
description: No description available

Name: Woody Nelson - Glade Runner Craft Flower 3.5g
description: The Woody Nelson edition of the Animal Cookies and Kush Mints #11 genetic was bred by Seed Junky Genetics and grown in an indoor vertical farm using living soil. This high THC cultivar is also rich in terpenes, including trans-caryophyllene, farnesene and beta-myrcene, and smells of green apple and cookie dough. The plant's colourful frosty buds are hand-trimmed and cured for a minimum of three weeks before packaging. Each glass jar includes whole flower and a Boveda humidity pack.

Name: BOXHOT HIGHLIGHTERS Alien OG All-in-One Disposable Pen
description: BOXHOT PRESENTS The Alien OG Highlighter, an all-in-one vape pen featuring some of the purest cannabis distillate available on the market. This extraterrestrial monster blasts you with gassy, earthy and lime flavours on the inhale, and leaves you with fruity pine on the exhale. BOXHOT Highlighters are equipped with rechargeable micro USB technology.

description: EastCann Mango Sour infused pre-rolls are made with a high THC sativa dominant hybrid of Sour Mango infused with bubble hash. This potent sativa has a distinct citrus and mango flavour profile. Mango Sour buds are dense with frosty trichomes, grown in small batches in organic living soil. EastCann bubble hash is a solventless and potent concentrate extracted with ice water and filter bags.

Name: CALI SLIMZ Tangie Sunset Pre-Rolls | 10-Pack
description: Tangie Sunset is a sativa dominant hybrid strain created through crossing the potent Jack Herer x Orange Crush strains. Tangie Sunset has a sharp citrusy flavour with a sour tangy exhale that has a savoury diesel kick. The aroma has a woody diesel overtone accented by zesty citrus effect as the buds are burned.

Name: D*GG LBS - Cryptic Chronic
description: Our legendary Cryptic Chronic, the bag is filled with buds that are thick and coated with trichomes, looking like they’re covered in fairy dust. The bag appeal is like nothing else – gassy, pungent, and earthy with a hint of sweetness. The buds are sticky icky with a dark purple colour and orange hairs. When you blaze it up, you’ll taste a smooth, sweet, and dank taste. This indica hybrid is the perfect choice for those looking for some classic west coast kush.

Name: MONJOUR BARE CBN Bedtime Blueberry Lemon Gummies
description: A dreamy blueberry complements lazy lemon with just the right balance. These delicious gummies each contain 20mg CBD, 7.5mg CBN and 2.5mg THC with no sugar coating and made with natural flavours.

Name: PORT NORTH Cherry Boat - Hand Rolled Ice Water Hash
description: Our hand rolled ice water hash is made solventless with zero additives. No mixing distillate or CO2 oil with tumbler kief made from waste material. Only high quality whole flower is taken and carefully frozen directly after harvest (this helps preserve delicate monoterpenes). After the flower is frozen we load small batches into a vessel that has been prepped with ice and water. The vessel creates a gentle water current that knocks off trichome heads. After a short gentle wash, we drain the trichome saturated water through micron specific mesh sieves. Once the heads are separated and collected from the ice cold water, they are placed in freeze dryers. Once fully dry, we meticulously hand roll each ball ensuring no cracks of any kind, helping prevent the inside from oxidation. Once finished, they are packaged into glass jars and placed in a cold storage area to cure. This hash is very delicate to temperature and must be stored in a cool and dry place to maintain its consistency.

description: A name like Motorbreath isn't given, it's earned. This strain is famously pungent, evoking an aroma that can only be described as industrial-strength chemical diesel. Its flavours are impressively distinct as well, with powerful notes of citrus, earth, diesel and garlic. Shipped in a black glass jar with a humidity pack, Motorbreath is characterized by spade-shaped minty green buds with thin long orange hairs and a coating of super frosty amber crystal trichomes. Top Leaf prides itself on carefully crafted cannabis cultivars with rich full-bodied flavour and complex terpene profiles grown to exacting standards and cured for 28 days in the heartland of Alberta.

Name: Elements Rice KS Slim Rolling Papers
description:
Elements Ultra Thin King-Size (KS) Slim Rice Rolling Papers comes with each pack containing 32 papers.
These rolling papers burn with zero ash, except for a tiny line of residue from the Acacia gum (sugar gum) turning into caramel as it burns!

Name: PURE SUNFARMS Gold Face | 3.5g
description: Gold Face is a BC-grown cultivar from the Pure Sunfarms greenhouse. This aromatic sativa is a pheno-hunted cross of Animal Face x Electric Grapefruit, with bright and juicy fruit punch aromas from dominant terpenes caryophyllene and pinene. These vibrant green and golden buds are chunky and dense, frosted in sticky trichomes. BC bud, hand harvested, hang dried and hand finished.

Name: SAN RAFAEL '71 Moon Berry Pre-Rolls
description: Moon Berry Pre-Rolls come packed with San Rafael ‘71’s own original Moon Berry balanced strain. Bred from MedReleaf’s Vespera and Equiposa, Moon Berry delivers a balanced 1:1 amount of THC to CBD along with rich flavour notes of berries, cream and  lemon. Each pre-roll pack includes a humidity pack to ensure freshness and housed in a compact, smell-proof doob tube. Each pre-roll is expertly rolled and packed with only the finest milled whole flower, never shake.

Name: CANACA Headbanger | 7g
description: Throw up the horns for Headbanger. With high THC, this sativa absolutely shreds and features amped-up earth, fruit and gas aromas. This Biker Kush x Sour cross is hang-dried, hand trimmed and carefully cured for an ultra-potent and irresistible flavour with a consistent burn. The buds are tight and dense with purple flecks and excessive trichome coverage. Advanced production techniques and cultivation expertise allow us to produce an intense expression of Headbanger with an enhanced sour and citrus flavour profile, high potencies. Featuring dominant terpenes of caryophyllene, limonene and fenchone dominant terps – you’ll want to experience an encore.

Name: KRONIC Island Pink
description: Discover the allure of Island Pink Kush famously known as Tom Ford Pink Kush, a potent Canadian Indica. Bred from a cross of Death Bubba and Pink Kush, this strain offers a sweet honey aroma complimented by hints of warm wood and subtle earthy undertones. The buds are adorned with orange and pink pistils peeking through a coating of sticky white trichomes. Grown in Toronto, this strain was pheno-hunted in-house by our team. Where all strains are hang dried, hand trimmed and never irradiated! We take pride in flushing each crop for 10-14 days, ensuring a smooth taste and a clean burn every time.

Name: GENERAL ADMISSION Melon Mania Distillate Infused Pre-Rolls
description: Sourced from quality whole flower cultivars, infused with our signature distillate and dusted in kief. Melon Mania brings cantaloupes bursting with juicy melon flavour. Fresh and floral aroma that toes the line between delicate and in-your-face sweetness. If you think you’re not into cantaloupe, you just haven’t tried Melon Mania yet.

Name: THE REPUBLIC The Republic Reserve 25 Plus Pre-Rolls
description: Discover The High Society Pre-Rolls by The Republic, where exceptional quality and value converge for a top-tier dank experience. Designed for the elite, these pre-rolls promise a supreme smoking journey with a premium indica-dominant flower and  potent THC.

Name: Cookies - E85 Pre-roll
description: E85 is a hybrid strain bred by Grandiflora Genetics and Cookies that holds a pungent gas and fruity dessert scent paired with an earthy, gassy and cakey sweet aroma. E85 produces dense buds with flecks of dark purple and green, and a medley of fiery orange hairs.

Name: D*gg lbs Cryptic Chronic Blunt | 2x0.5G
description: Cryptic Chronic hemp wrap blunts feature ceramic tips for an elevated experience. Cryptic Chronic is a premium craft cannabis strain that embodies the laid back lifestyle of the West Coast and old school hip hop. This indica dominant cultivar is the perfect choice for those who appreciate the finer things in life and enjoy top quality cannabis. This strain offers dense buds with a sweet and dank aroma that packs a serious punch. Slide this fan favourite into your regular rotation.

Name: Holy Mountain - I.C.C. 3.5g
description: Legendary strain ICC has entered the chat. This mighty miracle bud is seeping with aromas of gas, spice and sweet vanilla, thanks to its cake-heavy lineage. Indica-dominant. Can you say immaculate confection?

description: Classic Station House pre-rolls made from whole flower Amnesia Haze. A sativa with crisp, fresh aromas of pine and citrus. Machine rolled and packed just right for the perfect burn, every time. Precisely weighed and machine rolled for an ideal, even burn. Packed with a humidity device to extend freshness. Quality cannabis, everyday fares.

Name: PISTOL AND DYMOND 2.0 Pink Panties Diamonds & Sauce
description: Pink Panties Diamonds & Sauce is a special release between 2 of BC's well recognized legendary LPs, Dymond Concentrates and Pistol & Paris. Pink Panties is grown in-house by Pistol & Paris, and gets its name from the pink hue observed on the ripened trichomes. This strain is indica-dominant, consisting of a cross between Burmese Kush x Florida Kush. Once this strain reaches peak ripeness, it is cultivated and flash frozen before being shipped to Dymond Concentrates extraction labs where it is further refined into a caviar. This potent collaboration results in a deliciously gassy mixture of THCA diamonds and strain specific terpene sauce, created with the consumer being top-of-mind. A fantastic addition to your ultra-premium smoking experience.

Name: ADULTS ONLY Titillating Tangerine Magnum 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Introducing the biggest tease of them all, the hefty Titillating Tangerine Magnum vape from Adults Only. This sativa 510-thread distillate vape is housed in a premium extra-large cartridge. Complex flavours of tart tangerine and citrus fruits will have you begging for more of this delicious extract. All Adults Only Magnum vapes use exceptional extract that is made with our advanced and industry-leading CO2 extraction equipment and processes paired with only the most carefully crafted terpene profiles.

Celebrated for its potent effects with a unique aroma and flavour attributed to a combination of terpenes, including myrcene, caryophyllene, pinene and limonene. These terpenes contribute to the strain's herbal, spicy, pine-like and citrusy notes, enhancing the overall sensory experience. Prepare to be enchanted by Purple Haze, an iconic choice for those seeking a memorable cannabis encounter.

Name: KRONIC Super Silver Haze Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: Super Silver Haze is a classic sticky sativa-dominant strain, and one of many precious gems we acquired in the Legacy market. Bred in the 90's by Greenhouse Seeds, Super Silver Haze combines Skunk, Northern Lights, and Haze genetics. It was the first prize winner at the High Times Cannabis Cup in 1997, 1998, and 1999. Lime green buds come dusted in a heavy layer of sticky trichomes. The flavour palette is a delightful fusion of spice, skunk, and citrus with an aroma to match. Grown in Toronto, this strain was pheno-hunted in-house by our team. Where all strains are hang dried, hand trimmed and never irradiated! We take pride in flushing each crop for 10-14 days, ensuring a smooth taste and a clean burn every time.

Name: MTL CANNABIS Sage n' Sour | 3.5g

Name: ONE WORLD CANNABIS LA Kush Cake Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: LA Kush Cake pre-rolls in a pop top tube. It’s an indica-forward hybrid, the result of a cross between Wedding Cake and Kush Mints. Indoor hybrid greenhouse grown by our friends at Kusa Farms Ltd.

Name: Versus Black Cherry Rapid Seltzer | 355ML
description: Versus Black Cherry Seltzer is made with SōRSE® cannabis emulsion technology, which delivers a quicker onset with almost no cannabis taste or smell. With 10 mg of THC, this carbonated beverage tastes clean, crisp and refreshing.

Name: BUD LAFLEUR Banana Daddy
description: Banana Daddy is an indica strain with a high THC potency potential made by crossing Granddaddy Purp x Banana Hammock R1. Dense, chunky bud structure, deep purple and green buds coated with frost-like trichomes, Banana Daddy delivers fruity aromas with a light diesel finish. The dominant terpenes are myrcene, ocimene and alpha-pinene. Grown indoors in Pointe-Claire, Quebec, we hand harvest, whole plant hang dry, hand trim and slow cure.

Name: GENERAL ADMISSION Magic Melon Hybrid (1:0) 510 Thread Cartridge

Made with our signature triple-distilled distillate and boosted with botanical terpenes – these 510 thread cartridges deliver smooth hits, high THC potency, and the big, bold flavours you expect from GA!

This is an unethical amount of tropical tastiness from two mouthwatering flavours that can be enjoyed on their own or twisted into a third unique flavour with the push of a button. It’s mango madness enough with Mango Passionfruit, then they added the outlandish orange of Guava Sunrise and let you create a tropical flavour tornado on demand? Unspeakably delicious. But we’ll let it go this time. Oh, and Twisted vapes are rechargeable with 1.2g of extract, 1,000mg THC and 7% flavouring.

Name: SPINACH Atomic Sour Grapefruit 510 Thread Cartridge

Terpenes like alpha-humulene, pinene and terpinolene combine to deliver an over-the-top explosive flavour of sour-citrus. Our proprietary cold-filtered extract, distilled 4x through sub-zero temps, ensures ASG’s flavour and consistency.

Name: Organnicraft - Axess 3.5g
description:
Axess is a balanced hybrid strain released by Organnicraft. It offers a mellow high that is perfect for daytime use. This strain is a cross between two popular strains, Acapulco Gold and Sour Diesel. Its aroma is a blend of pine and citrus, and its flavor is earthy and sweet. Axess provides a balance of body and mind effects, making it a great choice for users seeking relaxation while remaining productive.
Organnicraft has released a new strain cross under the same name. Axess can also be a Slurricane x Kush Mints cross with Limonene , Germacrene and Pinene terpenes.

Name: PEPE Lemonatti | 28g
description:
Lemonatti is a classic in the North American market where citrus lovers dominate the cannabis landscape. This sativa marries a beautiful citrus bouquet with a delicate sweetness.

Created by crossing Gelonade and Biscotti, Lemonatti is a sativa that doesn’t disappoint when it comes to terpene content. Lemonatti delivers a flavour that can only be described as a lemon cookie topped with sweet and creamy lemon frosting. The product comes in a vacuum sealed bag with a humidity pack to ensure perfect moisture is maintained.

Name: KHUSHI Khushboo Pre-rolls | 3-Pack

Hunted for both potency and terpenes, the ninth plant in our extensive pheno-hunt proved to be the best expression of this exotic genetic. Expect strong blueberry and vanilla aromas and a sweet, candy and gas dry pull from these frosty buds. Craft designated and packaged in our compostable jars.

Name: CARMEL Studio 54 Solventless Infused Pre-Roll
description: Studio 54 was pheno hunted in-house and grown by Carmel. Bred by Deep East in California, Studio 54 is a cross of Sunset Sherbert x Pink Guava. Large dense spear shaped buds feature deep purple marbling and orange hairs. With this potent strain, expect flavours and aroma of guava, fuel and a little sherb. Because it’s the right thing to do, all of our flower is hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cold cured, and hand packaged. We believe fresh and terpy is best, so all our flower is packaged in a nitrogen flushed pouch with a humidity pack. Non-irradiated, obviously.

Name: RAD RESERVE Blue SKZ Infused Blunt
description: RAD Doobies Reserve Blue SKZ Infused Blunts offer a hella potent strain in a totally unique and convienient format, with an infused and flavoured distillate core. We only use the highest quality, fresh whole flower, never shake or trim, that's been skillfully crafted and rolled with premium hemp wraps. Find sweet and berry flavours with sour undertones with very high THC in this indica strain.

Name: VERSUS Blueberry Pomegranate Rapid Seltzer
description: Versus Rapid Seltzers are made with SōRSE® cannabis emulsion technology which delivers a predictable and consistent onset with almost no cannabis taste or smell. Containing 10mg THC, each can of this delicious carbonated beverage tastes clean and crisp.

Name: RIFF Crossfade Sativa Drop Pre-Roll
description: Get on a higher plane with Crossfade sativa Drops: fresher, hand-selected, expertly made. This is a carefully curated series of our top picks of top-shelf sativa genetics. A sensorial treat for extra potent experiences. Premium strains crafted to the highest standards, ‘cause otherwise it's not worth being on the shelf. Don’t sleep on these limited drops of exclusive pre-rolls though, because when they’re gone — they’re gone.

Name: SIMPLY BARE Insider's Cut |28g
description: Simply Bare Gas Series features pungent and gassy cultivars selected by our growers in Delta, BC. The cultivar in this series is fuelled with terpenes like myrcene, caryophyllene and limonene. However, when we feel it’s time to pump the breaks on this gas, and you’re ready to try something different, we’ll swap it out for something else. Every cultivar starts with our never irradiated whole bud that is cold cured to perfection.

Name: Pure Sunfarms - Sugar Cookies 28g
description: Sugar Cookies is an herbaceous hybrid featuring warm and cozy aromatics of sweet spice, citrus and a hint of gas with a creamy brown sugar finish. A cross of popular strains Cake Crasher and Jet Fuel Gelato, this Pure Sunfarms exclusive cultivar boasts high-THC and dense buds with a rich dusting of frosty trichomes. Grown in Pure Sunfarms sun-soaked greenhouse in the heart of BC’s Fraser Valley. Hand-harvested and freshly packed.

Name: TRUE FIRE Crispy Cream
description: Crispy Cream is an indica dominant hybrid that is the result of a carefully crafted cross between the delectable Glazed Donuts and Candy Cream. Name: FUEGO- Strawberry Cannacolada 510 Thread Cartridge Hybrid 1G
description: Fire up your summer with Fuego. This limited time offer combines a refreshing taste of strawberries, pineapple and coconut with high-potency cannabis extract in a quality 510 cartridge.

Name: 14" Proto Sandblasted Chrome Glass Bong
description: No description available

Name: KINGSWAY Splitshift Pre-Roll | 2-pack
description: Split Shift is a combination of the OG Kingsway pre-roll packs featuring both 'Dayshift' and 'Nightshift' pre-rolls in a convenient pack fit for every occasion. The pack contains 1 rotating single strain sativa-dominant flower (Dayshift) + 1 rotating single strain indica-dominant flower (Nightshift) providing consumers with two pre-rolls that cater to different usage occasions with a consistent THC.

Name: SHEEESH! Top Shelf
description: Sheeesh! Presents - Top Shelf! Taken from our Master Grower, Steve's Private Reserve is now available for a wider audience. These tasty jams are made from a hand-selected strain that was pheno-hunted and notable for it's exceptional flavours. Highlights hand-picked micro growers and Limited Release Strains.

Name: HONEY STICK- Concentrate Tool Set Silver
description: No description available

Name: Aurora Water Pipe by My Bud Vase
description: No description available

Name: LED Print Glowing Rolling Tray- Assorted Designs
description: No description available

Name: SILKY CONTINENTAL LA Wedding Pop | 3.5g
description: Our version of LA Wedding Pop is indica dominant hybrid strain created by crossing the delicious Wedding Cake and Triangle Kush BX2 strains. A powerful bud with a great flavour and high levels of THC. LA Wedding Pop buds have a sweet and sour citrusy grape flavour with a spicy, herbal and earthy aroma to match. This bud has airy small heart-shaped olive green buds with dark orange hairs and a coating of tiny purple-tinted white crystal trichomes.

Name: COMMUNITY- CURED RESIN HYBRID
description: Community Cured Resin is packed with a single-strain selection of our terpiest cured concentrates. This high-potency extract is made from cured flower, full of sun-grown flavour. The terpene-rich, aromatic flower is dried and then concentrated through CO2 extraction. The resulting cured resin is a full spectrum concentrate that relies on the flower’s natural terpenes, rather than botanical terpenes from non-cannabis sources. Community Cured Resin features a variety of strains from our passionate community of independent growers, curated by a brand that can be trusted by even the most sophisticated of value-seeking consumers.

Name: STICKY GREENS Bluntz - Honey Berry Infused Blunts
description: Sticky Greens Bluntz combine an old fashioned blunt with deliciously infused flower. We carefully infuse our blunts with a distillate core and naturally derived terpenes that showcase highly sought after blunt flavours. Honey Berry is true to its name and packed with pungent purple berry flavours followed by creamy honey and vanilla notes.

Name: SIMPLY BARE BC Organic White Rntz Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: Our BC Organic White Rntz is a FVOPA certified hybrid flower. This delicious, rare flower is a cross of popular Zktlz x Gelato cultivars. The sweet candy aromas are complemented with earthy, citrus undertones. Grown in living soil, hang dried for 14 days, cold cured and non irradiated. This is single strain, whole bud, milled to perfection and rolled with 100% organic hemp papers and finished by hand.

Name: SIMPLY BARE Craft Flight Pre-Rolls
description: The Simply Bare Craft Pack is your chance to try our indicas, sativas and hybrids in a pre-roll taster pack. Every three months, we drop a new craft pack containing our staple sativa, along with the two new limited edition cultivars of the season. Only a couple hundred of each combination will be created.

Name: PURE SUNFARMS Baked Animal | 3.5g
description: Baked Animal is a BC-grown cultivar from the Pure Sunfarms greenhouse. This potent hybrid is a cross of the widely popular Animal Face and smooth-smoking Baker’s Delight. Featuring sweet aromas of berries, cake, cream and light gas from dominant terpenes myrcene, caryophyllene and limonene. Its dense and colourful buds are rich with sugary trichomes. Pure BC bud, hand harvested, hang dried and hand finished.

Name: DEALR Galactica OG
description: Galactica OG is a rare indica-dominant hybrid grown in the Shuswap region of BC and created by crossing Jedi Kush x Saturn OG. The surprisingly pungent nose is dominated by skunk and fuel with a sweet earth finish. The flowers are round and emerald green with deep purple undertones and bright yellow orange hairs and a frosty coating of amber trichomes. Highly potent, this offering is aptly named Galactica, a beautiful BC grown Kush offering that connoisseurs will love.

Name: NUGZ Pheno Hunter | 15g
description: At Cannara, all of our exclusive genetics start with the pheno hunt. We sprout hundreds of seeds—a lengthy process where we flower out entire rooms of genetics that, up until today, we may not release. Introducing our Pheno Hunter bag! For those passionate canna-thusiasts looking for the new-new. Our Pheno Hunter offers limited drops of unique genetics from our gardens in a bulk offering perfect for those of us who like to get our hands on exclusive drops or for those who are a bit more DIY with concentrates. Get them while they’re hot!

Name: HIGHLAND GROW Dankarooz
description: Highland Grow’s indica dominant Dankarooz is a heavy hitting cross of Dank Dough and Rntz. The bright limonene nose is backed by an intense blueberry diesel that gives it a truly spectacular aroma and flavour profile. You don’t just smoke, you Dankarooz.

Name: BLK MKT Exclusives Pheno #1
description: Back by Popular Demand - the Exclusives Collection, where we bring you extremely limited R&D drops from our genetics portfolio, curated and dialled in by our Breeder & Master Growers. Always Handcrafted, from Our Genetics, Our Growers, and grown in Our Facilities. Graded & Hand Packaged to our Highest Standards.

Name: TRIBAL Drip Station Live Resin 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Tribal's new indica strain Drip Station smells like skunky rubber mixed with dew-soaked earth and pine trees. Coming from Legendary breeder Exotic Genetix, This strain is a cross of Greasy Rntz x Scotty 2 Hotty. We utilize a cryogenic BHO extraction process that preserves the profile of the flower and offers one of the highest levels of purity by preferentially extracting the cannabinoids, terpenes and flavonoids leaving behind all undesirable compounds. Our Drip Station Live Resin 510 vape cart is a premium product that delivers  a true to cultivar vape experience from inhale to exhale, with only one ingredient: fresh frozen flower.

Name: ODDBALL Dessert
description: A rotating strain-specific cultivar from your odd pals, geared to those who love dessert-like terpenes and what that brings to their cannabis experience. Dip into a quarter of bud that's ever-changing, just like your experience with cannabis is!

Name: FREEDOM CANNABIS Freedom Reserve - Sunrise Pre-Rolls
description: Freedom Reserve - Sunrise pre-rolls are a follow-up to the popular Freedom Reserve - Sunset product. 2%+ terpenes.

Name: BACK FORTY Sour Cherry 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Back Forty’s Sour Cherry 510 cartridge is a bold creation and captures the very essence of timeless cherry flavours, delivering an irresistible burst of sweetness complemented by a playful hint of tartness.

Name: INDIVA 1432 1:1 CBG/THC Milk Chocolate
description: Indiva 1432 chocolate is uniquely scored into pieces that are easy to break off, making dosing simple. Made with rich and delicious Callebaut chocolate sourced in Canada, each bite is creamy and smooth. This chocolate contains a 1:1 ratio of 10 mg of CBG and 10 mg of THC per pack. Indiva 1432 Chocolates offer a cannabis-free flavour with just the right amount of sweetness.

Name: ZELE Orange Sativa Craft Soda
description: Hovering down the street sippin’ on something bubbly and sweet. Take a succulent soul ride with Orange full-spectrum sativa craft soda, brewed with natural, vegan ingredients and 10mg of fast-acting, favourless THC. A refreshing blend of tangy and bright, experience this futuristic orange delight.

Name: GENERAL ADMISSION Crimson Toro Indica (1:0) Reachargeable All-In-One Vape
description: The Crimson Toro Rechargeable All-in-One Vape has the sweet and tangy flavours of blue raspberry and pomegranate. Made with our signature triple distilled distillate with botanical terpenes, this USB-C rechargeable all-in-one vape delivers smooth hits, high THC potency and the big, bold flavour you expect from G.A.

Name: 7ACRES Purple Pancakes Pre-Rolls |2-Pack
description: 7ACRES has developed an indica dominant cultivar with a unique combination of sweet cake, tropical fruit and fuel. 7ACRES Purple Pancakes was a result of a large genetic selection program with the goal of finding a novel strain. This particular phenotype stood out among the rest as it possessed both the sweet cake and fuel characteristics of Pancakes, along with a tropical fruit and berry from its Slurricane lineage.

Name: H&S- Dragon's Breath Indica Milled Flower 7G
description: Take a deep breath and set your senses ablaze with the savoury flavours of Dragon's Breath. The unique strain has funky and diesel aromas. Expertly milled for your roll, bowl or bong.

Name: PIFF Juicy Blunt
description: A classic blunt, the spice and fruit of our Maui Wowie compliments the vanilla notes of the wrap in a way that just works. The Juicy Blunt is proof that it doesn’t have to be complicated, just some sativa rolled up in a smooth burning blunt.

Name: COMMON GROUND Blueberry Muffin Blunt Pre-Roll
description: The Blueberry Muffin strain is an indica-dominant hybrid developed from Purple Panty Dropper crossed with Razzle Berry. This sungrown strain produces beautiful uniform buds highlighted with purple accents and frosted crystallized trichomes. Its freshly baked blueberry muffins aroma intoxicates the senses. We hang-dry and carefully cure our buds before preparing the blunts, and packaging them inside FSC-certified tubes. These are freshly sealed inside a 100% recyclable child-resistant pouch for optimal moisture content and shelf life.

Name: POTLUCK Blueberry Tart Pre-Roll
description: A twist on Canada's quintessential dessert, Blueberry Tart is a 50/50 balanced hybrid featuring delicious custard flavours followed by blueberry and subtle grape aromas, now available in a pre-roll format.

Name: NAKED MUMMER Cake Crasher Pre-Roll
description: These pre-rolls are in Naked Mummer branded cones. We use our in-house pheno of the popular Cake Crasher strain which was bred by the California breeder J-beezy from Seed Junky Genetics. The flower is full plant hang dried, cured, and trimmed. Our Cake Crasher pheno has a strong sweet and gassy aroma and taste with a smooth clean burn and white ash that is sure to delight.

Name: THE GREEN ORGANIC DUTCHMAN Organic Green Diesel  | 3.5g
description: TGOD™ presents a gassy and citrusy sativa dominant cultivar sustainably grown in living soil. Green Diesel has UK Cheese x (OG Kush x Burmese) lineage and offers very strong THC potency potential. High limonene content gives this lime green bud zingy flavour to match its fiery orange pistils.

Name: TASTY'S Strawberry Infused Pre-Rolls
description: Tasty’s Strawberry 50% THC Infused Pre-Rolls offer an unbeatable combination of THC and taste without breaking the bank. Each pack contains pre-rolls infused with powerful live resin diamonds for an incredible 50% THC. With an explosion of rich and sweet fruity flavours enhanced by botanical terpenes, Strawberry 50% THC Infused Pre-Rolls offer everything you crave at a price you’ll love.

Name: LUNCH Berry Bomb Disposable
description: Catch a flavour break with Berry Bomb, our 1.2g disposable indica vape. Jam packed with an explosive and surprising combination of berry flavours, you might even say it's the bomb.

Name: Beamer GRNDR Virgin Acrylic Detroit Logo 90mm 3-Pc Grinder
description: No description available

Name: XPLOR Jungle Fruit 510 Thread Cartridge
description: XPLOR your wild side with Jungle Fruit. Each draw provides a bouquet of tropical fruits and grape that will have you going ape. Combined with potent THC extract in a high-grade 510 cartridge to provide both novice and experienced users something new to explore.

Name: HOVER BEVERAGES Hover Lemon Iced Tea High
description: Enjoy the refreshing taste of Iced Tea with a hint of Lemon. Hover Lemon Iced Tea is both lightly carbonated & lightly sweetened and made with all natural flavours. Hover's High option comes with 10MG of THC and 10MG of CBD for a full-body, balanced experience.

Name: The Loud Plug - Frosted Swirl Live Resin 510 Thread Cartridge 1G
description: No description available

Name: VALHALLA FLWR Cosmic Cherry | 3.5g
description: Valhalla Flwr’s BC small batch Craft Cosmic Cherry is an indica strain created through crossing Wedding Cake x Wedding Crasher. This flower is grown indoors under the latest LED lighting in coco medium. It is hang dried, hand trimmed and cured to perfection. This flower comes non-irrigated in a nitrogen flushed package. Each bag is hand packed with individual humidity packs to ensure optimum freshness in our flower.

Name: SOLEI Peach Cranberry Cold Brew Tea
description: Peach Cranberry cold brew teas are tea-based, ready-to-drink cannabis infused beverages elevated with the juicy and natural flavours of peach and cranberry. Crafted with a black tea base, real fruit juices and only natural flavours – these recipes are enhanced with a balanced blend of 5 mg of THC and 10 mg of CBG.

Name: COLLECTIVE PROJECT 2:1 CBG Happy Place (Mango Peach & Yuzu)
description: Savour the taste of summer with every sip of our THC + CBG Mango Peach & Yuzu Juice. As the flavours unfold like a tropical paradise on your palate. Imbibe in the richness of mangoes, the sweetness of peaches, and the citrusy brightness of yuzu, all in one delightful can.

Name: MTL Cannabis - STRAWBERRY N' MINTZ PRE-ROLL Sativa 3x0.5g
description: MTL Cannabis Strawberry n' Mints has flowers with complex greens, interspersed with hints of red and orange. There is a thick layer of frosty trichomes that glisten. The main terpenes, myrcene, caryophyllene, help deliver a fresh berry flavour on the inhale, giving off an earthy, minty finish on the exhale.

Name: BOXHOT Alien OG 510 Thread Cartridge
description: BOXHOT PRESENTS: Alien OG, a 1.2 g 510 threaded vape, featuring 1000MG of THC and some of the purest cannabis distillate available on the market. This extraterrestrial monster blasts you with gas, earthy and lime flavours on the inhale, and leaves you with fruity pine on the exhale. All BOXHOT vapes are manufactured with exclusive, oversized hardware, making them optimized for big, full hits. Better yet, all BOXHOT vapes are produced with industry-leading CO2 extraction and refining processes, and feature an entourage of expertly infused premium strain-specific terpenes. All BOXHOT vape carts now work with auto-draw batteries!

Name: 6" Hemper Coco Mug Rig
description:
Enjoy the cozy ambiance of Christmas by the fire with the "6" Hemper Coco Mug Rig". Featuring a built-in handle and a classic mug shape, this rig adds warmth to your smoking routine. The hand-blown candy cane straw and honeycomb percolator with 40+ holes ensure smooth airflow, delivering flavorful hits even on chilly winter days. Just add fire, and let the Coco Mug rig elevate your spirits!

Specifications:

Height: 6 inches
Diameter: 2.6 inches
Percolator: Disc perc
Thickness: 3 mm

Name: GENERAL ADMISSION Peach Ringz Sativa 1:0 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Made for the masses, General Admission vapes are all about flavour. Big. Bold. Bringing people together. General Admission uses the power of taste to encourage moments of discovery for everyone to partake. We create quality THC distillate infused with botanical terpenes that complement the natural aromas of our strain selection. Peach Ringz is a sticky sweet and all-around sour burst of that classic slice of peach. Floral notes round out the sugary profile of this favourite strain, known for being exceptionally smooth and potent.

Name: ORIGINAL STASH OS.Funk Fuel Pre-Rolls
description: Gas guzzlers pay attention, Funk Fuel is legit. This is a premium pump and we’re only filling ‘er up with a blend of funky cheese and dirty diesel indica strains. These bags of flower and two-packs of pre-rolls belch fumes so funky you’ll think you’ve got a gas leak. We’re sure it’s fine, but know you’re getting that fire with these high THC buds. This is meticulously grown, carefully hang dried flower that’s worth taking down in flames.

Name: Station House- Sativa Daytime Express Pre-Roll 6X0.5G
description: Variety is the spice of life so why settle for one strain when you can have three classic strains? This unique pre-roll multipack gives you the best Station House sativa cultivars. Featuring two Blue Dream, two Amnesia Haze and two Ghost Train Haze. Always packed with a humidity device for extended freshness.

Name: THE LOUD PLUG- Benny Blunto Infused Pre-Roll 1X1G Indica
description: All that you've come to expect with Benny Blunto - now in an infused format!

Name: Weed Me - Mandarin Cookie Sativa 1G
description: Mandarin Cookie is a sativa-dominant hybrid with flavors of sweet, citrus and diesel. Expect an earthy kushy aroma with strong citrus overtones. Mandarin Cookie is made by crossing Forum Cut Cookies and Mandarin Sunset.

Name: Redecan - Animal Rntz Indica 3.5g
description: Animal Runtz is an indica-dominant strain that is the result of crossing Animal Cookies x Runtz. True to its lineage, Animal Runtz has a fruity tartness along with a sweet and sour aroma informed by high levels of caryophyllene, limonene, trans-ocimene and alpha-bisabolol. Sporting dense tight buds, this potent strain achieves remarkable THC levels. Animal Runtz by Redecan is improved through conscientious care and attention given to each plant through every stage of growth and harvested at its peak, expertly cured and hand trimmed to ensure the highest level of quality.

Name: NO FUTURE The Purple One Sativa THC Gummy
description: Isn't it funny that when you eat a real grape it tastes one way, then when you eat grape jelly or grape jam or grape juice it tastes nothing like the stuff we make wine from, but we still call that stuff "grape" whatever (insert food here)? It all somehow ends up tasting like candy and not the fruit at all! Wow, just wow.

Name: GOOD SUPPLY Pineapple Express Badder
description: What’s got a lab coat, safety goggles and a love for all things sticky icky? The brainiacs in our state-of-the-art hydrocarbon extraction facility, duh. Their latest obsession is turning our iconic Pineapple Express flower into a high terpene, full-spectrum, butane-extracted concentrate with a waxy, batter-like texture. The result? Pineapple Express Badder. We’re talking about a hype hybrid that hits with a haymaker of citrus, floral and caramel aromas that’s 5% terpenes, 75-85% THC and perfectly hand-whipped – all for a reasonable price. So, get on board with these high-impact extracts that are a true-to-strain representation of their Pineapple Express native flower, we’re sure you’ll feel real good about it.

Name: PURPLE HILLS Live Resin Infused Pre-Roll Taster Pack
description: Our Purple Hills Live Resin Infused Pre-Roll Tasters are a pack of three carefully rolled pre-rolls of hand-tended, sun-grown flower, infused with our terpiest live resin. Purple Hills genetics are identified to thrive in Creemore, Ontario microclimate and are carefully hand-tended throughout the season. Eco-conscious agriculture is a core tenet of Purple Hills and growing practices such as spring water irrigation and the use of natural soil amendments produced by free run farm animals have been implemented in this ongoing pursuit. The terpene-rich, aromatic flower is preserved through flash-freezing at harvest and then concentrated through hydrocarbon extraction. The resulting live resin contains all of the flower's natural terpenes and cannabinoids, delivering more cannabis flavour than CO2 or ethanol extracts. This three pack of live resin infused pre-rolls gives you the chance to taste each of the top three live resin flavours in the Purple Hills line-up in one pack.

Name: SPINACH GMO Cookies Pre-Roll
description: Don't let the name deceive you. GMO (Garlic, Mushroom, Onion) Cookies has an unmistakably sweet and savoury taste and is one of the most popular indica strains out there. You can't make a soup out of it, but it sure goes nicely in a bowl.

Name: SIMPLY BARE BC Organic Fruit Loopz Pre-Rolls | 5-Pack
description: Prepare your taste buds for an exciting product from the Simply Bare greenhouse. Our new BC Organic Fruit Loopz is a sativa dominant hybrid that's big on flavour. A cross of Blue Dream x White Widow, these two legendary cultivars collide to create a mouth watering product. Boasting fruity, berry and citrus notes, it's grown in living soil and is slowly hang dried and hand trimmed to preserve trichome integrity.

Name: COLLECTIVE PROJECT Original Blood Orange Yuzu & Vanilla Sparkling Juice
description: Our take on the classic treat, we added the bright flavours of Yuzu and Blood Orange together with sweet vanilla for a truly remarkable beverage. We then added cannabis citrus terpenes to round out the flavourful profile.

Name: VOLO Woof Walkers Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: Genetics make the difference and we have good genes. Each pack contains popular strains phenotype hunted and grown by Capulator himself. Each roll is made with whole flower only. Craft quality pre-rolls conveniently sized for portability.

Name: THE OZ CONFECTIONS CORP. Cookie Cake Pre-Roll
description: A species of cannabis that originates from South America, the Caribbean and Africa. The plants are normally taller and more slender than Cannabis indica

Name: C. Cereal Milk & Cèreal À La Mode Two-in-One Dual Chamber AIO
description: This All-in-One dual chamber vape is a potent show-stopper, packing style and two iconic flavours in the palm of your hand. Cereal Milk has a creamy and fruity flavour with a hint of gas, while Cereal Milk A La Mode is creamy with a sweet nutty cookie flavour with touches of fresh strawberries. The simple click of a button allows you to switch between these two flavours or to blend them together at the same time. Hardware created by the innovators at 14TH ROUND and designed for a top tier experience.

Name: OCB Premium King Slim Papers & Filter
description: No description available

Name: SENSIMILA Craft Collection - Sativa
description: The Craft Collection by Sensimila is a premium whole flower for connoisseurs seeking a high quality, hand crafted product. With new strains to be introduced throughout the year, Craft Collection offers a diverse range of rare legacy genetics. Selected cultivars for Sensimila Craft Collection are grown without pesticides or harmful chemicals, hang-dried, hand-trimmed, cured, never irradiated, hand-packaged and nitrogen flushed to preserve optimal flavour, taste and aroma. All Sensimila packaging is made with high quality eco-friendly recycled plastics. Each bag includes industry leading two-way 62% humid packs from Integra Boost.

Name: SPINACH Frosted Cream Puffs | 28g
description: Dive into a baker’s bowl of frosting, sweetness and colour with this decadent and frosty flower. With crystal clear buds and creamy flavours, Frosted Cream Puffs takes you on a delicious journey. With lineage that traces back to Snow Lotus and GSC, this cultivar hits when it comes to looks, tastes and smells. Caked with stick-to-your-fingers trichomes, this cultivar is a delicious delight with classic terpenes such as limonene, caryophyllene and humulene.​

Name: Organnicraft- Axess Pre-Roll Hybrid 2X0.75G
description: Organnicraft Axess pre-rolls is a rotational SKU of unique cultivars. We are always on the hunt for new unique genetics and flavour profiles to showcase our hands-on craft growing style. Axess is a chance for consumers to try our favourite picks of the moment. Hemp papers are rolled in batches of 100. Every pre-roll is individually inspected before it is hand packaged, true to the craft ideology.

Name: ABIDE+WHOLEHEMP CUSTOM BLENDS 10:4 Pre-Rolls | 5-Pack
description: ABIDE+WholeHemp 10:4 Pre-Rolls are a custom blend of ABIDE’s OG Haze and WholeHemp’s Premium CBD Flower. Each package contains pre-rolls with a consistent cannabinoid profile. 10:4 Pre-Rolls are made from premium flower (never trim), hand selected from the finest sungrown high THC and CBD flower and blended to deliver a consistent 2.5:1 THC:CBD ratio. ABIDE+WholeHemp 10:4 Pre-Rolls are wrapped in Pure Hemp cones and packaged in an eco-friendly, recyclable cardboard box.

Name: XPLOR Funky Monkey Indica Pre-Rolls | 2-Pack
description: Get you funk on with Funky Money pre-rolls! With a unique strain of gassy and funky aromas, our pre-rolls are sure to drive your senses bananas!

Name: SWEET VENGEANCE Pandora's 2 Pac Pre-Roll
description: Only the highest quality strains are selected for this product. Each pack consists of 2 single strain pre-rolls that has been selected based on high THC, white ash, aroma, indica effect, flavour, and flower quality.

Name: PAPA'S HERB Indica Astro Pink Saucy Diamond Disposable
description: Papa's Herb Astro Pink, a premium strain renowned for its impressive potency and rich flavour profile. Delight in the harmonious blend of earthy and floral notes, accentuated by subtle hints of vanilla, for a truly captivating smoking experience. Enjoy it in a premium Papa's Herb disposable, come to Papa!

Name: MUSKOKA GROWN Power Pack
description: Love Muskoka grown but can’t decide which indica flavours you like best? Try the Twofer and you don’t have to decide. We’ve taken Lakeside Kush and Sugar Cookies and combined them into one convenient pack. The Muskoka grown Twofer gives you the variety of two flavours.

Name: DAB BODS Pineapple Express Super Slim Electric Dartz Pre-Rolls
description: Dab Bods Electric Dartz bring to you an explosion of flavour in an easy to consume straight style pre-roll.  Sharing with you a delicious pineapple aroma in a sativa-leaning hybrid strain of Pineapple Express.  We have homogenized this gorgeous fluffy bud with a mix of all natural terpenes, making these little darts anything but a pre-roll.

Name: BUD LAFLEUR Bud's Black Hash
description: Bud's Black Hash is crafted using our top-quality sativa-dominant flower that is grown indoors, dry sifted, hand pressed and hand packaged. Produced with our in-house strains, this rich, flavourful, high-grade hash has a very strong THC potency potential. Shiny black on the outside, brown on the inside, resinous, malleable yet firm, it features pungent and earthy aromas.

Name: BEURRE BLANC. Carte Blanche Pure Live Rosin Honeydew 510 Cartridge
description: La Crème de la Crème. Carte Blanche Live Rosin 1g Vape Cart by Beurre Blanc. provides a true-to-flower experience, retaining all the cannabinoids, terpenes, and flavonoids derived from the Honeydew cannabis flower. Honeydew is a sativa-dominant cultivar oozing with sweet floral flavours and light citrus scents reminiscent of wildflower honey. Live rosin is made from fresh-frozen flower. Our Hashmakers use ice water to separate trichome heads from plant material, then freeze-dry to remove water. Once fully dehydrated, the oils are squeezed out with a rosin press and transformed into cart-stable liquid live rosin through our proprietary pressure tech process. The liquid live rosin is then deposited into a cart specially designed for low-temperature vaporization.

Name: TERRA LABS Blueberry Avalanche Live Resin Diamond Vape
description: The Blueberry Avalanche Liquid Diamond THC vape cart is a 510 thread cartridge that contains highly potent diamonds, expertly extracted to preserve the full spectrum of cannabinoids and terpenes. Infused with natural blueberry botanical terpenes, it delivers a sweet and fruity aroma and taste. Each draw is smooth and consistent, thanks to the advanced ceramic heating element. The sleek, discreet design of the cartridge ensures portability and ease of use.

Name: MONJOUR Me-time Mango | 30-Pack
description: Take some me time with Me-Time Mango CBD soft chews from monjour. This delicious sugar coated soft chew contains 50 mg of CBD each. Me-Time Mango soft chews feature a delicious mango and strawberry flavour.

Name: SPINACH Blue Dream Pre-Roll
description: Spinach™ products are not your average greens! Spinach has High Expectations™ for their Farm-to-Bowl™ products, and safety testing is one of the few things they take seriously. This sweet sativa is known for its herbal, pine and peppery aromas that come from the cultivars’ terpene profile rich in pinene, myrcene and caryophyllene. Available in multiple pre-rolls and dried flower formats that are perfect for sharing!

Name: SHATTERIZER 8 Ball Kush Shatter Double Infused Pre-roll
description:
We’re thrilled to roll out new innovation to our shatterizing family: the 8 Ball Kush Shatter Double Infused Pre-Roll. Made with love in Ontario and with 8 Ball Kush flower, infused with 8 Ball Kush Shatter, our Shatterizer Pre-Roll is double the 8 Ball Kush and then double infused and double rolled.
 
 This joint is Shatterized, rolled up and then rolled in Kief for double the Kushy Kushy pre-rolled #PerfectClouds. Tripling the trichomes with flower, shatter and kief is a combination you can bank on for the highest quality of flavours and potency.
 
 Our 8 Ball Kush Indica, grown from King Kush and Bubba Kush, is an herbaceous garden of terpenes, that will sink into your mouth and call the shots! Using the highest levels of science, tech and quality extraction methods and fresh cannabis inputs selected from the finest in Canada, we are pleased to welcome our NEW 8 Ball Kush Shatter Double Infused Pre-Roll to the Shatterizer Family!

Name: * HIGH VALUE Sativa Pre-Rolls | 10-Pack
description: You can have it all with High Value. Delivering quality, potency and value in every pack, High Value is about getting a quality smoke without any hassle. The High Value pre-roll contains a high potency, single strain sativa pre-roll made from whole flower. Machine rolled and hand finished in classic cones, High Value delivers some of the best bang for your buck when it comes to cannabis.

description: EVIDENCE Prison Pre-Rolls are infused pre-rolls made with a curated blend of whole flower, no shake, trim or stems! Infused with high terpene flavourful kief for a balanced taste and extra THC kick. Prison Pre-Rolls are made with our proprietary infusion technique and filled in unbleached hemp cones that keep the whole pre-roll homogeneous for a perfect even burn. We grow our own. We extract our own. We manufacture our own. All strain specific. All for you.

description: Wyld Sour Apple Sativa Enhanced THC gummies are sustainably made using real fruit, botanical terpenes and natural flavour. Each gummy contains 5mg THC, for a total of 10mg THC per pack. All Wyld gummies are packaged in an all-new compostable pouch, and our recipes are formulated by food scientists to provide consistent experiences that taste amazing. Wyld gummies use sunflower lecithin to improve bioavailability and onset time and are made to be thermostable up to 60°C, with a firm texture that doesn’t stick to your teeth. Each Sour Apple Sativa Enhanced gummy contains the terpenes limonene, valencene, alpha-pinene, and beta-pinene for an energetic and uplifting experience. This is a terpene-packed, juicy fruit of a strain into your melon. We guarantee you’ve never seen a melon like this, purple flecked with oversized trichomes on beautifully solid buds. Name: ASTROLAB Cold Cured Lightspeed Live Rosin

This flower is big on the gassy and sweet and sour aromas and gets a nice gentle complement of pine. These light green buds flecked with orange pistils are made up of dominant terpenes limonene, beta-caryophyllene and myrcene.

Name: SIMPLY BARE Organic Live Rosin Softgels
description: Get the full spectrum experience with our Live Rosin Softgels. These organic 10mg softgels come in a pack of 30, and will contain input from one of our many organic cultivars. Each softgel starts with our flower, hand trimmed and grown in living soil, then expertly pressed into Live Rosin and packed into softgels.

Name: T 2.0 Headstash Kush | 3.5G
description: Headstash Kush is an indica-dominant hybrid strain that offers complex fruity flavours with an alluring diesel twist thanks to its parents Sour Headstash x Biker Kush. With dense green bud covered in vibrant orange hairs, this terpene filled strain will pack a punch.

Name: Color Cannabis- Mango Haze Pre-Rolls 10X0.35G - sativa
description: Color Mango Haze Pre-Rolls are perfectly packed with gently milled flower, not trim or shake, to ensure each pre-roll contains the freshest and most flavourful cannabis possible. A balanced CBD/THC cultivar that is rich in flavour, its bountiful terpenes of p-cymene, myrcene, pinene, and beta-caryophyllene give this cultivar its signature mango scent. Mango Haze is a sativa-dominant hybrid that produces a mild THC potency potential with genetic cross between Northern Lights, Skunk, and Haze. Our Color Cannabis Pre-Rolls use flower that have been harvested with care, dried naturally, gently milled and then packed into the perfect size pre-roll. Each unit comes with single session size pre-rolls, weighing 0.35g each now available in a convenient 10 pack size.

These ultimate sour peach soft chews are what you're missing. They're tasty, sweet, sour and just peachy! You'll ap-peach-iate every chewy bite you'll get.

Name: LEMON AND GRASS Multi-Pack Sunset Gelato & OG Kush Live Terpene 510 Cart
description: The multi-pack includes our Sunset Gelato and OG Kush Live Terpene 510 cartridges. Utilizing fresh flower to craft a blend of ultra premium live resin terpenes with high quality distillate for a flavourful vaping experience. Sunset Gelato offers a bright tropical fruit aroma profile. Get a robust hint of gas and citrus with the infamous OG Kush.

Name: OHJA Truffle Breath Pre-Rolls | 10-Pack
description: Truffle Breath is a true hybrid sativa. This strain has an incredible lineage: Peanut Butter and Gorilla Butter. This bud has a skunky, caramel and gassy flavour with an earthy and pungent aroma to match. Truffle Breath buds are tapered spade-shaped forest green with lots of thin orange hairs and a coating of frosty, chunky and milky white crystal trichomes.

Name: Weed Me - Kush Quads  Indica 3.5g
description: No description available

Name: SHRED - Funk Master | 14g
description: Now you’ve got even more chances to discover the medley to Funky town. We've captured the essence of real dank buds with skunky, gas and earthy aromas that truly bring the funk. Get down and get dank with Funk Master at 20%+ THC and a humidity pack included in every pouch.

Name: PAPA'S HERB Sativa Fruit Punch Liquid Diamond Disposable
description: Papa's Fruit Punch, is a rechargeable disposable vape. High in potency and the perfect portable vaping experience for those looking for a deliciously fruity and high potency vape. Fruit Punch is packed with high-potency liquid diamond cannabis oil made from Melted Diamonds. Papa’s Fruit Punch strain is known for its fantastic flavour and potent effects. With each puff, you'll savour the sweet- sweet taste of delicious Fruit Punch – a sativa-dominant strain made by crossing Skunk x Haze x Northern Lights. Named after it’s deliciously sweet, fruity, and tropical flavours.

Name: THE LOUD PLUG Splitter | 28g
description: Why limit yourself to one strain when you can have two? Introducing The Loud Plug’s Splitter – bringing you the best of both worlds! With 2 strains of rotational flower, this bag is an elite bundle. Conveniently split down the middle, our packaging gives you the freedom to mix things up. Whether you choose one, the other, or combine the two in a dank salad, the choice is yours. We take pride in slow curing and hang-drying our flower, ensuring a top-tier experience in every hit. If you're all about variety and options, this bag is your go-to. With love from Scarborough.

Name: Homestead - Bangtail Milled Hybrid 7G
description: Our high-quality Bangtail Milled cannabis offers easy-to-roll single-strain flower at an accessible price point. Featuring a rotating selection of cultivars, all flower used in Bangtail Milled is hang-dried for optimal flavour.

Name: PURE SUNFARMS- Blueberry Kush High THC 510 Thread Cartridge Indica 1G
description: No description available

Name: CROOKED DORY Mint Smash
description: Mint Smash is a hybrid strain made by crossing Kush Mints x Hawaiian Tropics #4. This is a high THC strain with a unique minty taste. When you open a bag of Mint Smash you will be greeted with notes of citrus and berries combined with hints of tropical flowers. Mint Smash is known for its unique flavour and potent sativa effects, boasting a high THC range.

Name: TRURO Jealousy x Apples & Bananas | 7g
description: Jealousy x Apples & Bananas by Truro is a potent legacy indica dominant hybrid. Jealousy is a 50/50 hybrid strain produced by crossing Sherbet Bx1 with Gelato 41. Compound Genetics and Cookies collaborated to create Apples & Bananas, a combination of a Platinum Cookies and Granddaddy Purple hybrid with a Blue Power male. They crossed the resulting hybrid with Gelatti to create Apples & Bananas. The flavour profile is earthy and gassy with hints of spice. Jealousy x Apples & Bananas is proudly grown on the East Coast in Truro, Nova Scotia in our state-of-the-art small batch production facility, where each bud is carefully cultivated, hang dried, hand trimmed, slow cured (21-28 days) and hand packaged in 100% recyclable aluminum cans that are purged with liquid nitrogen to preserve the dried flower quality, moisture content and terpene profile for the ultimate craft cannabis experience.

Name: ADULTS ONLY Missionary Mango NSFW Diamond Coated Infused Pre-Rolls

These indica diamond coated pre-rolls are packed with potent liquefied THC diamonds that have a sultry sweet and exotic mango flavour. All Adults Only NSFW liquid diamond vapes are made using our advanced and industry-leading BHO extraction equipment and processes. You won’t find any added solvents, pigments, fillers or waxes in this extract.

Name: Table Top - City Slicker | 14g
description: Dust off those leather chaps because TABLE TOP™ City Slicker just saddled up to the dude ranch. It’s an evenly balanced hybrid with Gelato 33 and Stardawg lineage, very strong THC potency potential and ginger, citrus, spicy and garlic flavours. That should put some hair on your chest. It’s Got Legs™.

Name: Doja - Ucorn Cake Hybrid 3.5g

Take a chance, and perhaps you will get the opportunity to indulge in a small-batch never before seen Steel City cultivar, or maybe an aromatic fusion of complimentary strains. Each pouch of Loot Bag Grind contains whole flower milled to perfection for easy rolling, packing, baking or vaping. Our cannabis is harvested from our indoor, state of the art climate-controlled cultivation rooms ensuring consistent quality and freshness. Our pre-shredded (pre-ground) cannabis is packaged fresh, includes a humidity pack, and never requires or undergoes irradiation or other microbial elimination processes.

Name: Tweed - Wedding Cake | 28G
description: Tweed Wedding Cake is an indica strain with high THC and minimal amounts of CBD. Wedding Cake comes from a cross of Cherry Pie x GSC. Its buds are known to be dense and lime green, with hits of orange.

Name: RIZZLERS Rizz Dispenser

Name: 1SPLIFF Orange Rntz Pre-Rolls | 7-Pack
description: Orange Rntz pre-rolls are a true treat for cannabis connoisseurs and enthusiasts alike. With its high citrus lemon flavour and aroma profiles, this strain is sure to pack a punch that you won’t forget. The secret to Orange Rntz’s potency lies in its carefully selected blend of African Orange and Rntz strains. Orange Rntz flower is carefully hand-harvested, hang-dried, hand-trimmed and cured for a total of 21 days to ensure the highest quality and consistency in every pre-roll. Each pre-roll is packed with resin-filled buds. At 1Spliff, we believe in providing our customers with the best cannabis experience possible. Our pre-rolls are easy to use and offer a consistent, high-quality smoking experience every time.

Name: LITTI. Gulupa Gulp All-In-One Vape

It contains guarana for kick, it's non-carbonated for exceptional smoothness and contains potent THC and CBG cannabinoids. Straight with Banana Brain Freeze on ice or rock it chilled right out of the can. The choice is yours.

Name: BUD LAFLEUR Obi Star Pre-Roll
description: Obi Star is an indica dominant strain with a strong THC potency made by crossing Skywalker x OG Kush. With large cone-shaped lime green buds, Obi Star features citrus and earthy aromas. The dominant terpenes are terpinolene, myrcene and limonene. Grown indoors in Pointe-Claire, Quebec, we hand harvest, whole plant hang dry, hand trim, slowly cure cold for a minimum of 14 days and hand package. Our pre-rolls are prepared using our whole flower (never trim), finely milled, filled in 98 mm wood pulp paper, natural brown cone, not bleached, non GMO, using organic arabica gum, 26 mm W tip and burn white to light gray with a slow to medium burn rate.

Name: DANK CRAFT Space Cake | 7g
description: Carefully crossed from GSC and Snow Lotus, Dank Craft Space Cake is high in terpenes and THC. It delivers a creamy flavour profile backed up by bright notes of fruit and berries.

Name: MTL CANNABIS East Coast Dank'z Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: East Coast Dank’z is an indica strain that brings powerful notes of gas for the nose and taste buds alongside peppery spice to create a piquant flavour profile that’s balanced with hard candy sweetness. The flower itself is compact, expressing an array of bright greens with a flourish of amethyst, making it as nice to look at as it is to smoke.

Name: Pure Sunfarms - Pink Kush Indica - 14g
description: Pure Sunfarms’ cut of Pink Kush from BC’s Vancouver Island is a coastal relative of the legendary OG Kush. This special strain is beloved across Canada for its strong aromas, colourful flowers, and high THC potential. Beneath a thick coating of trichomes, the dense and round buds feature forest green leaves, often with a purple hue, mixed with dark amber pistils. Grown in a high-tech greenhouse in the Fraser Valley, each bud is carefully trimmed and hand-groomed, dried and cured to precise standards. Pink Kush showcases gassy aromas of white pepper, orange, butterscotch, coffee, earth, and grapefruit, the result of a rich combination of terpenes that includes caryophyllene, myrcene, humulene, bisabolol, and limonene.

Name: TASTY'S Mango Infused Pre-Rolls
description: TASTY’s Mango THC Infused Pre-Rolls offer an unbeatable combination of THC and taste without breaking the bank. Each pack offers pre-rolls, infused with ultra-potent THC-A diamonds for an incredibly high THC content. With a burst of tangy, sun-kissed mango flavours enhanced by botanical terpenes, Mango THC Infused Pre-Rolls offer everything you like at a price you’ll love.

Deliciously dusted, dank as hell, full of flavour so good you will have to share with the crew. Ghost Purp has an indica profile and is full of pungent fruit and gas notes. A brand new offering from the Endgame kitchen. Chef’s kiss*

description: Purple Hills Creemore Valley Kush Live Resin Carts are filled with terpene-rich, live resin. This complex, flavourful vape cart brings the profile of our fresh-frozen cannabis to life. Purple Hills genetics are selected to thrive outdoors in the Creemore microclimate and are lovingly hand-tended throughout the season by a small and dedicated team. The terpene-rich, aromatic flower is preserved through flash-freezing at harvest and then concentrated through hydrocarbon extraction. The resulting live resin contains all of the flower’s sun-expressed flavonoids, terpenes and cannabinoids, packing a more complete and complex cannabis flavour. Sustainable agriculture is a core tenet of Purple Hills. The Creemore Valley Kush Live Resin Cart is an indica dominant hybrid, bearing flavours of herb and spice, with notes of honey and the earthy sweetness that kush fans search high AND low for.

description: There’s no tip-toeing through tulips in this garden. These pre-rolls feature the popular strain "Grape Ape" - an indica dominant hybrid strain that has been known for its strong genetics Afghani and Medocino Purps. Robust flavours of ripe grapes and sweet berry citrus flavour profiles explode out of these three-pack pre-rolls. Providing you a perfect combination of concentrate and pre-roll, Dab Bods infused pre-rolls are a must have.

Name: PURPLE HILLS  Live Resin - Frosted CKS XL 510 Thread Cartridge

Our rich CO2 extract is cold-filtered at sub-zero temperatures before it is distilled four times to ensure consistent quality, time and time again.

LPC is an indica-dominant hybrid strain bred by crossing the delicious Sunset Sherbet with another indica-heavy hybrid strain. Named for its taste, LPC packs a sweet berry and grape flavour accented by nutty lemon and citrus. The aroma is earthy and woody, with hints of citrus and fruity berries throughout.

With a dense, tight bud structure and frosted like a wedding cake, you’ll want it to be death till you part. Vibrant green buds speckled with burnt orange pistils, this Kush boldly walks down the aisle with high THC and a dominant terpene profile of limonene, pinene, caryophyllene and ocimene. Born from a cross between Banana OG x Purple Punch, this is one bouquet you’ll never want to throw away.

Precisely weighed and machine-rolled for an ideal, even burn. Packed with a humidity device to extend freshness. Quality cannabis, everyday fares.
