Zlushiez' flavour profile can also be described as herbaceous, sweet and floral with a minty exhale. The flowers are lime and dark green frosted with sparkling trichomes and sparse amber hairs.

Grown indoors in Pointe-Claire, Quebec, we hand harvest, whole plant hang dry, hand trim, slow cure and hand package. Our pre-rolls are prepared using our whole flower (never trim), finely milled, filled in 109 mm wood pulp paper, natural brown cone, not bleached, non-GMO, using organic arabica gum, 26 mm W tip and burn white to light grey with a slow to medium burn rate.

Name: PURE SUNFARMS Blueberry Funk | 28g
description: Blueberry Funk is a BC-grown cultivar from the Pure Sunfarms greenhouse. This potent indica is a pungent cross of a legacy west coast Blueberry and Purple Punch. It offers sweet and funky notes of fresh blueberry, dried cherry, sweet peas and cheesy gas from the dominant terpenes that include caryophyllene and linalool. The plant produces dense and aromatic buds covered in trichomes. Pure BC bud, hand-harvested, hang dried and hand-finished.

Name: Highland Grow - Black Velvet 3.5g indica

Name: LOST FARM - Island Punch Infused with Chimp Mints Live Resin Soft Chews Hybrid 1 Pack
description: These tasty, tropical soft chews feature sweet citrus notes rounded out with the woodsy aroma of the indica-dominant Chimp Mints strain. Lost Farm soft chews are made without animal products. They are strain-specific and infused with live resin. At the time of harvest, cannabis flower is flash-frozen to preserve the rich flavours, complex aromas and broad terpene profiles typically lost in most edibles. From there, the flower is delicately extracted to create live resin, which is infused to create an edible with unparalleled flavour. Lost Farm is where past and future, nature and technology merge. Where the ambition of master cultivators meets the vision of edible engineers. Here, we make the freshest, most mouth-watering fruit-flavoured edibles featuring some of the most exciting cannabis strains for the most sophisticated consumers.

Name: WILDLIFE CANNABIS CO. Timbuds Pre-Rolls | 10-Pack
description: TimBuds is a high-THC cross of Platinum Cookies and Black Afghani Kush. Bred by master grower Jawad Skeineh in Humboldt County, California, TimBuds is pungent with aromas of menthol, citrus, chocolate and earthy undertones.

Name: 7ACRES- Platinum Kush Breath Pre-Roll 2X0.5G Hybrid
description: 7ACRES has developed a hybrid cultivar with a unique combination of sweet lemon, fruity berry and funky earth. 7ACRES Platinum Kush Breath was a result of a large genetic selection program with the goal of finding a novel strain. This particular phenotype stood out among the rest, as it possessed both the sweet lemon and fruity berry characteristics of Platinum OG, along with a funky earthy aroma from its OG Kush Breath lineage.

Name: HARTS Blue Breath Pre-Rolls | 10-Pack
description: Blue Breath is a slightly indica-dominant hybrid strain (60% indica/40% sativa) created through a delicious cross of the classic Thin Mint GSC x Blueberry strains. Blue Breath has a super sweet and citrusy fruity blueberry flavour that has a lightly sour exhale. The aroma is of earthy berries and herbs, accented by lightly sour citrus and fresh oranges. This bud has fluffy neon green buds with rich blue undertones, long tapered orange hairs, and blue-tinted bright white crystal trichomes.

Name: SHRED'EMS Sour Blue Razzberry
description: These sugar-speckled soft chews are jam packed with flavour and well-balanced with 5 mg CBD and 2.5 mg THC per piece. An electrifying blue raspberry flavour smashes together with lip-smacking sour, leaving you holding onto your tastebuds for dear life. Made with natural flavours and without animal products.

Name: 1964 Organic Super Lemon Haze | 14g
description: Super Lemon Haze by 1964 is our version of one of the most well-known sativa cultivars. Originating from a cross of Lemon Skunk and Super Silver Haze, this cultivar gives off citrusy aromas with an underlying sour tang. Grown in living soil, hang dried for 14 days, cold cured and non-irradiated.

Name: Viola - Bucketz Live Terpene Disposable Pen Hybrid 0.5g
description: Founded by ex-NBA player Al Harrington, Viola is a premium and well established socially relevant cannabis brand with the biggest black-owned footprint in the North American cannabis industry. From regulation to representation and reform, Viola’s mission is to create opportunities for communities of colour in the cannabis industry. This high THC dominant formula is a mouthwatering sativa with a unique gassy nose and fruity flavour. The VIOLA Disposable Pen is expertly formulated to deliver a smooth, full flavour each and every draw. Produced with fresh frozen live resin extracts, the rich terpene profile produces a stronger aroma and a fuller flavour, while our premium hardware featuring DOSE-CTI Technology delivers a consistent dose with every activation. Made with premium quality materials and electronic components ensuring high performance and reliability. Slightly diluted with distillate to deliver a smoother draw to enhance user experience. Ultra premium DOSE-CTI Technology delive

Name: Broken Coast Cannabis- PLATINUM GARLIC PRE-ROLL Hybrid 1X0.5G
description: Platinum Garlic is sweet, savoury and absolutely stunning. This unique cultivar features tight buds with remarkably deep green and purple colouration, fiery amber pistils and a thick coating of large, sticky trichomes. It’s a hybrid with high THC, 2-4% terpenes and features pungent onion & bold garlic aromas with an intense sweetness, and a touch of vanilla owing to their abundant beta-caryophyllene, myrcene and terpinolene terpenes. It’s a truly glorious strain that we can’t wait to share. Always grown indoors in small-batch, strain-specific rooms, then slowly hang cured and hand trimmed. At Broken Coast, we grow woah.

We capture the perfection of the flower by flash freezing the buds within minutes of harvest, to be extracted into a rich, live resin product with no added fillers, distillate or terpenes. It has a fruity citrus aroma and on the exhale, it gives a sweet taste that exudes similar characteristics to candy. Notes of diesel accompany the sweet and fruity citrus. Alien Rock Candy is highly potent. All flower is grown indoors in a state-of-the-art facility, grown with Remo nutrients in medicoir coco based grow medium with Eco Grow Tech LED lighting. All cultivars are full plant hang dried for two weeks before being hand trimmed. All batches are cured in barrels before being bulk packaged.

Name: DIVVY Pink Gas | 3.5g
description: From the plugs who brought you some of your faves, Divvy's got you with Pink Gas. A cross of 33 Splitter x Peach Ozz, Pink Gas has big resinous buds and gives you a strong fuel aroma off the flower with gassy and gelato terpenes. Expect high THC and bang for your buck

description: Created by Jungle Boys Genetics in California, Stellar Sunrise is an ultra-potent, flavourful sativa-dominant hybrid, resulting from the cross of Green Crack x Triangle Kush. This exceptional strain was selected not for just its unique fruity flavour but for its high potency, terpene profile and CBG content. Astro Boyz ensures that our flower is craft quality, indoor grown, hang-dried, hand-trimmed, slow cold cured, hand-packaged and non-irradiated. We take great pride in offering superior quality products ensuring an exceptional out-of-this-world experience.

description: Bred by Seed Junky Genetics in California, Animal Face is an ultra-potent, flavourful sativa-dominant hybrid created by crossing the Face Off OG clone and Animal Mints male. Our version of Animal Face was selected out of 100 different phenotypes, not only for its potency and terpene profile, but also because of its unique flavours of lemon and cake. All of our flower is hang-dried, hand-trimmed, slow cold-cured and hand-packaged. We believe fresh and terpy is best, so all of our flower is non-irradiated and packaged in a nitrogen-flushed pouch that features an airtight seal.

Name: SOVEREIGN Ceramic Tip Lemon Squeezy Infused Pre-roll
description: Lemondrpz Kush was pheno-hunted by the growers at Seven Leaf, the first 100% Indigenous-owned and operated licensed producer. This proprietary cut is indica dominant with a citrusy lemon smell. Bubble hash is created by agitating premium fresh frozen Lemondrpz Kush in ice water. As the trichomes separate and fall through the water, they are caught using 45 to 159 micron sieves, graded and dried. The dry bubble hash is then evenly spread for a consistent burn. The cone is wrapped around a reusable glass filter tip. By adding ultra-premium concentrates to the pre-roll, SOVEREIGN amplifies both the flavour and potency of this pre-roll. We give back to the First Nations community by donating a portion of proceeds to the Strong Roots North Charitable Foundation.

Embrace the subtle art as you indulge in the rich essence of The CANNON. Delight in the harmonious blend of flavours, carefully curated to provide a balanced and refined encounter. Each inhale brings forth a symphony of nuanced notes, allowing you to savour the essence of the Pink Kush and Cotton Candy in their purest form! With its precisely measured composition, this pre-roll is crafted for those who appreciate the art of subtlety, it promises a genuine and unadulterated encounter, free from the distractions of exaggerated claims or associations.

The way the product was always intended to look, feel and smell, our Old School Pressed Hashish packs a flavourful punch that will take you back to simpler times.

Name: HIGH STREET CANNABIS Platinum Punch Remix  | 7g
description: Lineage: Platinum x Purple Punch. Breeder: InHouse Genetics. Phenohunted: Hidden Reserves. Nose: Creamy, sweet and floral. Taste: Creamy, smooth and sweet. Platinum Punch Remix is one of the most sought after legacy strains in Canada. It quickly became popular making the rounds through Vancouver and Toronto’s cannabis scene. Since 2019, it's been Hidden Reserves most popular strain and the people still want more. Platinum Punch Remix is a legacy legend ready for its legal debut.

Name: 7 FARMS DOWN - Cherry Boat 7g Sativa
description: Selected from a sativa-dominant worked line, Cherry Boat was bred in-house for its potency and flavours that flowers rapidly for a seamless late summer harvest. This truly unique cultivar blends one of Canada’s strongest heirloom genetics -- an 11 week Pink Kush S1 -- with its heightened THC potential crossed with the delicious aromas and flavours of Top Dawgs Cherry Chem. Grown in sunny southwestern Ontario and cared for by a talented team of legacy growers and breeders, Cherry Boat reeks of sweet fruit with earthy chocolate undertones and a whole lot of funk. Bred by, selected by and grown by 7 Farms Down.

Name: SITKA LEGENDS Trufflez
description: Legendary master grower, Tyler of Verte West, has taken it to the next level dialing in his latest masterpiece, Trufflez. Be prepared for a taste explosion with the cross between the delicious Zktlz x Cherry Noire. The terpene profile can only be described as sweet and earthy. Be prepared for an intense sour candy flavour with hints of grapefruit, licorice and pineapple. And true to Tyler's technique and the strain lineage, this strain is smooth. The team at Verte prefer very small flower rooms for their small batch flower. Pushing 10 weeks for flower time, Verte's five week hang dry, burp and cure is one of the slowest in the industry, pulling everything they can out of the dense beautiful buds and terpene profile. Once the stems have the perfect snap, each bud is meticulously hand trimmed. And, of course, this beautiful flower is never irradiated. Each pouch is hand packed with large and medium buds with one or two small buds to make weight, to ensure you get the product you deserve.

Our proprietary hydrocarbon extraction process takes THCa diamonds and converts them into an high purity and high potency THC liquid isolate. Our liquid diamond isolate is flavoured with a custom botanical terpene blend and paired with Greentank hardware, delivering a high purity, potent and consistent session from the first puff. Kiwi Kush has kiwi and citrus notes balanced with herbal and earthy undertones and a frosty, cooling sensation on the exhale.

description: Our Jenn's OG pre-rolls are single strain consisting of nothing but our Chocolate Marshmallows flower. We have put utmost focus on maintaining the pure taste of the bud in its pre-rolled form and to keep it an exclusively cannabis product across all of its components. Pre-rolls are rolled in ultra-thin hemp paper allowing for a slow and even burn. We further treat them to food grade filter tips made of pure hemp and featuring bio-cooling technology to cool down the smoke without foregoing any of the flavour. The combination of passionately cultivated strains, a gentle processing and their elegant, fully bio-degradable filters made of pure hemp material makes Jenn's OG pre-rolls a true connoisseur piece prone to become the next benchmark.

Mosaz is a blend of some of our favourite exotic terps and inspired by some of Endgame’s most popular cart flavours. A guaranteed banger with big flavour and some of our highest THC% to date.

You don't need to compromise on quality to get great taste and potency. Our all-in-one vape is made from an innovative hemp plastic blend to reduce our carbon footprint and plastic use.

Name: ANIMAL Orange Tsunami AIO

Name: General Admission - Watermelon Splash Distillate Infused Pre-Roll 1x1G Indica

Sweet, fragrant and smells like you've carved a whole patch of watermelons, these pre-rolls will have you ready for the summer holiday even if the weather has other plans.

Name: HIGHLY DUTCH ORGANIC Rotterdam Indica Pre-Rolls | 14-Pack

This terpene-rich, high-THC indica flower delivers a strong aroma and rich flavour profile for the cannabis enthusiast looking for an affordable, naturally grown product. Terpene lovers, look no further.

Name: AMBR Grape Crusher
description: Grape Crusher, as you can expect, is a fizzy Grape Soda with a touch of citrus and 10mg of THC for a potent beverage with a rapid onset.

Name: ELIOS RESERVE ZeroG Live Rosin Infused Pre-Roll
description: New addition to our Elio's Reserve family of products, is our high potency rosin infused pre-roll. Crafted by our extraction team, this solventless, golden, terpene rich rosin is combined with our whole flower. We just married two high quality ingredients for your pre-roll enjoyment. This infusion makes the flavour profile of fruity, diesel and warm spices notes bold with boosted potency.

Name: RITUAL STICKS French Cookies Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: French Cookies is a rare slightly sativa dominant hybrid strain (60% sativa/40% indica) created through a reverse of the classic Platinum Cookies strain. With a deliciously potent flavour, French Cookies has a sweet and creamy cookie flavour with a lightly fruity exhale. French Cookies buds are spade-shaped and minty green with light orange hairs, purple and blue leaves and a sticky coating of bright white crystal trichomes. Ritual Sticks are held to the highest of standards, using only the same top quality, whole flower you have learned to expect from us. Our pre-rolls are proudly filled with Ritual Green premium cannabis, wrapped in natural, hand rolled Futurola straight slims, some of the thinnest papers on the market.

Name: CALI #1 STUNNA INFUSED PRE-ROLL
description: Made from the finest artisan bubble hash and flower – CALI's first infused pre-roll. #1 STUNNA is a true expression of flower and hash in a pre-roll format. Combined with CALI's Rozay and Pink Diamonds dried flowers and 9 lb Hammer artisan bubble hash, this infused pre-roll has been blended to craft perfection. A combination producing ultimate gripping flavours and terpene profiles, living up to its name: #1 STUNNA.

Name: SPINACH GMO Cookies Pre-Rolls | 10-pack

Grown in Pure Sunfarms' sun-soaked greenhouse in the heart of BC’s Fraser Valley. Hand-harvested and freshly packed.

Name: BON VOYAGE! Flight Pass Pre-Roll | 2-Pack
description: Our Lyonleaf team of passionate cannabis experts, operation masterminds and plant scientists has been cultivating craft cannabis at our newly purpose-built 30,000 square foot indoor facility in Montreal, Quebec since February 2020. To date, we have had over 150 successful harvests. We consistently harvest once per week following a sophisticated production schedule. This allows us to dial in on many variables at our facility such as grow media, nutrients, environmental, lighting and cultivation practices, to produce standardized craft cannabis from each batch. We have been providing our standardized craft cannabis in bulk flower format with other licensed producers that package it for their brands and distribute to different provinces. In supporting these brands, we have learned what consumers want in terms of price, potency, strain, product type and packaging type in addition to the standardized bag appeal that consumers deserve.

Aromas of pungent earth and pine are predominant. It is full of flavour and slightly sweeter and more floral than the nose would suggest but leaves a unique aftertaste of pine and juniper.  At WAGNERS we believe in hard work and Well Made Weed. Our Pink Bubba joints are just that, Well Made.

Named for its super delicious flavour, Oreoz is a great choice for anyone who's after a high level of potency and a great taste too. Like its name suggests, it's named after the classic chocolate cookie sandwiches filled with delicious sugary filling. Oreoz has a unique aromatic profile that blends chocolate, peppery spice and herbs as well as earthy diesel accents. Flavours include chocolate, diesel, nuts, pepper, spice and sweet. Aromas include chocolate, diesel, herbs, pepper and spice.

description: Each bag is hand packed with individual humidity packs to ensure optimum freshness in our flower. Rainbow Lava is a one-of-a-kind true hybrid strain unique to Valhalla Flwr. This strain is notably rich in terpenes and carries a sweet, fruity scent with undertones of a woody, clove like aroma. Containing flavours best described as spicy or peppery, this is a strain that will truly ignite all the senses. Alaskan Thunder is a sativa strain made up of Afgani x Russian Ruderalis. This flower has frosty dense buds and a spicy aftertaste, it carries flavours of banana and orange.

description: Milk Cake is a hybrid cross from CKS x Cherry Pie x ICC. A sativa-leaning hybrid with loud flavour, a sweet milk & ice cream nose and dense, quality buds dripping with trichomes and high THC potency.

description: The GMO is strong with this one. Triple Burger is bred by back-crossing (GMO x GMO) to stabilize the strain, then crossing that linage with with Han-Solo Burger. (Larry OG X GMO CKS). Its calyx, gasoline scented flowers are something any connoisseur will lust after. Its intense fuel aroma gives way to an equally strong gas flavour in its smoke. Hints of skunk, rubber and cheese are also present, with a hint of sweetness. Triple Burger is bred by back-crossing (GMO x GMO) to stabilize the strain, then crossing that linage with with Han-Solo Burger. (Larry OG x GMO CKS). One of the most potent strains in Tribal's new line-up, typically averaging close to 30% THC. Its intense fuel aroma gives way to an equally strong gas flavour in its smoke. Hints of skunk, rubber and cheese are also present, with a hint of sweetness. Our pre-rolls are produced with nothing but whole buds which have been consistently ground to deliver rich flavours and wrapped in premium hemp cones.

Name: REDECAN Space Age Cake | 14g
description: Galactic heights await with Space Age Cake. A profoundly potent, indulgent indica offering creamy pepper, citrus and nutty flavours. Big, dense buds — bigger resinous terps at 2.5-3.5%. This GSC x Snow Lotus cross is everything you love about CKS strains with an unexpectedly bright fruit and berry aromatic backbone from the caryophyllene, limonene and linalool dominant terps.

Name: THE LOUD PLUG Venom OG Live Resin Cart
description: You asked, and we delivered! Our infamous Venom OG you’ve all come to know and love is now available as a Live Resin 510 vape cart, bringing to life the full profile of this beloved strain. This high-potency and high-terpene extract is crafted from single-strain fresh-frozen flower that’s undergone an arctic extraction journey to lock in all the complex terpenes, flavonoids, and cannabinoids. This cart boasts a burst of skunky spice, subtle peppery notes, with a hint of zesty lemon that'll awaken your senses. Elevate your vaping experience with the full profile of Venom OG, all in one sleek 510 vape cart. Brought to you with love, from Scarborough.

Name: Ghost Drops- The Triple Threat Pre-Rolls- Hybrid 3X0.5G
description: Ghost Drops offers each of its first drops in a convenient pre-roll multipack. This unique sku gives consumers the opportunity to try the Ghost’s first drops with a single convenient purchase. Each perfectly rolled pre roll is hand crafted with whole flower, All bud, no bull.

Name: Edison - Jolts - Freshly Minted Sativa Lozenges
description: Edison JOLTS is Canada’s first 10 mg THC lozenge. These lozenges are slow-dissolving and deliver a jolt of mint flavour. For optimal sublingual/buccal absorption, suck lozenge until peppermint flavour peaks (about 15 seconds), then hold under your tongue or between cheek and gum until fully dissolved. PATENT PENDING.

Name: BOLD Root Beer Float Pre-Rolls
description: Root Beer Float is a rare indica-dominant strain created through crossing XXX OG x Vanilla Kush. Enter into a sweet hazy, earthy flavour with hints of lemon and pine aroma. Enjoy the classic Root Beer flavour combined with frothy vanilla notes. We only use whole flower in our pre-rolls because that's the way it should be. BOLD Craft Cannabis is indoor grown, small batch, hang dried, slow cured and hand trimmed.

Name: SAN RAFAEL '71 Chemango Kush
description: Chemango Kush by San Rafael ’71 is a premium, indoor-grown strain bred from premier genetics from a world-class breeding facility in Comox, British Columbia. A next-generation cultivar, Chemango Kush was bred to deliver high THC potency and an intriguing blend of fruit, sour, and chem aroma notes. This powerful indica features huge, ultra-dense buds with gorgeous olive-green tones and glistening trichomes. Chemango Kush is hang-dried, hand-finished and carefully hand-bottled with an included humidity pack.

Name: MTL CANNABIS Wes' Coast Kush | 14g

Name: DIME BAG Tropical Pocket Puffs Pre-Rolls | 4-Pack

These buds show off every shade of green and the trichome covering is so mean you’ll want to say you knew about it before it was famous. We’re predicting this one will be very popular.

description: The Silver Stick Slim is a 3" sleek micro-dose inhaler. It features a natural cotton filter to block any loose flower that could travel down the device and traps tar for a smoother draw. It’s made in the USA from an ultra-durable the aircraft-grade alloy and is easy to clean. Once fully loaded with ground cannabis the device will provide 2-3 inhalations before needing to be reloaded. The compact design will fit into most standard 4” dugouts.

Name: AXEA THC-Free Nighttime CBN/CBD Isolate Oil
description:
Refined to its purest form with 100% Coconut MCT Oil, blended with Axea's unique CBN+CBD formulation. 10mg/g CBN = 300mg CBN Total and 35 mg/g CBD = 1050mg CBD total. No artificial colours.


Axea's Nighttime CBN/CBD Isolate Oil is a THC-Free Crystalized isolate oil. Enjoy a good night's sleep, wake up energized, clear headed, and ready to take on the day. Using only the highest-grade ingredients, including 100% coconut oil, sparring the destruction of palm trees. Axea represents mind and body balance, backed by real science. As a supporter of natural wellness, Axea will donate a portion of sales to help fight opiate addiction and mental health. For more information, please visit www.axea.ca

Name: TRUE FIRE Tai Punch Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description:
The extreme trichome laden Tai Punch is a sativa dominant cross between the flavourful Sunset Sherbet and the powerful Purple Punch strains.

These pre-rolls are made of premium flower only, no shake and no trim. In fact, we hand trim the flower prior to milling it into the pre-roll.

Name: DAB BODS Rockstar Shatter 2.0
description: Dab Bods would like to introduce our next generation of Shatter, Rockstar Shatter 2.0. We will never stop trying to improve our products and our shatter is no exception. With the addition of terpenes, our 2.0 shatter gives a more malleable texture with a heightened taste profile. Rockstar Shatter 2.0 is sure to take centre stage in the Shatter market. Featuring flavours of sweet grapes with undertones of spice, this indica strain made by crossing Rockbud x Sensi Star is here to rock your world!

Name: REDECAN (14G) INDICA DOMINANT WAPPA
description: Standing firm at a moderate height and with a stocky build, Redecan Wappa is an indica dominant strain, characterized by its large, densely packed flowers with a broad base, and tapered, pointed tip. Its flowers grow a beautiful green and yellow, sporting vibrant hues of purple in the fall as a response to its cooler growing environment. Wappa exudes an overwhelmingly skunky, yet fruity aroma, thanks to high levels of myrcene and caryophyllene. Consistently testing at high THC levels between 23-29%, Redecan's Wappa strain is the go-to choice for cannabis lovers across the nation. All of our bud is carefully harvested, expertly cured to preserve natural flavour and moisture, trimmed by hand, and inspected.

Name: XMG - Cream Soda 355ml (Blend) New SKU
description: Each sleek can of this cream soda beverage has 10 mg of nano-infused THC with all-natural flavours.

Name: SAN RAFAEL '71 Cosmic Cream
description: Cosmic Cream by San Rafael ’71 is an impressively high-THC indica bred from original, elite genetics developed by our R&D team at Occo – a world-renowned breeding facility nestled in Comox, BC. This top-tier indica takes you on a nostalgic trip with its comforting aroma, reminiscent of sweet cereal milk with subtle hints of fruit and loamy earth. Dank and dense, Cosmic Cream’s flowers are compact and acorn-shaped with a glistening sheen of visible trichomes. Cultivated under the highest quality standards, San Rafael '71 flower is hang-dried, hand-finished, and carefully hand-bottled with an included humidity pack.

Name: BULLRIDER Select Pre-Roll
description: Showcasing the hard work of breeders and farmers, Bullrider Select will feature limited flower drops from the best Canada has to offer. This high potency strain finishes with a boasting terpene profile of 3.9%. A sativa dominant strain which was formed when OG Kush was combined with Strawberry Diesel.

Naturally grown in microclimate conditions inspired by the unique environments each plant thrives in – Pink Grapefruit OG pre-rolls are single strain, whole bud, milled to perfection and evenly rolled with eco-friendly papers. Every pack of pre-rolls comes in a reusable kit that locks in freshness for pre-rolls that are ready when you are. These hypnotic herbs are light green with golden stigma hairs, and long-stemmed trichomes.

Every pull from this elite cart slaps with a potent hit of flavour and 90–96% THC, finishing with a frosty, cooling sensation on the exhale.

Name: PROVINCE BRANDS Yandi Fresh Green Apple Cider
description: Made with real apple juice, natural Granny Smith apple flavouring and 10 mg of THC, Yandi Fresh Green Apple Cider is the ideal sparkling beverage for both the casual beverage consumer as well as the avid cider connoisseur. Yandi Fresh Green Apple Cider is for the consumer who prefers their apple cider tart and traditional. Designed to be enjoyed two ways: as both a cold or a hot beverage depending on the season and your preference, making Yandi Fresh Ciders two unique products in one can. Using the same apple cider base as Province Brands' very well received Raspberry Apple Cider, the raspberry has been replaced with the perfect amount of natural tart apple flavour to give Canada's first cannabis cider brand an off-sweet twist. Yandi Fresh Green Apple Cider tastes exactly as you’d expect with no cannabis taste or smell and no experimental flavour combinations.

Name: BACK FORTY Panda Puff Pre-Rolls | 10-Pack

Made from Grand Daddy Purps flower infused with the extract used in our Purple Monkey vapes, this smooth-smoking indica is taken to the next level with a chamomile blunt wrap.

Name: BOXHOT FATTIES- Cherry Kush Infused Blunt Indica 1X1G

Name: REDECAN Frosted Animal Cake
description: Put on your party hat and get ready to celebrate Frosted Animal Cake. This frosty beast leans sativa and unleashes high THC potency with ferocious citrus, diesel and nutty flavours. Meticulously grown, carefully hang dried and hand trimmed for the wild expression of Frosted Animal Cake available.

Name: DEBUNK - Fifty Woods Triple Infused Blunt
description: A potent nod to legacy cannabis culture, DEBUNK Fifty Woods Berry is milled flower that is coated with THCa diamonds and a terpene enhanced liquid diamond infusion for a legendary honey and berry flavour profile with an earthy undertone. Wrapped in our signature chamomile blunt wrap and tipped with bubble hash.

Name: NORTHBOUND CANNABIS Melonberry Kiss All In One Vape
description: Sink in and savour Northbound Cannabis' Melonberry Kiss all-in-one vape cartridge. Indulge in the sweet blend of velvety melon and the subtle blackberry flavours. This indica dominant cart promises a smooth and tasty experience. Packaged in an all-in-one vape, it delivers a burst of fruity flavour and reflects our commitment to the planet. Our all-in-one vapes are made from an innovative hemp plastic blend, with a lower carbon footprint and less plastic usage. Designed to deliver a sweet journey with a custom distillate formulation, ensuring you won't compromise between flavour and potency.

With high THC and a diverse terpene profile, it promises to deliver full-bodied flavour with a bold and dank aroma that doesn't shy away from making a statement. Each bud is hang dried and slow cured, reflecting our unwavering dedication to quality and consistency. Opt for Republic Reserve 25 and join us in fostering a community where top-tier quality and value are always #ForThePeople.

It is a cross between two popular strains, Amnesia Haze and Skunk One. The buds are light green and covered in a thick layer of trichomes, which give it a frosty appearance. The aroma of Lemon Haze is intense and citrusy with notes of lemon, lime and a hint of earthiness. This first product is part of the Retro Haze brand, a line of cannabis products inspired by strains that made their mark during the 60s, 70s and 80s and the philosophy behind those eras. Indoor grown, hand trimming and a full plant cure process.

This rare genetic immediately broke through the five other phenotypes during our search, and with such a great history behind it, we think this will be the start of something amazing! As with all of Rocket Factory’s flower, we expertly flush and dry this flower so the experience is smooth with a lasting aroma from start to finish. Rocket Factory leverages our purpose-built facility and the latest technology to monitor each crop and bring the plants to their full potential.

Name: REDECAN Redees Cold Creek Kush Pre-Rolls
description: Redees by Redecan are an unparalleled pre-roll. Thoughtfully designed in a unique straight-roll, Redees are personal sized and come in a package that’s compact and convenient. A sativa dominant hybrid between the ever-popular MK Ultra and Chemdawg 91, Cold Creek Kush, or CCK, is a globally recognized strain, known for its light green hues, amber hairs and trichrome-frosted flowers. CCK is a potent strain that tests with high THC levels. Cold Creek Kush is recognized for its dank smell, resembling a damp rainforest with notes of earth, wood, sour and pine, giving a strong but fresh aroma and a dank, spicy and herbal flavour, informed by high levels of beta-pinene, nerolidol, trans-caryophyllene and limonene. Just as with any Redecan Evergreen strain, CCK is carefully harvested and expertly cured to preserve its natural flavour and moisture, trimmed by hand and inspected.

Name: REDECAN Space Age Cake Redees Hemp'd Pre-rolls
description: Galactic heights await with Redees Space Age Cake. A profoundly potent indica with high THC offering creamy vanilla, nutty and ammonia flavours in our signature straight-cut pre-rolls. This GSC x Snow Lotus cross is everything you love about CKS strains and smokes exceptionally smooth in Redees. Space Age Cake is an especially resinous flower, so expect dapples of oil on the paper and a fragrant, thick smoke that coats the palate. You can focus on the Space Age Cake while we focus on delivering meticulously grown flower into perfectly rolled Redees, every time.

Potluck dinners are events where the attendees bring a dish to a meal - a different meal. This indica dominant cultivar is well known for its dense purple and pinkish buds coated in vibrant orange pistils. Crack a bud open and you’ll be greeted with aromas of sweet honey and citrus, then complemented with rich earthy undertones. Including all that you would expect from a Tom Ford but with the added bonus that it’s hang dried for 14 days, cold cured and non-irradiated.

Name: Bud La Fleur - Zombie Rasta Pre-Roll 1g
description: Zombie Rasta is an indica-dominant strain with a high THC potency potential made by crossing the classic White Widow x Silver Haze x Black Domina strains. Featuring bright green buds coated in light orange hairs and frosty white crystal trichomes, this genetic has sweet, spicy and earthy aromas with light touches of rich berries. The dominant terpenes are myrcene, limonene and caryophyllene. Our pre-rolls are prepared using whole bud flower (never trim). Finely ground and compacted in 109mm wood pulp paper, natural brown cone (unbleached), and a 26mm tip, our pre-rolls burn white to light grey with a slow to medium burn rate. Grown indoors in Pointe-Claire, Quebec, we hand harvest, hang dry, hand trim, slow cure and hand package.

This makes it an ideal choice for those seeking a gentle yet effective cannabis experience. Milled and rolled into the perfect pre-roll.

description: Bred by the legendary SeedJunky Genetics, Gogurtz pairs Rntz with Cap Junky. Dense dark purple buds with green hues emit heavy candy and gas aromas. Gogurtz brings out the best characteristics of its parent strains. Rntz passes down that fruity flavour profile that smells just like a bag of sugary candy, while Cap Junky gives it that gas aroma. Grown indoors by a micro-cultivator in the Niagara region, each lot is cultivated in small batches under 45 HPS lights in a 1,000 square foot grow room, hang dried, hand trimmed and cold cured in glass jars for three weeks. Hand packaged and nitrogen flushed with a humidity pack and detailed information on the package including top three dominant terpenes, strain name, harvest date, name of cultivator and cultivation processes. CELEBRITY is dedicated to providing the consumer with an exclusive selection of small batch cannabis. No hype, no gimmicks.

It contains between 800-900 total mg of total THC. This new approach to vapes, allows for higher potency than your standard distillation and winterization that is found in most vape carts. The Diamond Vape does not burn the throat. As well, the purity of the decarboxylated Diamond allows botanical terps to be added to cart, pulling through a beautiful flavour without competing tastes from other components.

Live rosin is made from hand-bucked, frozen fresh flower. We use ice water to separate trichome heads from plant material, then freeze-dry to remove water. Name: Dab Bods - Blueberry Resin Infused Pre-Rolls

The resin infused pre-rolls maintain all of the terpenes from the live plant and combines them with cured hand crafted flower in a convenient format for individual consumption. These pre-rolls feature the popular and potent strain "Blueberry Haze" - a sativa leaning hybrid strain. This 3 pack of pre-rolls showcases very bright, fresh explosive flavours of blueberry with subtle undertones of vanilla, spice and musk. Because of its lineage, the start low and go slow rule is a must with this flower. Providing you a perfect combination of concentrate and pre-roll, Dab Bods infused pre-rolls are a must have.

Name: SUPERNOVA FARMS Space Funk Pre-Rolls | 3-Pack
description: Space Funk (Eastside OG x Purple Jellato) is a sativa dominant hybrid. This strain was thoughtfully pheno-hunted by our master grower for over 15 months to find the strongest characteristics of this genetic. This particular phenotype has notes that are sweet, creamy and citrusy with a gassy terpene profile. Consumers can expect high quality fuel flavoured buds. Key highlights include two straight weeks flushing with 0ppm filtered water, hang dried, hand trimmed, hand rolled and cured for at least 120 days. We break each bud and remove the middle stems before grinding to make Dutch-crown pre-rolls in 100% recyclable packaging.

The visual bag appeal of chunky, sticky orbs of golden green flower combined with a pinene-forward terpene profile and lofty THC levels have pushed Golden Grape to the forefront of our production focus. Golden Grape began in a dedicated cannabis nursery, where this overachiever rose to the top of our never-ending phenotype hunt for the highest performing genetics. The team fully embraced the challenge of bringing out the best qualities of this outstanding specimen. They start by cultivating in small batches so each plant receives the full attention it deserves through each phase of the grow. Harvested at peak ripeness, each plant is hang-dried and slowly finished to achieve perfect moisture. Finally, each bud is inspected and hand trimmed with the utmost care by the dedicated quality control team, ensuring that every bag achieves its maximum visual potential.

Name: C. Georgia P. Ceramic Tip Diamond Infused Pre-Roll
description: The legendary Georgia P. in a pre-roll infused with premium diamonds and finished with a ceramic tip for enhanced air flow and an even burn all the way through. The strain is known for having a pungent aroma that smells like fresh peach, with a sweet berry flavour, hints of nutty dough and rich cherries.

All Wyld soft chews are packaged in an all-new compostable pouch, and our recipes are formulated by food scientists to provide consistent experiences that taste amazing. Wyld soft chews use sunflower lecithin to improve bioavailability and onset time and are made to be thermostable up to 55°C, with a firm texture that doesn’t stick to your teeth. Each Wyld Dark Cherry 5:1 soft chew contains the terpenes myrcene, linalool, beta-caryophyllene, and terpineol. Wyld is proud to be a Climate Neutral Certified brand.

Name: PROVINCE BRANDS Yandi Fresh Peach Apple Cider
description: Made with real apple juice, natural peach flavouring, and 10 mg of THC, Yandi Fresh Peach Apple Cider is the ideal beverage for both the casual beverage consumer as well as the avid cider connoisseur. Using the same apple cider base as Province Brands' very well-received Raspberry Apple Cider, the raspberry has been replaced with the perfect amount of natural peach flavour to give Canada's first cannabis cider brand a stone fruit twist.

Highly aromatic guava Biscotti flower is flash-frozen at harvest. It is then concentrated through hydrocarbon extraction. The end result is a full flavoured rich live resin with natural flavonoids, terpenes and cannabinoids.

Name: ENDGAME Black Cherry Punch x Jack Herer Shatter

We chose these two strains as they often make amazing concentrates and have very complementary profiles. Expect a delicious floral bouquet of flavour with a sweet citrus accent.

Name: Regal Single Flame Sleek Torch Lighter

The Regal lighters are a stylish cigar lighter and perfect for anyone looking for a more powerful windproof lighter
The Sleek lighter is a single flame torch for those not looking for to hot of a flame
These stylish lighters are a great gift or treat for yourself
Available in gold, gold/silver, black/silver

Name: OGEN - Peach Chauffeur #15 28G Sativa
description: Peach Chauffeur #15 features a sweet tropical bouquet with a hint of earthiness. Its trichome coating adds a soft silvery sheen to the overall visual of the bud, reminiscent of the soft silvery coating on a perfectly ripe peach. This is one of our highest testing phenotypes for terpenes so far. Our indoor grown craft buds are hand trimmed to preserve trichomes and we use minimal packaging with a secondary seal to keep your bud fresher longer.

Name: TABLE TOP- STICKY BUNS PRE-ROL INDICA 3X0.5G
description: Sticky Buns is a popular TABLE TOP™ strain, and now it's available in a pack of pre-rolls! This flavourful indica-dominant hybrid offers very strong THC potency potential with distinct vanilla and cookie flavour from a terpene blend of caryophyllene, myrcene and linalool. The sticky name comes from the big, sticky trichomes that cover the dense, deep green buds. We'll leave the buns up to your imagination, but you can rest assured It's Got Legs™

Name: NAKED MUMMER Nebula Runtz
description: Nebula Runtz was bred by the Atlantic team and made by crossing Toyz from Archive genetics and Bakers Dozen by Exotic genetics. The terpene profile is a mix of Gelato, from Toyz, and a deep gas taste and aroma from bakers dozen’s triple OG x CKS & Cream.

Name: ASTRONAUT CANNABIS Liquid Diamond Lemon Frappe 510 Thread Cartridge
description: Next up for the Astronaut brand is our very own liquid diamond line! These diamonds are extracted from an outdoor grown cultivation facility to achieve the purest form in taste and overall entourage effect. Our team at Astronaut has carefully dedicated months of R&D to present this lineup with top notch quality diamond, but cartridges of the highest quality that will burn through the thicker concentrate with 0 to no clogging while maintaining a full flavour profile from the strains they are extracted from. Our Lemon Frappe does no shame to the Top-Quality Liquid Diamonds we plan to present to our customers. This sativa-leaning hybrid brings a sweet and fruity taste upon inhale – leaving a ton of room to taste the beautiful terpene profile and a great smell on exhale.

Name: XPLOR Funky Monkey Infused Blunt
description: Get your funk on with Funky Monkey Infused Blunt. With a unique strain of gassy and funky aromas, boosted by an infusion of kief and wrapped in an aromatic blunt, our infused pre-roll is sure to drive your senses bananas!

Name: Persy 2nd Press Live Rosin Strain Specific Full Spectrum Solventless soft chews
description: Persy offers both 1st and 2nd press live rosin soft chews. Considering our starting material and that we are extremely gentle with our 1st press, our second press live rosin maintains a very high quality and allows us to offer the same strain specific experiences at lower prices. Applying pressure in quality, consistency and transparency, using 2nd press strain specific live rosin bred and grown by top producers in Canada. High terpene, 2nd press live rosin syrup infused with complementary flavours carefully selected by Persy. Our high quality edibles truly offer strain specific full spectrum cannabinoid and terpene profiles without degrading them in the decarboxylation and infusion process. What's in your edible?

Name: HiWay - Slow Lane Indica - 28g
description: Hiway Slow Lane Indica is a strain-specific product where the strain rotates from lot to lot to allow you to try a variety of new and exciting batches. It has strong THC potency and minimal CBD, carefully cultivated to bring you cannabis that doesn’t compromise on quality at a great price.

Name: POTLUCK - Blue Lagoon Thunder
description: Introducing Blue Lagoon Thunder by Potluck, a part of the all new Tropical Collection of flavours. Blue Lagoon Thunder brings a storm of tropical flavours, combining notes of fresh oranges and ripe pineapple with a subtle hint of rich coconut packed into our all-in-one rechargeable vapes.

Name: Pura Vida - Sativa Honey Oil Dispenser 1G
description: Pura Vida’s 1g Sativa Honey Oil Dispenser contains concentrate that's been carefully extracted from the highest quality, hand selected sativa flower. This all-glass dispenser multi-tool is heat resistant and safe for use for applying directly into dab rigs, dab pens, taken orally, applied topically, or adding full spectrum concentrates to anything else – rolling papers, refill vape carts, and more. Our proprietary extraction process allows us to produce a full plant profile, preserving its distinctive sweet and spicy flavour profiles.

Name: @OUEST Banjo-GPS | 3.5g
description: Banjo-GPS is a potent sativa-leaning hybrid .Bred and phenotyped by renowned cannabis breeder, Parker Sullivan, Banjo has received considerable critical acclaim in recent years. This variety is bursting with citrus fragrances and subtle blueberry notes, while producing a distinct incense-like aroma when smoked or vaporized. Recent indoor production testing of Banjo resulted in 4% total terpenes. Dominant terpenes include myrcene, limonene and farnesene.

Name: THINKER CLASSICS Jack Herer (ON) | 3.5g
description: THINKER Classics deliver craft quality cuts of classic cultivars. Bringing back original strains, THINKER Classics curates the best throwbacks. The first drop is a highly sought after sativa, Jack Herer, that is bursting with citrusy and peppery aromas and flavours. Cultivated in small batches to craft specs, the flower is hang-dried, perfectly cured and hand-trimmed. Old school strains grown with the latest craft techniques.

Name: WAGNERS Pink Bubba
description: Pink Bubba is a beautiful example of an indica-leaning hybrid in both effect and flavour. A cross between Pink Kush x Bubba Kush, the cannabis has a compact structure that shows stunning mint green and deep purple hues. Bright orange hairs and a thick coating of trichomes add texture and depth to this beautiful flower. Aromas of pungent earth and pine are predominant and the smoke itself is smooth. It is full of flavour and slightly sweeter and more floral than the nose would suggest but leaves a unique aftertaste of pine and juniper.

Name: 3SAINTS Road Dawg | 3.5G
description: If you want a low potency bud, look elsewhere, as Road Dawg is NOT your go-to choice. This strain delivers potent THC, accompanied by robust effects, making it advisable to steer clear if you’re a novice. The flower exhibits a minty green hue, adorned with thick pistils and an even thicker layer of glistening, trichomes. Road Dawg offers a unique flavour profile in a good way—melding tropical fruit with hints of mint, all underscored by a pronounced diesel note. Hand harvested, hang dried, and dry trimmed to protect those hard-won trichomes.

Name: VOLO MAC V2
description: Find your new best bud. VOLO presents MACV2 from seed to shelf. This cultivar is brought to you by one of the most recognized breeders: Capulator Genetics. MACV2 is a cultivar crossing GSC, Alien Dawg, Starfighter and Columbian. This Cap’s Cut selected unicorn-phenotype produces potent terpenes and high THC.

Name: THE LOUD PLUG Exotic Gas Live Resin 510 Thread Cartridge

This high-potency and high-terpene extract is crafted from single-strain fresh-frozen flower that’s undergone an arctic extraction journey to lock in all the complex terpenes, flavonoids, and cannabinoids. Savour the dank, sweet, and earthy flavours of this live resin with an unmistakable gas twist. Elevate your vaping experience with the full profile of Exotic Gas, all in one sleek 510 vape cart. Brought to you with love, from Scarborough.

Name: PURE SUNFARMS Jet Fuel Gelato Pre-Rolls | 10-Pack

Pure BC-grown whole flower with no trim and no shake. Conveniently portioned and made with natural paper, each pre-roll is finished with a twisted end to prevent spillage and act as a wick. Pre-rolls are nestled into a recyclable carton.

This flower comes as a lovely lighter green colour, with a light earthy, herbal smell with a gentle undercurrent of mint. These same flavours come out when burned as a subtle flavour, perfect on its own or when combined with your favourite other strains to allow the CBG to counteract the less desirable traits of THC. This flower comes to us from a specialty grower who does indoor and outdoor cultivation.

description: Mood Ring MR Sommelier Selection sativa. With 20+ years of cannabis experience, our cannabis sommelier has mastered the art of phenotype hunting and evaluating premium cannabis. Packaging: nitrogen sealed cans that ensure preservation of the cannabinoids, terpenes, humidity and aromas.

CELEBRITY is dedicated to providing the connoisseur with the most exclusive selection of premium small batch cannabis. No hype, no gimmicks and no legacy blah blah blah.

description: Amnesia Haze is everything a true sativa should be. Uplifting lemon and citrus notes accompanied by energetic spice, earth and zesty aromas from its distinct terpene profile that stays true to her landrace sativa origins. This sativa marvel should satisfy even the most discerning with its lime green buds and delicate texture that is thickly covered in oily trichomes. Always grown indoors in small-batch, strain-specific rooms, then slowly hang-cured and hand-trimmed. At Broken Coast, we grow woah.

Jonny Chronic cartridges are made by Greentank and are compatible with most generic 510 threaded batteries.

Name: IRIE CRAFT CANNABIS Dripz
description: Each one of Dripz's large and dense flowers is handcrafted with utmost care and attention. From the moment of cultivation to the final product, every step is meticulously carried out to ensure the highest level of quality. Once the flowers are harvested, they undergo a thorough and precise drying process, which involves hanging them to air-dry for a minimum of 14 days. Then is set to cure for a minimum of 30 days. This not only preserves the potency of the flower, but also enhances its flavour and aroma. As a result of the intensive process, these flowers possess an overwhelming and captivating aroma that fills the room upon opening. Their flawless appearance is a testament to the careful craftsmanship and the attention to detail.  All in all, these are not just flowers, but luxurious and exquisite products that have been carefully curated to deliver a premium experience.

Name: CLEM & CO. Apricot Cream x Cheese 1:1 Pre-Rolls
description: Experience the perfect harmony of nature with Apricot Cream x Cheese 1:1 cannabis pre-rolls. These beautifully balanced pre-rolls blend the best of myrcene, caryophyllene, and pinene terpenes for a truly captivating experience. Myrcene, with its fruity and floral notes. Caryophyllene adds a touch of spice to the mix. Pinene, with its crisp pine aroma. With a precisely balanced THC to CBD ratio, these pre-rolls offer the best of both worlds. You'll enjoy the benefits of both cannabinoids without the overwhelming effects of high THC strains, making Apricot Cream x Cheese 1:1 the ideal choice for those seeking a balanced and flavourful cannabis experience.

Name: MAX1000 Zaza HTFSE 510 Thread Cartridge | 1.5g

MAX1000 contains terpenes from both HTFSE from fresh frozen cannabis for botanical terpenes to provide complex flavour notes. The cartridge is designed for large hits with a wide ceramic tip to provide a more comfortable feel than cold, hard metal and sophisticated quality feel compared to plastic. Formulated and designed for maximum potency, capacity and vapour production.

With hydrocarbon extraction, that flower’s terp sauce and crystallized cannabinoids are isolated and then reunited, to fill our 510 XL cartridge that draws a clean hit of smooth concentrate from start to finish. This 1.2g 510 thread hardware takes the popular Purple Hills live resin carts to the next level of value and convenience. The Gorilla Zktlz genetic combines the famous GG#4 X Zktlz, which provides a gassy flavour, with a thick tropical fruit bouquet and a hint of chocolate.

We utilize a cryogenic extraction process that preserves the profile of the flower and offers one of the highest levels of purity by preferentially extracting the cannabinoids, terpenes and flavonoids.

You’ll find its aromas fall into the Kush territory meaning it has spicy and gassy notes with a unique warm roasted coffee undertone. This genetic has Edison's highest THC range yet!

Made without animal products or gluten, it comes with a quick onset and higher dose of THC and a double dose of CBD. Best served chilled with a slice of lime. 25 calories | 5g sugar

Name: GREENSEAL Pink Octane | 14g
description: Pink Octane’s sky-high THC and gassy undertones shot it straight to the top of GreenSeal’s in-house Nursery program. The potency is visible on this blushing indica-typical phenotype that is absolutely covered with frosty trichomes. You’ll be tickled pink by its sweet and nutty flavour profile, mingled with a subtle touch of funky fuel aroma.

Name: SPACE RACE CANNABIS Mission Control
description: Mission Control is a unique selection of dried flower – not just another cannabis experience. Each indica strain in our rotating selection has been meticulously grown, harvested and dried to maximize the full spectrum of effects, handpicked for you. Every pack of Mission Control arrives with a distinctive aroma, unique flavour profile and potent effects. Let Mission Control be your guide and embark on a cannabis journey.

Name: LAHOJA Pink Slurricane
description: Pink Slurricane is a hybrid cannabis strain known for its unique and pungent aroma as well as its potent effects. It is created by crossing Pink Kush x Slurricane, resulting in a hybrid that offers a balance of both indica and sativa. Pink Slurricane is characterized by its dense, frosted buds that are often tinged with shades of pink or purple, making it a visually appealing strain.

Big Steppa diamonds are coated with a light layer of gassy true-to-strain terps that combine one of the strongest extracts you’ll ever taste with just the right amount of flavour. Good to dab or as an added fuel in whatever you’re rolling up.

Name: BC GREEN Westcoast Apples and Bananas

These buds grow colourful, dense, extremely potent on the nose and contain a thick blanket of trichomes. When it comes to the flavour of this bud, the name says it all. Apples and Bananas packs a sweet and fruity taste that's filled with delicious sugary bananas and sharply sour apples, with a touch of black pepper to it, too. The aroma takes a spicier turn, with sharp punches of savoury sweet diesel. This is an extremely unique strain with scents and flavours that bounce out of the package as soon its opened. This bud has grape-shaped fluffy forest green buds with deep purple leaves, matching undertones and distinct orange hairs.
